<s> hkma launches first cd-rom </s>
<s> the hong_kong monetary authority ( hkma ) has released a cd @-@ rom as an interactive guide to hong_kong 's monetary and banking systems . </s>
<s> the cd @-@ rom contains a digest of information in the hkma annual report and additional video clips corroborating the importance of hong_kong as an international financial centre . </s>
