<s> " he added . </s>
<s> so far 36 countries have accorded visa @-@ free access to hksar passport holders , </s>
<s> and another seven have announced that they will allow hksar passport holders the same treatment as bn ( o ) passport holders . </s>
<s> demand for the new passport is overwhelming . </s>
<s> the department has received around 120,000 applications . </s>
