<s> commemorative covers for year of heritage on sale </s>
<s> two commemorative covers on the year of heritage are now on sale from the heritage resource centre of the antiquities and monuments office ( amo ) . </s>
<s> the two covers , one on the heritage day in lung yeuk tau and the other on the exhibition on hong_kong 's heritage , are the second and the third in a series of postal items to commemorate the various activities of the year of heritage . </s>
<s> priced at hk $ 25 each , </s>
<s> the second cover bears a hk $ 1.3 definitive stamp and the date chop of the post office while the third cover bears the hk $ 1.3 stamp of british royal cypher which was cancelled by the special postmark of june 30 , 1997 . </s>
