<s> the buildings department approved a total of 42 building plans in july -- 18 on hong_kong island , 11 in kowloon and 13 in the new territories . </s>
<s> this compared with 46 building plans approved in june and 47 in may . </s>
<s> the approved plans covered 25 for apartment and apartment / commercial developments , three for commercial developments , seven for factory and industrial developments , </s>
<s> and seven for community services developments . </s>
<s> consent was given in the month for works to start on 47 building projects , which will provide 45,242 square metres of usable domestic floor area and 197,997 square metres of usable non @-@ domestic floor area on completion . </s>
<s> the department also issued 33 occupation permits -- 10 on hong_kong island , 10 in kowloon and 13 in the new territories . </s>
<s> of the buildings certified for occupation in july , the usable floor area for domestic and non @-@ domestic uses were 33,343 square metres and 123,842 square metres respectively . </s>
<s> the declared cost of new buildings completed in the month totalled about $ 3.724 billion . </s>
<s> in addition , 16 demolition consents involving 12 buildings and structures were issued . </s>
<s> the department 's control and enforcement division received 1,176 complaints against unauthorised building works in july , and issued 183 removal orders on unauthorised works . </s>
