<s> " a social welfare department spokesman said today ( saturday ) . </s>
<s> " those who should be paid through the hong_kong bank or hang seng bank on the public holidays will have their pay days advanced to september 30 . " however , </s>
<s> those who should be paid through other banks on september 30 , october 1 and 2 will get their payments after the public holidays on october 3 , " he added . </s>
