<s> the metrication committee , and the committee on management and supervisory training of the vocational training council . </s>
<s> ms shing is currently a member of several advisory committees on the business and social sciences field in academic institutions including advisory committee on business & management studies , hong_kong polytechnic university and course advisory committee , ba ( hons ) in arts & social sciences , </s>
