<s> issue and settlement date : tuesday , 14 october 1997 </s>
<s> amount on offer : hk $ 500 million plus an additional hk $ 100 million </s>
<s> maturity : three years </s>
<s> maturity date : 16 october 2000 </s>
<s> interest rate : 6.50 % per annum payable </s>
