<s> and the ongoing commitment to the rule of law , a free and open press , civil liberties and human rights . </s>
<s> he outlined his plans to improve education , </s>
<s> encourage the development of value @-@ added service industries and increase the use of information technology to maintain hong_kong 's economic vitality and competitiveness in the future . </s>
<s> non @-@ means tested loan for tertiary students </s>
<s> the government announced today ( tuesday ) that a new non @-@ means tested loan scheme ( nls ) would be introduced for all full @-@ time local tertiary students in the 1998 / 99 academic year to complement the existing means @-@ tested loan scheme . </s>
<s> the administration will also implement a number of measures to improve the local student finance scheme ( lsfs ) to enhance its efficiency , </s>
<s> " it is government policy that no qualified student will be denied access to tertiary education because of a lack of means , " deputy secretary for education and manpower , mr matthew cheung kin @-@ chung , </s>
<s> said . </s>
<s> the government now provides means @-@ tested grant and / or loan through the local student finance scheme ( lsfs ) to eligible full @-@ time local tertiary students studying at specified tertiary institutions . </s>
<s> in 1996 / 97 , </s>
<s> a total of $ 968 million in grants and $ 945 million in normal and extended loans were disbursed to 37,502 students ( or about 60 per cent of the total student population ) . </s>
<s> successful applicants of the lsfs on average received $ 27,985 in grants and / or $ 24,566 in normal loans . </s>
<s> " we will introduce a new non @-@ means tested loan scheme for all full @-@ time local tertiary students in the 1998 / 99 academic year to complement the existing means @-@ tested scheme , </s>
<s> " mr cheung noted . </s>
<s> " the new loan scheme will disburse around $ 1,274 million in 1998 / 99 , </s>
<s> benefiting about 50,000 tertiary students or 79 per cent of the student population . </s>
<s> ( c ) failed in the means test ; </s>
<s> and ( e ) want to incur education @-@ related expenses not currently covered by the lsfs , e.g. purchase of personal computers . " </s>
<s> mr cheung explained that the nls would operate on a " no @-@ gain @-@ no - loss and cost @-@ recovery basis " so as to avoid subsidising students who were not prepared to be means @-@ tested or who failed the means @-@ test , </s>
<s> and to avoid possible abuses of the scheme for non @-@ educational purpose . </s>
<s> " we will charge a risk @-@ adjusted civil service housing loan scheme ( cshls ) interest rate ( i.e. 7.575 per cent at the moment ) , </s>
<s> which is based on the no @-@ gain @-@ no - loss cshls interest rate ( currently at 6.075 per cent ) plus 1.5 per cent to cover government 's risk in providing students with unsecured loans , </s>
<s> " he said . </s>
<s> " in addition , we will charge an annual administrative fee to recover the full costs incurred in processing an application and administering a loan repayment account . </s>
<s> according to preliminary calculation , </s>
<s> the annual administrative fee will be around $ 185 ( at 1998 / 99 price level ) . </s>
<s> under the new scheme , a student may borrow up to the tuition fee level . </s>
<s> those already receiving some assistance under the lsfs may apply for top @-@ up loans under the nls up to the difference between the amount of financial assistance they obtain under the lsfs and the maximum financial assistance under the lsfs provided that the tuition fee level would not be exceeded . </s>
<s> nls recipients have to repay their nls loans in 40 quarterly instalments within ten years upon graduation . </s>
<s> assuming an undergraduate student borrows up to 80 per cent of the tuition fee throughout his three @-@ year course , </s>
<s> he will have to repay about $ 1,500 each month or $ 4,500 a quarter until 10 years after graduation . </s>
<s> to prevent possible abuses of the new scheme for non @-@ educational purposes , </s>
<s> nls loans will be disbursed to institutions concerned direct for settlement of tuition fees . </s>
<s> mr cheung stressed that those needy students who satisfied the means test would continue to enjoy grants and loans at low interest rate of 2.5 per cent per annum . </s>
<s> turning to the measures to improve the lsfs , mr cheung said that they were aimed at enhancing the scheme 's efficiency , transparency and fairness . </s>
<s> " we will replace the existing cumbersome formula which takes into account income , expenditure and asset with a new formula which no longer takes into account family expenditure , </s>
<s> except for uncontrollable medical expenses for chronically ill family members , " he explained . </s>
<s> " this will simplify the vetting procedures and minimise intrusion into the privacy of applicants ' families . </s>
<s> furthermore , the new formula will benefit low @-@ income , low @-@ expenditure family . </s>
<s> " in assessing the applicants ' assets , we will treat liquid and fixed assets equally . </s>
<s> in so doing , we will no longer treat households with liquid assets less favourable than those who own one or more flats in addition to their residence . </s>
<s> this also brings the lsfs asset test in line with the practices of other government assistance schemes . </s>
<s> " to speed up processing time and facilitate early payment of financial assistance , </s>
<s> we will ask applicants to provide details of their assets and sign a declaration confirming the level of the household 's current net assets . </s>
<s> authentication of application will only be conducted after payment of financial assistance . </s>
<s> we will of course rectify any discrepancies identified in the authentication process . </s>
<s> " overall speaking , roughly the same number of students will continue to be eligible for financial assistance under the new formula . </s>
<s> some groups ( notably those with low @-@ income , </s>
<s> low @-@ expenditure but some liquid assets ) will be better off whereas those high @-@ income , </s>
<s> high @-@ expenditure group with expensive fixed asset in addition to their first home will become worse off . </s>
<s> " we believe that the new formula will target at the genuinely needy . " </s>
<s> mr cheung pointed out that the government would also step up measures to strengthen the integrity of the means @-@ tested lsfs to ensure that government subsidies go to those who are genuinely deserving families . </s>
<s> " in drawing up the non @-@ means tested loan scheme and the series of improvement measures , </s>
<s> we have accepted the key recommendations of the joint committee on student finance ( jcsf ) , </s>
<s> which is a non @-@ statutory committee comprising lay members , </s>
<s> as well as institutional and student representatives of institutions covered by the lsfs , " he noted . </s>
<s> " the jcsf also took account of the recommendations of consultancy study and the views expressed during the public consultation exercise in 1996 . </s>
<s> " subject to the approval of funds by the finance committee of the provisional legislative council , </s>
<s> we will implement the improvement measures and launch the nls in the 1998 @-@ 99 academic year , " he said . </s>
