<s> training course and seminar in building management </s>
<s> owners ' corporations and mutual aid committees in kwun tong are invited to take part in a two @-@ day training course and a seminar on building management next month . the programme , jointly organised by the kwun tong provisional district board 's housing committee and kwun tong district office , </s>
<s> is aimed at helping the public get a better understanding of building management . </s>
<s> the training course will be held on november 17 ( monday ) and november 20 ( thursday ) from 8 pm to 9.30 pm at kwun tong district office conference room , third floor , 6 tung yan street , </s>
<s> kwun tong . the course will focus on two topics : " building management without corruption " and " maintenance of electricity facilities in buildings " . </s>
<s> participants who have completed the two @-@ day course will be awarded an attendance certificate . </s>
<s> the seminar will be held on november 22 ( saturday ) from 2 pm to 5 pm at the regal kowloon hotel in tsim sha tsui east . </s>
<s> the topics include " fire prevention safety measures " and " the authorities and liabilities of owners ' corporations " . speakers include representatives from the fire services department , buildings department and law society of hong_kong . </s>
<s> application forms for the training course and the seminar are now available at the kwun tong district office . </s>
<s> applications for the course and the seminar will close on november 7 and november 12 respectively . </s>
<s> enquiries can be made on 2341 6315 ext 39 or 40 . </s>
<s> students to be quizzed on careers </s>
<s> about 159,500 students from 306 secondary schools including four special schools in hong_kong will take part in the careers quiz next week , </s>
<s> setting a record high number of participants since the careers quiz was first launched in 1982 . </s>
<s> " the 16 th careers quiz , </s>
<s> an annual event organised by the labour department 's careers advisory service , aims at enhancing students ' awareness of the importance of choosing a suitable career as well as encouraging them to actively look for information on careers and further educational opportunities , " senior labour officer , </s>
<s> mrs louisa poon , said today ( tuesday ) . </s>
<s> the quiz , to be held from october 27 to 31 , </s>
<s> requires participating secondary 3 to secondary 7 students to answer 50 multiple choice questions in 30 minutes . </s>
<s> it is the first time that secondary 6 and 7 and special school students are invited to take part in the quiz . </s>
<s> students will be asked questions on careers information , tertiary educational opportunities , technical and vocational training , employment legislation and services offered by the labour department . </s>
<s> winning schools and students will be awarded a total of about 1,800 prizes sponsored by pentax cameras and binoculars , enjoy sunglasses , lamy ball pens and instant @-@ dict electronic translators . </s>
<s> mrs poon expressed appreciation of the generous donations by the sponsor and the tremendous technical support by the itsd . </s>
<s> " the careers quiz is an associated activity of the 8 th education and careers expo to be held from february 19 to 22 , </s>
<s> 1998 at the hong_kong convention and exhibition centre . the quiz questions will be displayed at the expo and members of the public are welcome to try the questions there and win attractive souvenirs , </s>
<s> " she added . </s>
<s> members of owners ' corporations and mutual aid committees and the general public are invited to attend a seminar on fire prevention organised by the wan chai area committee this friday ( october 24 ) . </s>
<s> with the assistance of wan chai district office and sponsorship from wan chai provisional district board , the seminar is aimed at promoting public awareness of fire prevention in buildings . </s>
<s> senior station officer of the fire protection bureau of the fire services department , mr chan yiu @-@ ming , will share his knowledge on fire prevention at home . </s>
<s> his talk will be supplemented by a video on fire prevention and a forum for participants to exchange views with the speaker . </s>
<s> assistant district officer from wan chai , mr eric chan , will officiate at the seminar . </s>
