<s> 71 convicted pollution cases in september </s>
<s> a total of 71 convictions were recorded in the courts in september for breaching anti @-@ pollution legislation enforced by the environmental protection department . </s>
<s> of these cases , </s>
<s> 25 were convictions made under the water pollution control ordinance ( wpco ) , 27 under the noise control ordinance ( nco ) , 11 under the air pollution control ordinance ( apco ) , </s>
<s> six under the waste disposal ordinance ( wdo ) and two under the dumping at sea ordinance ( daso ) . </s>
<s> the fines ranged from $ 2,000 to 100,000 . </s>
<s> china state construction engineering corporation and shui on building contractors limited were fined for the heaviest fine last month for breaching the noise control ordinance . </s>
