<s> planning : an important role in city development </s>
<s> planning has played an important and positive role in hong_kong 's development in the past 50 years , </s>
<s> the director of planning , dr peter pun , said today ( thursday ) . </s>
<s> citing an example , </s>
<s> dr pun said the new town and comprehensive housing development programme launched by the government in 1970 s not only provided an effective solution to the housing problem but also improved living conditions . </s>
<s> " while urban renewal programmes offer opportunities to upgrade the living environment , community facilities and transportation , </s>
<s> appropriate reclamation projects provide new land for hong_kong 's overall planning such as the development of the new airport and extension of commercial areas in the city centre , </s>
<s> " he said . </s>
<s> dr pun was speaking at the opening ceremony of the planning departments ' outreach programme at pooi to middle school in kowloon city . </s>
<s> turning to education , </s>
<s> dr pun said the department had to reserve sufficient and suitable land for the construction of various educational facilities to meet the growth of the population . </s>
<s> " to help achieve the target of quality education and implement the policy of whole @-@ day primary schooling , </s>
<s> we will spare no efforts in identifying and reserving adequate sites for the construction of educational institutions of different kinds and scales , </s>
<s> " he added . </s>
<s> dr pun also said his department attached great importance to promoting public understanding of city planning . </s>
<s> " in the course of planning , </s>
<s> we do not only apply professional knowledge but also seek to balance the needs and interests of various sections of the community , " he said . </s>
<s> " we listen to the views of various quarters through consultation , </s>
<s> " he added . </s>
<s> the outreach programme is one of the planning department 's activities to celebrate the 50 th anniversary of the setting up of a dedicated office within the government for town planning . </s>
<s> the programme features a roving exhibition among 14 secondary schools which covers a number of planning topics , </s>
<s> including new town development , airport @-@ related projects , conservation and urban renewal . </s>
<s> professional town planners will also speak on a topic chosen by each participating school . </s>
<s> a spokesman for the department of health said today ( thursday ) the suspected cholera case notified to the department yesterday was confirmed as a local cholera case . </s>
<s> the patient was a 33 @-@ year @-@ old female living in sheung shui . </s>
<s> she presented with watery diarrhea on october 15 and is now being treated in princess margaret hospital . her present condition is satisfactory . </s>
<s> " investigations are ongoing to trace the source of infection and there is no evidence of secondary spread , </s>
<s> " the spokesman said . he added that the patient 's family had no symptoms of cholera and their home was disinfected . </s>
<s> cholera is an endemic disease in hong_kong . </s>
<s> there are a total of 14 cases of cholera so far this year ( as at october 23 ) while the number of cholera cases from 1994 to 1996 are 56 , </s>
<s> to prevent cholera and other food borne diseases , the spokesman advised the public to observe good personal , food and environmental hygiene . </s>
<s> * wash hands with soap after visiting toilet and before preparing or eating food ; </s>
<s> * observe good environmental hygiene and keep kitchen and cooking utensils clean ; </s>
<s> * cook food , especially meat and shellfish , thoroughly before consumption ; </s>
<s> * store properly all perishable food not meant for immediate consumption ; </s>
<s> * leftover food should be reheated thoroughly before consumption ; </s>
<s> * all garbage and waste should be stored in a covered container before disposal . </s>
<s> insurance premium income recorded 4. 8 pc growth in 1996 </s>
<s> the hong_kong insurance industry grew by 4.8 per cent in 1996 in terms of premium income , compared with 11.8 per cent in 1995. according to the provisional statistics on the hong_kong insurance market released today ( thursday ) by the commissioner of insurance , </s>
<s> mr alan wong , the total premium income of general business ( excluding lloyd 's ) and long term business amounted to $ 45.9 billion in 1996 , representing about 3.8 per cent of the hong_kong gross domestic product . </s>
<s> despite the overall growth , general business experienced a decline in 1996 . </s>
<s> gross premiums dropped by 9.6 per cent from $ 20.1 billion in 1995 to $ 18.2 billion in 1996 , compared with a marginal growth of 2 per cent in 1995 . </s>
<s> gross premiums in respect of direct business and reinsurance inward business were down by 8.6 per cent to $ 13.9 billion and 10.4 percent to $ 4.3 billion respectively . </s>
<s> except accident & health business , gross premiums in respect of all other major classes of business showed a decline . </s>
<s> the decline in the case of motor vehicle business and general liability business ( comprising mainly employees ' compensation business ) was particularly notable where the gross premiums declined by 18.7 per cent to $ 3 billion and 20.4 per cent to $ 3.2 billion respectively in 1996 . </s>
<s> property damage business remained the largest class , accounting for 33 per cent of the total gross premiums in 1996 , </s>
<s> followed by motor vehicle business and general liability business each representing 17 per cent . </s>
<s> compared with the drop in gross premiums , net premiums after reinsurance decreased by a relatively higher rate of 12 per cent to $ 11.7 billion in 1996 . </s>
<s> this can be explained by the reduction in retention ratio from 66 per cent in 1995 to 64 per cent in 1996 . </s>
<s> total claims paid amounted to $ 8.6 billion in 1996. the net amount after deducting reinsurance recoveries stood at $ 5.5 billion . </s>
<s> the net claims incurred ratio ( net claims incurred to net earned premiums ) slightly improved from 54 per cent in 1995 to 53 per cent in 1996 . </s>
<s> albeit smaller than that in 1995. underwriting profit for 1996 was in the region of $ 0.6 billion as compared with $ 0.7 billion in 1995 . </s>
<s> lloyd 's underwriters in hong_kong are subject to a different reporting system and therefore the above statistics do not include those relating to lloyd 's . </s>
<s> turning to the premium level in 1997 , according to the latest monthly premiums reported by insurers , </s>
<s> gross premiums for the period from january to august 1997 amounted to about $ 12.8 billion , representing a marginal growth of 2.4 per cent compared with the corresponding period in 1996 . </s>
<s> long term business , on the contrary , </s>
<s> continued to register a growth of 17 per cent in 1996 , as compared with a 22 per cent growth in 1995 . </s>
<s> individual life business remained as the major contributor to long term business . office premiums in force amounted to $ 19.6 billion at the end of 1996 , </s>
<s> the number of individual life policies in force exceeded 3.1 million which covered about 49 per cent of the hong_kong population ( on the basis of one person holding one policy ) , </s>
<s> compared with 45 per cent at the end of 1995 . </s>
<s> net liabilities in respect of these policies increased by 26 per cent to $ 41 billion . </s>
<s> as regards new individual life business , despite a drop of two per cent in the total number of newly issued policies to 594,396 in 1996 , </s>
<s> office premiums for these new policies increased by 18 per cent to $ 5.5 billion . this was mainly attributable to the growth in sales of ( investment ) linked policies which attracted considerable single premiums . </s>
<s> office premiums of new linked business increased by 44 per cent to $ 1.7 billion which accounted for about 30 per cent of office premiums for new individual life business . </s>
<s> non @-@ linked business represented the remaining 70 per cent with about 45 per cent related to whole life policies . </s>
<s> in 1996 , the total number of retirement schemes policies managed by insurance companies grew by 10.5 per cent to 13,549 . </s>
<s> total contributions and net liabilities thereof also increased by 13.8 per cent to $ 7.2 billion and 19.3 per cent to $ 33.3 billion respectively . </s>
<s> office premiums in force in respect of group life , permanent health and annuity business only accounted for three per cent of the long term business . </s>
<s> while group life and permanent health business registered a growth in premiums , annuity business however experienced a significant decline in 1996 . </s>
<s> as at september 30,1997 , there were 217 authorised insurers . </s>
<s> among them , there were 153 general insurers , 45 long term insurers and 19 composite insurers . </s>
<s> as regards insurance intermediaries , there were 317 insurance brokers and 33,320 insurance agents . </s>
<s> survey on chinese medicine organisations and institutions </s>
<s> the preparatory committee on chinese medicine ( pccm ) announced today ( thursday ) that it would conduct a survey on traditional chinese medicine ( tcm ) organisations and institutions in hong_kong . </s>
<s> introducing the survey at the press briefing , the chairman of the pccm , dr daniel tse , said : </s>
<s> " the aim of the survey is to collect statistics and related information in respect of these organisations and institutions so as to facilitate the pccm in making recommendations for the development and regulation of tcm in hong_kong . " </s>
<s> " the survey is targeted at tcm organisations , </s>
<s> they will be requested to provide data and information using the cut @-@ off date of september 1 , 1997 by completing the respective questionnaires . </s>
<s> " </s>
<s> also at the press briefing were the chairman of the traditional chinese medicine practitioners sub @-@ committee , mr cheung tai @-@ chiu ; and the vice @-@ chairman of the chinese medicine sub @-@ committee , mr chang wei @-@ chung . </s>
<s> explaining the types of tcm organisations which will be invited to participate in the survey , mr cheung said : </s>
<s> " they include tcm associations and societies whose members comprise principally of individuals in the tcm profession and trades , as well as tcm federations and trade organisations . " </s>
<s> mr chang clarified that : " these institutions should have been set up on or before september 1 , 1997 and registered under the business registration ordinance . the survey however does not cover tcm retailers . " </s>
<s> he further appealed to the tcm traders that by supporting the survey voluntarily , </s>
<s> the development of tcm in hong_kong could be greatly enhanced . </s>
<s> on the survey on tcm research institutions , mr chang said : </s>
<s> " it will assist the pccm in understanding the current development of tcm scientific research in hong_kong . it will also facilitate the future communication between pccm and these institutions . " </s>
<s> appealing to all the tcm organisations and institutions concerned , dr tse said the survey would help accelerate the future development of tcm in hong_kong and its success would rely on their support . </s>
<s> the closing date for the survey is november 30 , 1997. completed questionnaires should be returned to the pccm secretariat , first floor , </s>
<s> shun feng international centre , 182 queen 's road east , wan chai , hong_kong . </s>
<s> enquiries can be directed to 2527 8309 or 2527 8312 . </s>
<s> eleven consent applications approved in third quarter the lands department issued a total of 11 consents for the pre @-@ sale of residential and non @-@ residential units in uncompleted developments from july 1 to september 30 , 1997 . </s>
<s> a spokesman for the lands department said today ( thursday ) that among them , nine consents were for the sale of 5,441 residential units on hong_kong island and in sha tin , </s>
<s> tai po , sai kung , tsuen wan , kwai tsing and yuen long . </s>
<s> the majority are due for completion before the end of august 1998 . </s>
<s> the other two applications were for the pre @-@ sale of commercial units in central and tai kok tsui . </s>
<s> " the government has so far issued six pre @-@ sale consents which are subject to the additional anti @-@ speculation measures announced by the secretary for housing on march 26 , </s>
<s> 1997. they involve 4,172 units , " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> as at september 30 , </s>
<s> a total of 16 applications for pre @-@ sale consent involving 14,359 residential units and 10 applications in respect of non @-@ residential developments were pending approval . </s>
<s> among the 16 applications , four are private sector participation scheme ( psps ) projects involving 11,674 units . </s>
<s> the other 12 developments , </s>
<s> totalling 2,685 units , are private developments subject to the anti @-@ speculation measures introduced on june 8 , 1994 . </s>
<s> these developments are located in various parts of the territory . the majority are estimated to be completed between early 1998 and early 1999 . </s>
<s> among the 12 developments , only one with 98 units in shau kei wan , is not subject to the additional anti @-@ speculation measures as the application was submitted before march 26 . </s>
<s> since the introduction of the new measures for the pre @-@ sale of residential units in june 1994 , the department has given consent to a total of 43,828 residential units . </s>
<s> during the same period , five psps projects ( totalling 8,150 units ) , </s>
<s> seven sandwich class housing developments ( 5,954 units ) and five flat @-@ for @-@ sale scheme projects ( 4,462 units ) - all of which are not subject to the new measures - were given pre @-@ sale consents . </s>
<s> the director of legal aid , mr chan shu @-@ ying , </s>
<s> today ( thursday ) announced that a performance pledge on processing time will be introduced with effect from november 1 , 1997 . </s>
<s> for all applications received on or after november 1 , the department will make a decision on whether to grant legal aid within the time frame as set out below : </s>
<s> standard performance type of applications processing time target civil legal aid within 3 months 80 % from the date of </s>
<s> * appeals </s>
<s> * court of first within 10 working 90 % instance of the high days from the date court / district court of application </s>
<s> * committal proceedings within 8 working 90 % days from the date of application </s>
<s> queensway government offices , 66 queensway ; kowloon branch office of the legal aid department , third floor , mong kok government offices , 30 luen wan street , mong kok as well as the district offices . </s>
<s> the launching of the performance pledge on processing time is one of the major initiatives introduced to improve the quality of legal aid services , and has the full support of the legal aid services council . </s>
<s> the department has accepted the need to speed up the processing of application for legal aid to meet the rising expectations of the public . </s>
<s> in november last year , the department formed a working group to examine the issue . </s>
<s> a quality improvement team was also formed to study how the workflow in the processing of applications could be simplified and streamlined . </s>
<s> the following improvement measures have been adopted : </s>
<s> * since april 1997 , the application and processing division including the kowloon branch office have been reorganised and strengthened . </s>
<s> * starting from september 1 , 1997 , the department has completely taken over all means @-@ testing of legal aid applications from the social welfare department . </s>
<s> * the information and advisory service has been strengthened to provide information on availability of legal aid and scope of legal aid services and such other information as may be of assistance to potential applicants . </s>
<s> * a series of training or refresher course has been arranged since early june to prepare staff working in the application section . </s>
<s> * the guidelines for professional staff on processing of applications were revised . </s>
<s> * a checklist of documents required from legal aid applicants for processing applications was prepared . </s>
<s> * a one @-@ stop service was introduced such that as far as possible , an applicant is given an appointment to attend the department to enable both the means test and the statement taking work to be done on the same day . </s>
<s> effective control system to protect traders ' interests </s>
<s> the hong_kong special administrative region ( hksar ) government is doing all it can to ensure that its effective trade control system works and that the interests of its legitimate traders are protected , </s>
<s> mr lai is one of the speakers of the general session on customs and trade at the new york state bar association conference being held in hong_kong . </s>
<s> " as enshrined in the basic law , </s>
<s> the hksar remains a separate customs territory after the transition . </s>
<s> " the integrity of our trade control system is the cornerstone of our separate customs territory status . </s>
<s> " we take our international obligations under the world trade organisation ( wto ) agreement on textiles and clothing seriously and maintain the utmost vigilance over attempts to abuse origin rules . " </s>
<s> " we believe that we have an effective system to deal with the problem of illegal transshipment , </s>
<s> particularly with the series of new initiatives that we have introduced in the past two and a half years , " mr lai said . </s>
<s> such initiatives include factory audit checks introduced in november 1996 and the integrated consignment and factory inspection introduced since march 1997 . </s>
<s> the trade department had taken administrative action against factories which failed to comply with the factory audit check requirements by suspending their licensing and certification facilities . </s>
<s> " we will continue with these initiatives , and will continue to work in co @-@ operation with our trading partners to enhance both sides ' effectiveness in the common objective of tackling illegal transshipment , </s>
<s> " mr lai added . </s>
<s> " on control over strategic commodities , </s>
<s> we are glad to see the reaffirmation of the united_states supportive policy towards the hksar in the agreed minute signed by us commerce department secretary , mr william daley and our secretary for trade and industry , miss denise yue in hong_kong earlier this month . </s>
<s> " as stated by our secretary , </s>
<s> it is in hksar 's own economic and commercial interest to maintain effective controls over strategic commodities trade because only by so doing can we ensure our free access to sophisticated goods and technologies essential for hong_kong 's economic development , </s>
<s> " mr lai said . </s>
<s> in 1996 , 201 cases were successfully prosecuted , involving goods of a total value of more than $ 800 million . </s>
<s> a total fine of $ 3.6 million was imposed by the courts . </s>
<s> " we are indeed following the highest standard of control , and our laws are being implemented professionally and impartially . </s>
<s> " we look forward to receiving continued support from our trading partners , " mr lai said . </s>
<s> turning to how the " one country , two systems " concept works in the area of trade after the transition , mr lai said , </s>
<s> " the basic law confers on the hksar a high degree of autonomy in economic , trade , finance and monetary matters . </s>
<s> " as provided in the basic law , </s>
<s> the hksar shall pursue the policy of free trade , and we have a level playing field for local and overseas companies alike . " </s>
<s> mr lai said , " as a separate trading entity different from the mainland of china , </s>
<s> trade between hong_kong and the mainland of china continues to be operated on the basis and rules of foreign trade . </s>
<s> " article 116 of the basic law provides that export quotas , </s>
<s> tariff preferences and other similar arrangements obtained by the hksar shall be enjoyed exclusively by the region . " </s>
<s> " according to the basic law , </s>
<s> the hksar remains its full and separate memberships to the wto and the asia @-@ pacific economic co @-@ operation ( apec ) , using the name ' hong_kong , china ' . </s>
<s> " i can assure you that our independent voice will continue to be heard in international trade forums , </s>
<s> " mr lai said . </s>
<s> " our independent participation in the wto will remain unchanged after china accedes to the organisation . </s>
<s> " we will continue to defend hksar 's trading interests vigorously , " mr lai added . </s>
<s> declaration of explosives depot as protected place </s>
<s> the chief executive in council has ordered that the government explosives depot relocated from stonecutters island to kau shat wan , </s>
<s> lantau island should be declared as a protected place under section 2 of the protected places ( safety ) ordinance ( cap. 260 ) , an sar government spokesman said today ( thursday ) . </s>
<s> the government explosives depot at stonecutters island was declared as a protected place under the same ordinance . </s>
<s> " subsequent to the relocation , </s>
<s> we need to update the ordinance so that the guards protecting the depot at kau shat wan are lawfully authorized to discharge their duties , " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> the guards will be assigned by a firm pursuant to a contract managed by the civil engineering department as they were at stonecutters island . </s>
<s> " the amendment is necessary to ensure public safety and is considered to be essential for the smooth operation of the hksar , </s>
<s> " the spokesman added . </s>
<s> seminar on building management well received </s>
<s> more than 150 members of owners ' corporations and mutual aid committees in the central and western district participated in the seminar on building management and home safety tonight ( thursday ) in sheung wan civic centre . </s>
<s> jointly organised by the central and western district office , the multi @-@ storey building owners association of central district ( hong_kong ) limited , the multi @-@ storey building owners association of western district ( hong_kong ) limited and the central and western district fight crime committee with sponsorship from central and western provisional district board , </s>
<s> the seminar was organised to arouse participants ' awareness and concern over effective building management . </s>
<s> speaking at the opening of the seminar , central and western district officer , mrs charlotte li , said : </s>
<s> " we have long been concerned about the safety of buildings in our district . </s>
<s> it is expected that the seminar can benefit the participants by providing them with expert advice to upgrade the management of their buildings . " </s>
<s> " eliminating or minimizing our building safety problems will surely contribute to better protection of lives and property , </s>
<s> " she added . </s>
<s> during the two @-@ hour seminar , representatives from four government departments were invited to speak on their respective areas of expertise . </s>
<s> chief building surveyor of the buildings department , mr hui siu @-@ wai , explained to the participants the consultation paper on building safety inspection scheme ( bsis ) requiring privately @-@ owned buildings over 20 years old to undergo building safety inspections on a mandatory basis . </s>
<s> the subject drew intense discussion among participants and constructive comments were collected . </s>
<s> senior station officer of the fire services department , mr ng lung @-@ kwong , shared his knowledge on fire prevention and escape ; </s>
<s> while labour officer from the labour department , ms tai lai @-@ sheng , gave a talk on relevant labour ordinances affecting building security guards . </s>
<s> two other speakers from crime prevention bureau of the central police station , mr chiu hon @-@ keung and mr fong chi @-@ keung , stressed the importance of building security and gave advice on crime prevention . </s>
<s> the talks were followed by exchanges between the speakers and the participants . </s>
