<s> in order to give more room for the overnight interbank interest rate to move , </s>
<s> the hong_kong monetary authority has adjusted the bid and offer rates under the liquidity adjustment facility ( laf ) to four per cent and seven percent respectively with effect from today . </s>
<s> the corresponding rates before the adjustment were 4.25 per cent and 6.25 per cent . </s>
<s> since the inception of the laf in june 1992 , the width of the laf corridor has been maintained at 200 basis points . </s>
<s> during the asian currency turmoil , overnight interbank interest rate has exhibited a higher degree of volatility . </s>
<s> a wider laf corridor is considered appropriate to provide more room for the overnight interbank interest rate to move to reflect conditions in the interbank market . </s>
<s> the laf rates and the width of laf corridor will be reviewed from time to time in the light of market conditions . </s>
