<s> public consultation on building inspection scheme to end </s>
<s> members of the public are reminded to give their views on a proposal to implement the building safety inspection scheme on a mandatory basis before the two @-@ month consultation ends on friday ( october 31 ) . </s>
<s> the proposal will eventually apply to all private buildings over 20 years old . </s>
<s> " a total of 41 submissions have so far been received from the public , </s>
<s> " a spokesman for the buildings department said today ( sunday ) . </s>
<s> " we are glad that responses so far indicate support in principle for the proposed scheme , " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> " in addition , </s>
<s> we have consulted professional bodies , the financial sector , the lands and building advisory committee , the provisional legislative council and the provisional district boards , </s>
<s> " he said . </s>
<s> " constructive comments have been received on matters of detail covering technical standards , </s>
<s> procedures , financing and other practical problems , " he said . </s>
<s> " we will study all comments in detail before we put any legislative proposals to the provisional legislative council next year , </s>
<s> " he said . </s>
<s> " we hope the mandatory phase of the scheme can be implemented next august , " he added . </s>
<s> he said that the government would consider setting up a $ 500 million urban rehabilitation fund to provide low interest loans to qualified owners of buildings to undertake building inspection and repair works . </s>
<s> " if found feasible , details of the fund will be announced at a later stage , </s>
<s> " he added . </s>
<s> the scheme will impose a legal responsibility on building owners to have their properties regularly inspected , maintained and repaired to ensure safety of occupants and the public . </s>
<s> under the proposed scheme , the building authority will issue statutory orders requiring building owners to appoint authorised persons or structural engineers to inspect their properties . </s>
<s> there will be two levels of inspection , namely general appraisal and detailed investigation . </s>
<s> " detailed investigation and repair works will be necessary only if recommended by building professionals after the general appraisal , </s>
<s> and supported by the buildings department , " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> he stressed that proper maintenance of buildings was not only in the interest of public safety but also could enhance their value , </s>
<s> to the benefit of owners . </s>
<s> the marine environment of yan chau tong marine park will be greatly improved following the removal of abandoned fishing gear on the seabed today ( sunday ) . </s>
<s> the removal exercise was organised by the agriculture and fisheries department ( afd ) to clear the so @-@ called ghost @-@ fishing gear ( gfg ) found in the marine park so as to prevent causing further damage to marine resources . </s>
<s> an afd spokesman pointed out that these abandoned fishing equipment left on the seabed by fishermen might continue to trap and kill marine life . </s>
<s> " the resources trapped inside are wasted and in turn reduce the harvest of fishermen , </s>
<s> while by @-@ catch such as crabs and sea urchins might be killed incidentally , " he said . </s>
<s> a similar exercise was conducted in 1995 at hoi ha wan , where about one tonne of gfg was removed and disposed of . </s>
<s> he said the exercise could help to increase the awareness of fishermen on the problem of gfg . </s>
<s> " it will also promote co @-@ operation among afd , green groups and fishermen for the management of the marine park , " he said . </s>
<s> yan chau tong was designated as a marine park last year under the marine parks ordinance for long @-@ term improvement to the marine environment . </s>
<s> marine parks are set up to protect the rich and diverse communities of marine life and the variety of landscape of the territory 's seashore and coastal waters . </s>
<s> in addition to providing a place for the enjoyment of the public , fishermen will also be benefited through a better fish stock generated from the area . </s>
<s> today 's exercise was assisted by divers from a number of organisations , including the hong_kong marine conservation society , prodive , south china dive club and ymca dive club . </s>
<s> fishermen from sha tau kok and kat o and students from the baptist university also helped in this event . </s>
<s> the abandoned gear was identified by afd staff beforehand . the removed gfg will be disposed of in a landfill tomorrow . </s>
