<s> hongkong post launches new speedpost marketing campaign </s>
<s> hongkong post will be launching a new tv commercial in both tvb and atv english and chinese channels starting tomorrow ( monday ) , </s>
<s> as part of a fresh marketing campaign for speedpost , the postmaster general , mr robert footman , announced today ( sunday ) . </s>
<s> " we are using ' we put time on your side ' as the overall creative theme to emphasise that speedpost is committed to on @-@ time delivery of documents and packages for customers all over the world . </s>
<s> " in the commercial , we will see a speedpost man collecting a parcel from a busy hong_kong office . </s>
<s> from the moment he touches the parcel , everything around him starts moving backwards . </s>
<s> as the reverse action continues , </s>
<s> he walks forwards through the streets of hong_kong and ends up in beijing , where he delivers the parcel to a kite factory . </s>
<s> " the moment he hands over the parcel , the action starts going forwards again , </s>
<s> signifying that speedpost puts time on your side , " mr footman explained . </s>
<s> in a second version of the commercial , the parcel is delivered to a fashion studio in paris . </s>
<s> the beijing and paris versions will be aired alternately to reinforce the message that speedpost operates an international courier service with an extensive global network and with the widest courier network in china covering more than 1,500 cities . </s>
