<s> mr footman noted that there would be print advertisements in major newspapers , big posters at mtr station , and posters put up at post offices . </s>
<s> " the hurdles and green light in the poster advertisements reinforce the key message that no matter what happens , </s>
<s> we put time on your side to guarantee speedy and reliable delivery services , or your money back . " in order to meet the changing needs of customers , </s>
