<s> dollar link will not change : fs </s>
<s> the financial secretary , mr donald tsang , today ( monday ) reiterated that hong_kong would not change the dollar link . </s>
<s> he warned that the only people who would be burned by speculation against the hong_kong dollar were the speculators . </s>
<s> speaking at the 11 th international investment funds conference , mr tsang said he understood that there were particular sectors of the economy hurt by the exchange rate changes relative to some other asian economies , </s>
<s> " but my duty is to serve the public interest , not sectoral interest , " mr tsang said . </s>
<s> he said : " hong_kong is not any other asian economy . we do not have a huge , unearning stock of vacant offices . </s>
<s> two thirds of our domestic exports and three quarters of our re @-@ exports within asia go to china and japan ; </s>
<s> " crucial sectors of our economy , such as our financial services industry , benefit from stability . " </s>
<s> mr tsang said he would watch developments in the region closely , </s>
<s> particularly the efforts of various governments to put in place remedial and structural reform measures needed to tackle economic imbalances and financial weaknesses underlying the present turmoil . </s>
<s> mr tsang stressed : </s>
<s> " here in hong_kong , our economy is not unbalanced , our finances are not weak : </s>
<s> hong_kong is here for the long term as a centre to serve the stable and sustained growth of the region . " </s>
<s> he added that hong_kong would do its share , </s>
<s> as a responsible partner in the regional economy , in international measures for financial and economic co @-@ operation to cope with the present difficulties . </s>
<s> turning to the 1998 / 99 budget , </s>
<s> the financial secretary said he was aware that there was concern in some quarters about the substantial amount of money the government was going to spend over the next few years for funding the various initiatives in the chief executive 's policy address . </s>
<s> " let me make it crystal clear that we are not going to depart from our prudent fiscal policy . </s>
<s> we can accommodate all the initiatives announced by the chief executive in the 1997 policy address and in the related policy programmes within the level of expenditure permitted under our budgetary guideline . </s>
<s> " that budgetary guideline enables us to raise public spending over our medium range forecast period by five per cent annually in real terms . " </s>
<s> stressing that the government was particularly vigilant in control of recurrent government spending , </s>
<s> mr tsang said the estimated increase in spending of $ 7.7 billion in the next financial year , to implement the programme announced in the chief executive 's policy address , represented five per cent real growth . </s>
<s> overall capital spending of $ 88 billion for the new initiatives was likewise clearly affordable , </s>
<s> against total expenditure of about $ 50 billion in the current financial year , he added . </s>
<s> he assured the investment fund managers that the government would be able to make these investments without overloading the budget . </s>
<s> on hong_kong 's position as a premier financial centre , mr tsang said this would be strengthened by increasing training , </s>
<s> by greatly improved financial communications infrastructure ; and above all that , by maintaining the rule of law , </s>
<s> freedom of information , low , simple and predictable tax rates and open markets . </s>
<s> those were the things which gave everyone a level playing field on which to make sensible investment decisions , mr tsang added . </s>
<s> he also told the fund managers that the clear commitment to continued financial and economic reform in mainland china , set out at the 15 th party congress , </s>
<s> meant that hong_kong 's pivotal role as the best place for mainland enterprises to raise capital would develop firmly in the years ahead . </s>
<s> in his concluding remarks , </s>
<s> mr tsang said hong_kong had passed through the watershed of 1997 with strong reserves , with healthy economic fundamentals , </s>
<s> with continuity of prudent fiscal management and with enduring opportunity . </s>
<s> " today , and no doubt from time to time in years to come , </s>
<s> we face challenges and difficult days , days when steady nerves are needed . </s>
<s> " and when the clouds pass , as they will , we have the abundant and refreshing potential of free markets , </s>
<s> operating under the rule of law , to carry us on , </s>
<s> " mr tsang said . </s>
<s> joint effort to combat indecent materials on the internet </s>
<s> the sar government and the hong_kong internet service providers association ( hkispa ) jointly announced today ( monday ) the promulgation of a code of practice and practice statement dealing with indecent and obscene materials transmitted on the internet . </s>
<s> this is part of the government 's initiatives to address the community 's concern over the accessibility of indecent and obscene articles on the internet by children and young persons , the commissioner for television and entertainment licensing authority ( tela ) , mr eddy chan , </s>
<s> he said : " the code of practice is the result of many months of hardwork by the government and the hkispa . </s>
<s> the adoption of a self @-@ regulatory code of practice and practice statement achieves the balance of maintaining the free flow of information on the one hand and safeguarding the interests of our young people on the other . " </s>
<s> the code provides detailed guidelines and procedures in dealing with complaints relating to the transmission of obscene and indecent materials through the internet . </s>
<s> " we will keep in view the implementation and effectiveness of the code with the hkispa and review it in a year 's time , </s>
<s> " he said . </s>
<s> in addition to the promulgation of the code , the tela has launched a series of publicity and public education programmes , including tv / radio apis , </s>
<s> leaflets and a list of filtering software to help parents exercise guidance . </s>
<s> these publicity leaflets have been distributed to the internet users through the internet service providers . </s>
<s> the education department has also issued guidelines to schools on the proper use of the internet . </s>
<s> a list of filtering softwares is posted on the home pages of tela , the education department and the hkispa in a concerted effort . </s>
<s> consultancy study on planning and development in nw nt </s>
<s> the planning department ( pd ) and the territory development department ( tdd ) have today ( monday ) jointly commissioned a consultancy study to examine the scope and feasibility of accommodating strategic growth developments in the northwest of the new territories . </s>
<s> the " planning and development study on north west new territories " will be carried out in two stages under the concerted management of the two departments . </s>
<s> the first stage will be on planning and be led by the pd while the second stage will be on engineering and site investigation and headed by the tdd . </s>
<s> the study is one of the three integrated planning and engineering studies featured in the 1997 policy address , and is a positive step towards meeting the chief executive 's target of producing 85,000 flats a year . </s>
<s> it will also include engineering investigations on the developments and infrastructure required in the area to accommodate an additional population of 100,000 over the next 10 years and another 100,000 in the following five years . </s>
<s> the study will adopt a completely new approach to allow the planning and engineering assessments to be carried out concurrently as an iterative process thus cuts the development process by one to two years . </s>
<s> the study is due for completion by early 2000 at a cost of $ 55.7 million . </s>
<s> an agreement was signed today between the project manager of the territory development department 's new territories north development office , mr che ping @-@ doon , and a representative from the consultancy firm -- binnie consultants limited . </s>
<s> the recommended outline development plan will be completed possibly by the end of next year and the relevant district boards will be consulted on the recommendations . </s>
<s> detailed engineering design and construction works will follow after the completion of the study . </s>
