<s> provisional statistics of retail sales for august 1997 </s>
<s> the value of total retail sales in august 1997 , </s>
<s> estimated at $ 20.6 billion , increased by 8 % when compared with august 1996 , according to the provisional figures on retail sales released today ( monday ) by the census and statistics department . </s>
<s> after discounting the effect of price changes over the period , total retail sales increased by 3 % in volume . </s>
<s> compared with a year ago , sales of motor vehicles continued to record a robust increase , by 58 % in value and 59 % in volume . </s>
<s> sales of other consumer durable goods also increased significantly , by 11 % in both value and volume . </s>
<s> concurrently , sales in other types of outlets recorded increases of various magnitudes in both value and volume . sales in these outlets included jewellery , </s>
<s> watches and clocks and valuable gifts ( 4 % in value and 7 % in volume ) ; food , alcoholic drinks and tobacco ( 12 % in value and 5 % in volume ) and miscellaneous consumer goods ( 8 % in value and 1 % in volume ) . </s>
<s> sales in supermarkets increased by 11 % in value and 2 % in volume . </s>
<s> sales of fuels grew by 8 % in value , but remained virtually unchanged in volume . </s>
<s> meanwhile , sales of clothing and footwear showed no apparent change in value , but registered a decline of 8 % in volume . </s>
<s> sales in department stores decreased by 4 % in value and 11 % in volume . </s>
<s> compared with july 1997 ( this comparison is affected by seasonal factors ) , total retail sales in august 1997 increased by 1 % in value and 2 % in volume . </s>
<s> comparing the period from january to august 1997 with the same period in 1996 , total retail sales rose by 8 % in value and 3 % in volume . </s>
<s> the relevant components of the consumer price index are used as deflators . starting from the reference month of january 1997 , a new series of value and volume indices reflecting changes in the combined sales of supermarkets and supermarkets operating in department stores was compiled . </s>
<s> the report containing the analysis of the august 1997 results is now on sale at $ 3.00 per copy at the government publications centre , ground floor , low block , </s>
<s> queensway government offices , 66 queensway ; and the publications unit of the census and statistics department , 19 th floor , wanchai tower , </s>
<s> 12 harbour road , wan chai . </s>
<s> enquiries about the survey results may be directed to the wholesale and retail trade statistics section of the census and statistics department ( tel no : 2802 1258 ) . </s>
