<s> sar government response to moody 's rating </s>
<s> in response to media enquiries concerning the revised rating outlook for hong_kong banks , a sar government spokesman today ( thursday ) made the following remarks : </s>
<s> " moody 's comments reflect the more difficult operating environment caused by the recent turmoil in both regional and global financial markets . </s>
<s> despite this , the hong_kong banking sector is well @-@ capitalised and robust because : - </s>
<s> * profitability in the first half of the year was very good and this provides the banks with a cushion in today 's more difficult conditions ; </s>
<s> * bad debts are at very low levels and asset quality has improved further during this year ; </s>
<s> * in particular , the loan loss experience on residential mortgages which are the main component of property lending in hong_kong is </s>
<s> banks in hong_kong suffered virtually no defaults on their mortgage lending during the 1994 / 95 downturn in the property market . </s>
<s> they should therefore be well placed to deal with an adjustment in property prices , should that occur . " </s>
<s> monetary statistics for september 1997 </s>
<s> according to statistics published today ( thursday ) by the hong_kong monetary authority , total deposits and loans and advances rose during september 1997 . </s>
<s> table 1 gives a summary and comparisons with earlier months . </s>
<s> deposits </s>
<s> total deposits rose by 2.0 per cent in september , reversing a 0.8 per cent drop in august . </s>
<s> hong_kong dollar ( hk $ ) deposits and foreign currency deposits increased by 1.7 per cent and 2.5 per cent respectively . </s>
<s> during the month , demand deposits grew by 2 per cent , having fallen by 5.8 per cent in august . </s>
<s> savings deposits declined further by 4.1 per cent in september , having decreased by 2.8 per cent in the previous month . </s>
<s> time deposits increased by 3.6 per cent , reversing a drop of 0.5 per cent in august . </s>
<s> the rise in time deposits may be partly due to a shift from savings deposits to time deposits , as banks offered higher time deposit rates in response to higher interbank rates . </s>
<s> the placement of money with banks for new share subscription on or before the refund dates also contributed to the rise in time deposits . </s>
<s> both us dollar ( us $ ) and non @-@ us $ foreign currency deposits grew in september . </s>
<s> us $ deposits rose by 2.4 per cent , following an increase of 0.5 per cent in august , </s>
<s> while non @-@ us $ foreign currency deposits rebounded by 2.6 per cent , after declining for three consecutive months . </s>
<s> as a whole , foreign currency deposits recorded a 2.5 per cent rise in september . </s>
<s> loans and advances </s>
<s> total loans and advances rose by 0.8 per cent in september , after falling by 0.6 per cent and 0.4 per cent in july and august respectively . </s>
<s> during the month , domestic credit expanded sharply by 3.8 per cent , </s>
<s> with a rise of 4.2 per cent in other loans for use in hong_kong more than offsetting a small decline of 0.4 per cent in loans for trade financing . </s>
<s> meanwhile , offshore loans fell further by 2.3 per cent , having decreased by 1.5 per cent in the previous month . </s>
<s> hk $ loans expanded by 4.1 per cent while foreign currency loans fell by 1.4 per cent . </s>
<s> as the increase in hk $ loans was larger than that of hk $ deposits , the hk $ loan @-@ to - deposit ratio rose to 112.1 per cent at end @-@ september , from 109.6 per cent at end @-@ august . </s>
<s> quarterly analysis of loans for use in hong_kong by major economic sector </s>
<s> during the september quarter , domestic credit expanded rapidly , albeit at a slower rate than in the june quarter . </s>
<s> residential mortgage loans surged further by 9.0 per cent during the quarter , </s>
<s> and loans to stock @-@ brokers increased substantially by 106.2 per cent , partly due to new share subscriptions . </s>
<s> on the other hand , loans to the manufacturing sector and to the wholesale and retail trades fell by 3.1 per cent and 2.2 per cent respectively . </s>
<s> the growth of loans for building , construction and property development moderated to 4.3 per cent , from 11.3 per cent in the previous quarter . </s>
<s> money supply </s>
<s> hong_kong dollar money supply rose in september across @-@ the @-@ board , with hk $ m 1 increasing by 1.8 per cent and hk $ m 2 and hk $ m 3 rising by 1.7 per cent . </s>
<s> in the 12 months to september , hk $ m 1 , hk $ m 2 and hk $ m 3 rose by 9.2 per cent , </s>
<s> 21.7 per cent and 21.6 per cent respectively . </s>
<s> the annual growth in broad monetary aggregates continued to outpace that of nominal gdp . </s>
<s> plea for information on illicit fuel activities </s>
<s> the assistant commissioner of customs and excise ( administration and excise ) , mr ronald au yee @-@ leung , today ( thursday ) appealed to members of the public for more information on illicit fuel activities . </s>
<s> speaking at a signing ceremony to renew the oil industry reward scheme for another year effective from this month , </s>
<s> mr au stressed that the department was determined to repress all kinds of illicit fuel activities . </s>
<s> the reward scheme , financed by caltex , crpc , esso , </s>
<s> mobil and shell , was first launched on april 1 , 1996 to encourage the public to give information on illicit fuel activities . </s>
<s> " as before , </s>
<s> the five oil companies will contribute a total of $ 1 million to pay rewards ranging from $ 3,000 to $ 140,000 to any person who provides information leading to seizure and forfeiture of illicit fuel and conviction of persons involved , </s>
<s> " mr au said . </s>
<s> over the past 18 months , </s>
<s> based on information received under this scheme , the hong_kong customs and excise department has seized 251,050 litres of illicit fuel and arrested 16 people with a total reward of $ 140,000 being paid out . </s>
<s> " to further promote the scheme , </s>
<s> the five oil companies also sponsor the publication of a poster and a leaflet to enhance the public awareness on the serious consequence of involving in illicit fuel activities , " he noted . </s>
<s> copies of the leaflet are available for public collection at all customs offices , district offices and oil filling stations . </s>
<s> information on any illicit fuel activities can be passed to the department by : </s>
<s> ( a ) calling : 2545 6182 ( 24 hours ) ; </s>
<s> ( b ) fax : 2543 4962 ( 24 hours ) ; </s>
<s> ( c ) letter to the department , gpo box 1166 ; or </s>
<s> ( d ) reporting in person at any customs offices . </s>
<s> the transport department has recently arranged to disseminate real time pictures free of charge from its closed circuit television ( cctv ) system to local electronic media . </s>
<s> the main objective of the arrangement is to strengthen the provision of traffic information to the public . </s>
<s> speaking on the new scheme , a spokesman for the department said : </s>
<s> " television and radio stations can now receive real time visual signals through the cctv terminals installed in their studio . </s>
<s> " these signals are coming from a total of 75 cctv cameras mounted at various strategic locations on major roads on hong_kong island , kowloon , tsuen wan new town and tuen mun road . </s>
<s> " the new scheme enables the media to follow closely the latest road traffic conditions in these areas and to produce up @-@ to @-@ the - minute traffic bulletin for their audiences . </s>
<s> " moreover , </s>
<s> the media can response instantly to special traffic situations and emergencies and relay the messages immediately to the public . " </s>
<s> at present , </s>
<s> television broadcasts limited ( tvb ) , asia television limited ( atv ) , commercial radio and radio television hong_kong ( rthk ) have joined the scheme . </s>
<s> the two television stations will broadcast some of these pictures live in their traffic news programmes from november this year . </s>
<s> the cost of the new scheme includes $ 100,000 for installation works and $ 400,000 for annual rental of video transmission circuits from hongkong telecom . </s>
<s> the cctv system is a supplement to the operation of the area traffic control ( atc ) system which enables the department to monitor closely the road traffic conditions so as to achieve a flexible and effective traffic control within the territory . </s>
<s> energy advisory committee meeting </s>
<s> two draft codes of practice on energy efficiency of lighting installations as well as of air conditioning installations were endorsed by the energy advisory committee at a meeting today ( thursday ) . </s>
<s> the two codes are part of a comprehensive set of building energy codes that the government is developing . </s>
<s> the objective of the codes is to improve energy efficiency through the design of buildings , their building services and their electrical and mechanical installations . </s>
<s> the code of practice for energy efficiency of lighting installations sets out the minimum requirements for achieving energy @-@ efficient lighting installations and applies only to fixed lighting installations in indoor spaces . </s>
<s> the code adopts a prescriptive control approach by which energy efficiency requirements are quantified in terms of definite values . </s>
<s> the code of practice for energy efficiency of air @-@ conditioning installations sets out the minimum requirements for achieving energy @-@ efficient design of air @-@ conditioning installations in buildings which specifies design parameters and control criteria for air @-@ conditioning installations and minimum coefficient of performance for air @-@ conditioning equipment . </s>
<s> both codes are considered to be achievable in hong_kong and will be reviewed periodically . the codes will be implemented in 1998 on a voluntary basis . </s>
<s> members also discussed the energy policy in hong_kong during today 's meeting . </s>
<s> topics covered included security of supply , safety , regulatory environment and competition as well as the measures to promote efficient use of energy and minimisation of environmental impact . </s>
<s> members were briefed on the second asia @-@ pacific economic co @-@ operation ( apec ) energy ministers meeting ( emm ) , which was held in edmonton , canada in august 1997 . </s>
<s> the overall theme of the second apec emm was " energy : infrastructure for sustainable development " . </s>
<s> the energy advisory committee , which is chaired by professor charles kao kuen , </s>
<s> advises the government on energy policy matters , including energy efficiency and conservation . </s>
<s> a garment manufacturer was today ( thursday ) fined $ 921,800 at tsuen wan magistracy after pleading guilty to five counts of making a false statement regarding manufacturer of goods in export licence application . </s>
<s> the goods involved were some 5,000 dozens of lady knitted dresses worth about $ 4.3 million . </s>
<s> the court heard that in october 1995 , katal knitting factory limited submitted five applications for export licences covering the goods for export to the united_states . in each of the applications , </s>
<s> the factory declared itself as the manufacturer of the goods . </s>
<s> investigations by officers of the customs and excise department revealed that the declaration made by the factory in the five export licence applications was untrue . the factory had in fact subcontracted the knitting process to local factories . </s>
<s> in order to obtain the export licences to facilitate the export of the goods , the factory falsely declared in the export licence applications that it was the manufacturer of the goods . </s>
<s> a spokesman for the customs and excise department said the offences were serious . </s>
<s> officers of the department would step up their enforcement actions to track down such malpractice to protect the commercial reputation of hong_kong and to ensure that the confidence of its trading partners in hong_kong 's textiles control system would not be undermined by some dishonest businessmen , the spokesman added . </s>
<s> the maximum penalty for making a false statement in an export licence application is a fine of $ 500,000 plus two years imprisonment . </s>
<s> members of the public having information on any suspected illegal textile transhipment activities could call the hotline 2804 2388 . </s>
<s> textiles traders who encounter licensing problems in respect of markets in the united_states and canada are welcome to discuss their issues with experienced officers of the trade department 's customer service centre starting next monday ( november 3 ) . </s>
<s> a spokesman for the trade department said today ( thursday ) that the establishment of the customer service centre in the textiles control branch of the asia and americas division was part of the department 's on @-@ going efforts to further enhancing its standard of services to traders . </s>
<s> the centre is headed by a customer service manager and manned by a team of four customer service officers who are knowledgeable in answering enquiries and handling requests for special services on licensing matters . </s>
<s> the three major areas of services to be provided by the centre in respect of both the usa and canada markets are as follows : </s>
<s> * enquiries on general licensing matters ; </s>
<s> * requests for special licensing / enquiry services ; </s>
<s> * suggestions from customers . </s>
<s> the main types of special licensing and enquiry services to be handled by the centre are as follows : </s>
<s> * issue of certified true copy of export licence ; </s>
<s> * enquiries on quota allocation ; </s>
<s> * enquiries on status of export licence application due for issue ; </s>
<s> * expeditious issue and amendment of export licence ; </s>
<s> * instant approval service for restrained export licence application covering sample shipment ; </s>
<s> * assistance for textile consignments that encounter customs clearance problems at the importing end ; </s>
<s> * issue of export licence on a retrospective basis ; </s>
<s> * quota reclaim ; and </s>
<s> * issue of replacement visa for lost export visa in respect of the usa market . </s>
<s> the centre is located at the textiles licensing office of the branch on the second floor of the trade department tower , 700 nathan road , kowloon . </s>
<s> its operating hours are as follows : </s>
<s> saturday 9 am - 12.30 pm </s>
<s> the spokesman reminded traders that the licensing and enquiry services currently provided at counters numbers 12 @-@ 20 of the americas textiles controls branch will be suspended as from november 3 ( monday ) . </s>
<s> for further enquiries on the operation and scope of services of the centre , </s>
<s> please contact the customer service manager , mr simon chan , on 2398 5418 . </s>
<s> external trade figures for september 1997 </s>
<s> the value of hong_kong 's domestic exports and imports in september 1997 increased over a year earlier , </s>
<s> while that of re @-@ exports showed virtually no change . these are shown in the external trade figures for september 1997 released today ( thursday ) by the census and statistics department . </s>
<s> the value of total exports ( comprising re @-@ exports and domestic exports ) in september 1997 increased slightly by 0.6 per cent over a year earlier to $ 126.9 billion . </s>
<s> within this total , the value of re @-@ exports , </s>
<s> at $ 107.8 billion , was virtually unchanged from a year earlier , while the value of domestic exports increased by 4.2 per cent to $ 19.0 billion . </s>
<s> the value of imports increased by 1.9 per cent over a year earlier to $ 133.2 billion in september 1997 . </s>
<s> as the value of total exports in september 1997 was smaller than that of total imports , a visible trade deficit of $ 6.3 billion , </s>
<s> equivalent to 4.8 per cent of the value of imports , was recorded . </s>
<s> this was larger than the corresponding deficit of $ 4.6 billion , equivalent to 3.5 % of the value of imports , in september 1996 . </s>
<s> for the first nine months of 1997 as a whole , the value of total exports increased by 3.0 per cent over the same period last year . </s>
<s> within this total , the value of re @-@ exports rose by 3.7 per cent while the value of domestic exports decreased by 1.2 per cent . </s>
<s> the value of imports had an increase of 5.0 per cent . </s>
<s> for the first nine months of 1997 combined , </s>
<s> a visible trade deficit of $ 127.5 billion , equivalent to 11 per cent of the value of imports , was recorded . </s>
<s> a government secretariat spokesman noted that hong_kong 's domestic exports had shown signs of bottoming out in recent months . </s>
<s> for the first time since the fourth quarter of 1995 , the value of domestic exports registered an increase , by 2.8 per cent in the third quarter of 1997 over a year earlier . </s>
<s> as domestic export prices had been on an easing trend , domestic exports could have risen by around 6 per cent in real terms in the third quarter over a year earlier . </s>
<s> the spokesman also noted that , after allowing for the continued easing in re @-@ export prices , re @-@ exports could have risen by around 4 per cent in real terms in the third quarter over a year earlier . </s>
<s> hong_kong 's re @-@ export performance was being influenced by the structural shift to offshore trading , involving increasingly direct shipment from the mainland . </s>
<s> although this could not be revealed from the merchandise trade statistics , hong_kong 's exports of services should have benefited . </s>
<s> also likely to have been boosted were hong_kong 's income inflows from related industrial investment ventures in the mainland . </s>
<s> the spokesman further observed that the visible trade deficit had been narrowing in recent months . </s>
<s> the ratio of deficit to the total value of imports came down substantially from 17.6 per cent in march to 9.5 per cent in july , </s>
<s> 7.4 per cent in august , and further to 4.8 per cent in september . </s>
<s> a more detailed analysis of hong_kong 's external trade for september 1997 , by commodity and country , will be released in mid @-@ november 1997 . </s>
