<s> aids situation in 3 rd quarter this year </s>
<s> a total of 52 persons were found to be positive for the hiv antibody test in the third quarter this year , bringing the cumulative total number of reported hiv infections to 907 , </s>
<s> the department of health announced today ( friday ) . </s>
<s> the number of new hiv infections reported in the third quarter is the highest ever received in a single quarter since the surveillance system was established in 1984 . </s>
<s> sixteen aids cases were reported in the same period leading to a total number of 290 confirmed cases . </s>
<s> for this quarter , the ratio of reported male to female hiv infections is three to one . </s>
<s> ninety percent acquired the infection via sexual contact . </s>
<s> routes of transmission of the 907 hiv infected are : 473 through heterosexual and 271 through homosexual or bisexual sex ; 16 were injecting drug users ; </s>
<s> four were mother @-@ to @-@ child transmission around the time of birth ; and 67 acquired the infection through contaminated blood or blood products . </s>
<s> as for the remaining 76 , the information available was inadequate for classification . </s>
<s> report of helicopter accident in march 1996 published </s>
<s> the hong_kong special administrative region government today ( friday ) published the report of the investigation into a helicopter accident that happened in tai lam country park on march 16 , 1996 . </s>
<s> the accident involved an aerospatiale sa 315 b lama helicopter carrying out power line stringing between electricity pylons . </s>
<s> the aircraft was substantially damaged after the accident . </s>
<s> the pilot sustained serious injury but there was no injury to the persons working on the ground or on the pylon . </s>
<s> the investigation was conducted by the civil aviation department . the objective of the investigation is to identify the cause of the accident and prevent future recurrence . </s>
<s> the report contains an analysis of the circumstances surrounding the accident , together with conclusions and recommendations . </s>
<s> five recommendations were made in the report and they were addressed to the operator of the crashed helicopter , heliservices ( hong_kong ) limited to take remedial measures as necessary . </s>
<s> copies of the report are for sale at the government publications centre , ground floor , lower block , queensway government offices , 66 queensway , hong_kong . </s>
<s> draft cheung sha wan outline zoning plan approved </s>
<s> the chief executive in council has approved the draft cheung sha wan outline zoning plan ( ozp ) to provide a statutory land use framework for the development and redevelopment within the area . </s>
<s> the ozp covers a total land area of about 341 hectares . </s>
<s> upon full development , the district is expected to have a population of 203 400 , </s>
<s> 40 per cent accommodated in public housing and 60 per cent in private housing . </s>
<s> about 77.7 hectares of land , or 22.8 per cent of the total area , </s>
<s> has been zoned " residential ( group a ) " for high @-@ density residential developments , while another 0.6 hectares at tai po road , </s>
<s> or 0.2 per cent of the total area , has been zoned " residential ( group c ) " for low @-@ rise , low @-@ density residential developments . </s>
<s> meanwhile , three sites covering about five hectares , </s>
<s> or 1.5 per cent of the total area , have been zoned " comprehensive development area " ( cda ) . </s>
<s> the two cdas , at tai po road , are intended for low @-@ density residential uses , </s>
<s> while the other located to the south of lai chi kok road , covering the disused cheung sha wan shipyards , </s>
<s> is intended for hotel , commercial and residential uses . </s>
<s> about 43.2 hectares , or 12.7 per cent of the total area , </s>
<s> have been zoned " government / institution / community " ( gic ) for the development of facilities to serve local residents . </s>
<s> police stations , a fire station , an ambulance depot , an abattoir , a vegetable wholesale market , an indoor games hall and urban council complexes , and a number of schools . </s>
<s> about 31.3 hectares , or 9.2 per cent of the total area , have been zoned " industrial " . </s>
<s> this covers the existing factory buildings and is intended for general industrial uses , service trades and warehouses . </s>
<s> the cheung sha wan industrial area located to the west of hing wah street and the industrial sites at tonkin street and lai chi kok road are within this zone . </s>
<s> about 56.9 hectares , or 16.7 per cent of the total area , </s>
<s> have been zoned " green belt " for the preservation of the natural landscape . </s>
<s> it covers mainly the wooded foothills to the north of ching cheung road and tai po road which provides a green backdrop to the area . </s>
<s> about 27.4 hectares , or eight per cent of the total area , </s>
<s> have been zoned " open space " to provide for active and passive recreational uses . </s>
<s> the tung chau street park , sham shui po park , cheung sha wan playground , sham shui po sports ground , maple street playground , and po on road playground are within this zone . </s>
<s> about 9.4 hectares , or 2.8 per cent of the total area , have been zoned " other specified uses " . </s>
<s> these include the cheung sha wan roman catholic cemetery , two petrol filling stations and two multi @-@ storey car / lorry parks . </s>
<s> the remaining 89.5 hectares of land , or 26.2 per cent of the total area , has been reserved for road and other related uses . </s>
<s> the approved ozp no. s / k 5 / 13 is available for public inspection during office hours at : </s>
<s> * planning department , 16 th floor , murray building , garden road , central , </s>
<s> * sham shui po district office , 6 th floor , west coast international building , 290 un chau street , </s>
<s> copies of the draft plan are on sale at the survey and mapping office , lands department , 14 th floor , murray building , garden road , hong_kong and the kowloon map sales office , ground floor , </s>
