<s> no question of hk breaching ilcs </s>
<s> in response to a number of press enquiries on a complaint with the international labour organisation ( ilo ) against the government over the repeal of two labour laws , a spokesman for the education and manpower bureau reiterated today ( saturday ) that there was no question of hong_kong breaching the international labour conventions applicable to hong_kong . </s>
<s> he said : </s>
<s> we report regularly to the ilo on the application of these two and other conventions which hong_kong has applied . " </s>
<s> in respect of collective bargaining , </s>
<s> the spokesman said that ilo in its own publication " freedom of association " categorically stated that " nothing in article 4 of ilc no. 98 places a duty on the government to enforce collective bargaining by compulsory means with a given organisation ; </s>
<s> such an intervention would clearly alter the nature of bargaining . " </s>
<s> rat prevention campaign launched </s>
<s> the department of health is now launching a territory @-@ wide education campaign to remind the public of the importance of rat prevention and to provide them with some basic rat prevention knowledge . </s>
<s> a spokesman for the department said today ( saturday ) that the campaign , </s>
<s> bearing the theme " a clean environment prevents rats " , was organised with sponsorship of the provisional urban council and the provisional regional council . </s>
<s> " besides , </s>
<s> rats can gnaw on home fittings and furniture causing financial loss and may occasionally bite people of lower mobility , </s>
<s> " he said . </s>
<s> the spokesman added that the fundamental method in rodent control was to improve the sanitation of the environment . </s>
<s> he advised the public to take the following precautionary measures to prevent rat infestations : </s>
<s> * keep the premises clean . </s>
<s> store all food properly and put all refuse and food remains into a proper dustbin so as to leave no food for rats . </s>
<s> * seal off any holes on ceilings , walls and floors . </s>
<s> inspect regularly the bottom and back of bulky furniture and concealed places so as to eliminate breeding places for rats promptly . </s>
<s> * keep drain gratings in good repair . </s>
<s> render all ventilation openings rat @-@ proof by installing strong wire nettings with narrow gauges to keep rats away from the premises . </s>
<s> affix metal plates to the lower part of wooden doors to keep away rats . </s>
<s> during the campaign period , </s>
<s> printed educational handouts such as posters , advisory letters and leaflets will be distributed to building management offices , incorporated owners and mutual aid committees to appeal for their co @-@ operation in implementing rat prevention measures . </s>
<s> the printed materials will also be sent to the district environmental health offices of the urban services department and the regional services department , district offices of the home affairs department , the housing department and the education department for wider publicity . </s>
<s> members of the public can also make use of the 24 @-@ hour hotline 2380 2580 to listen to rat prevention messages in the form of a drama and to obtain the information through facsimile . </s>
<s> further advice or assistance on rat prevention can be obtained from the pest control units of the respective district environmental health offices of the two municipal services departments . </s>
<s> parents reminded to bring children for measles vaccination </s>
<s> the department of health today ( sunday ) reminded parents to bring their one to five @-@ year @-@ old children to any general out @-@ patient clinics ( gopcs ) or maternal and children health centres ( mchcs ) for measles vaccination before the current special measles vaccination campaign ends on november 15 . </s>
<s> since the vaccination campaign started on september 8 specifically for children between one and five , about 200,000 children have been vaccinated , representing 52 per cent of this age group . </s>
<s> " it is important that those who have not come forward for the vaccination , should do so early to avoid last @-@ minute rush , </s>
<s> " a spokesman for the department said . </s>
<s> although most children in hong_kong have received their first dose of vaccine when they are one year old , a second dose will serve to enhance their immunity , the spokesman explained . </s>
<s> " the vaccine is safe , effective and free , </s>
<s> and can be received four weeks after the first one , " he emphasised . </s>
<s> the spokesman warned that measles is an acute communicable disease which can lead to complications such as chest infection , middle ear infection , </s>
<s> infection of the brain or even death . </s>
<s> " the measles , mumps and rubella ( mmr ) vaccine or anti @-@ measles vaccine ( amv ) offers very good protection against the disease , </s>
<s> " he added . </s>
<s> in the meantime , health staff of the department have been visiting primary schools to vaccinate children between the age of six and 11. some 330,000 pupils have been covered , </s>
<s> representing 71 per cent of this age group . </s>
<s> the spokesman noted that during the last vaccination exercise for people between 12 and 19 , a total of 420,000 youngsters were covered , </s>
<s> representing 72 per cent of this age group . those who have missed the last exercise for various reasons can still go to any gopcs or mchcs for vaccination before november 15 . </s>
<s> " most clinics now allow walk @-@ in vaccinations . prior appointment may not be necessary . </s>
<s> " do take advantage of the last two weeks to give your children maximum protection against measles , </s>
<s> " the spokesman added . </s>
<s> for enquiries , members of the public can call the special measles vaccination campaign hotlines 2833 0111 and 2591 6330 . </s>
<s> code of practice for lift and escalators work issued </s>
<s> the labour department has issued the code of practice for safety at work ( lift and escalator ) for the purpose of providing practical guidance on the general duties provisions of the factory and industrial undertakings ordinance in relation to performing lift or escalator works . </s>
<s> chief factory inspector ( operations ) , mr tse ming @-@ sing , </s>
<s> said today ( sunday ) that the code recommended safe systems of work for those proprietors or contractors to ensure the safety and health of their employees in the installation , maintenance and repair of lifts or escalators . </s>
<s> " a safe and healthy working environment for those employed in the industry will be assured by complying with the code , </s>
<s> thus accidents and ill @-@ health arising from the work can avoided , " mr tse said . </s>
<s> he added that the safety of persons engaged in lift or escalator work was the responsibility of the proprietors or contractors , the supervisors and the persons physically carrying out work on lifts or escalators . </s>
<s> " all persons working on lifts or escalators are expected to take due care of themselves and other , </s>
<s> " he added . </s>
<s> " they should also pay attention to potential hazards , make proper use of safeguards provided and follow closely defined safe working procedures . " </s>
<s> both the chinese and english versions of the code can be obtained from the advisory and development division , occupational safety and health branch ( oshb ) , labour department , 14 th floor , harbour building , 38 pier road , </s>
<s> central or any building , engineering and construction divisional offices of the oshb . </s>
<s> enquiries about the code can be made to the advisory and development division on 2854 9645 . </s>
<s> tourists can literally have at their fingertips the latest information on hotels , restaurants , </s>
<s> shopping and scenic spots in town when a computerised map enquiry system is in place early next year . </s>
<s> a spokesman for the lands department said today ( sunday ) that the system would integrate advanced internet map technology to provide a high technology tourism facility in hong_kong . </s>
<s> " a number of display kiosks will be installed at popular tourist locations such as mass transit railway stations and the airport , </s>
<s> " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> " inside the kiosk will be a computer terminal . through a digital location map on the screen , a tourist can gain access to a wealth of information including sightseeing , </s>
<s> shopping , hotel and dining services , " he added . </s>
<s> unlike the traditional maps , the system will also furnish an enquirer with interesting photographs and videos relating to the selected places or events . </s>
<s> for instance , </s>
<s> a tourist enquiring about dining facilities nearby needs only to touch a few screen buttons and a location map with restaurants will pop up . </s>
<s> a next touch on any one of the restaurants will give the tourist additional information about that restaurant . it will even connect him to the internet homepage of the restaurant if there is one . </s>
<s> " a useful feature is the link @-@ up with the wondernet website of the hong_kong tourist association from which hotel room rates and facilities can be retrieved and reservation made , </s>
<s> " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> the map will also be able to perform some intelligent geographical search of special facilities such as post offices , police stations , </s>
<s> and shopping places within a five @-@ minute walk from where the tourist is . </s>
<s> a convenient travelling route to the destination will also be suggested . </s>
<s> " the tourist information will be available to all internet users worldwide . this will certainly be of interest to prospective tourists and help them plan their sightseeing routes before arriving in hong_kong , </s>
<s> " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> while the system is targeted primarily at tourists , it will also be available for use by the general public . </s>
<s> funded by the hong_kong jockey club charities trust , the two @-@ million @-@ dollar system will be set up by the survey and mapping office ( smo ) of the lands department with the assistance of the hong_kong tourist association . </s>
<s> the smo will regularly update the data bank to take account of the rapid changing relief and topography of land . </s>
<s> tenders are being invited for the setting up of the system . the works are expected to begin in january for completion in march next year . </s>
<s> quality assurance in school education </s>
<s> the education department is going to launch the first phase of quality assurance inspection on a number of secondary , primary and special schools next year . quality assurance inspection will take the form of whole @-@ school inspection . </s>
<s> under the new approach , efforts on inspections within the department can be more focused and co @-@ ordinated . </s>
<s> it can also provide schools with a more comprehensive view on their strengths and weaknesses for improvement and development . </s>
<s> since schools can have access to inspection reports , the new mode of inspection is expected to become a more transparent and accountable quality assurance mechanism . </s>
<s> major aspects of the schools ' operation within a specified time will be looked into during whole @-@ school inspection . </s>
<s> they include administration and management , curriculum provision , teaching and learning processes , caring system , support services , quality assurance mechanism , accommodation , </s>
<s> the aim is to provide an impartial outside view of the quality of the inspected school . furthermore , </s>
<s> procedures and quality indicators to all schools as a base for self @-@ evaluation and improvement can also be established . </s>
<s> the government and members of the public will have a clear picture of the current situation regarding quality of school education . </s>
<s> the ultimate aim is to activate schools ' initiatives in their pursuit of quality education , and inspection by the department can become a catalyst for their success . </s>
<s> comprising education officers and inspectors from various divisions of the department , and front @-@ liners including principals and teachers , was formed in september to prepare for the implementation of the new mode of inspection . </s>
<s> team members will receive further training to equip with skills and techniques to undertake quality assurance inspection . </s>
<s> to promote understanding and support of quality assurance inspection among key players in education , the education department is going to organise a number of consultation sessions next month ( december ) . </s>
<s> govt response to consumer council competition policy report </s>
<s> the government today ( monday ) published a response to the consumer council 's competition policy report . </s>
<s> announcing the government response , the secretary for trade and industry , miss denise yue , said : </s>
<s> " we are committed to promoting competition . </s>
<s> we see this not so much as an end in itself , but a means to enhance economic efficiency . " </s>
<s> " we are pleased to take on board the consumer council 's recommendation that we should apply competition policy in a more transparent , consistent and comprehensive manner . </s>
<s> we will formulate a specific policy statement on the objectives of promoting competition and provide some pointers for government departments and bureaux to follow . </s>
<s> we will require all units within government to give due regard to the competition angle in major policy considerations and to submit new initiatives for promoting competition . </s>
<s> " this is necessary because we would like the government to play an exemplary and proactive role in promoting competition wherever practicable . </s>
<s> the financial secretary will chair a competition policy advisory group ( compag ) to provide a dedicated forum for reviewing policy matters on competition . </s>
<s> we will invite experts to attend compag on a need basis . </s>
<s> " to complement the government 's efforts , </s>
<s> we will invite the consumer council to continue to monitor and review trade practices in the private sector and to make recommendations to the government as appropriate . we will urge the council to assist businesses to establish pro @-@ competition code of practices , " miss yue said . </s>
<s> miss yue said : </s>
<s> " we do not agree with the consumer council 's proposal to enact an all @-@ embracing competition law . </s>
<s> perhaps the difference is one of emphasis . " </s>
<s> " we prefer to encourage businesses to self @-@ regulate . this is more in line with our free and open trade and minimum government intervention principles . </s>
<s> we also prefer to take into account the special requirements of individual sectors before we regulate . </s>
<s> it is not realistic to assume that a general competition law can be a substitute for sector @-@ specific regulations . " the rationale behind and effects of business practices cannot always be pre @-@ judged . </s>
<s> we also doubt if such a piece of general legislation is the most cost @-@ effective way of promoting competition and achieving economic efficiency in hong_kong . also , </s>
<s> the extent of restrictive business practices in hong_kong does not appear to be so pervasive as to merit general outlawing . </s>
<s> " the government is also concerned that an all @-@ embracing competition law would need to be backed by an enforcement agency of a size and scale not necessarily commensurate with the scale of the perceived competition problem in hong_kong . </s>
<s> indeed , </s>
<s> many world @-@ renowned institutes have named hong_kong one of the freest or most competitive economies in the world , despite the absence of a general competition law . </s>
<s> " we are not averse to the use of laws to regulate anti @-@ competitive behaviours . but we would limit these to sectors which have a substantial public interest at stake or which may be more prone to anti @-@ competitive behaviours , " miss yue added . </s>
<s> miss yue thanked the consumer council for producing a most valuable and comprehensive report on the state of competition in hong_kong . </s>
<s> the report with its constructive recommendations had stimulated enlightening discussions in the community regarding the significance of competition and the best approach to enhance it . </s>
<s> in formulating the response , the government has extensively consulted various organisations in the society , including over 110 private organisations and relevant government bureaux and departments . </s>
<s> the majority supports maintaining and sharpening hong_kong 's competitive edge within the existing framework but urges the government to review more carefully the need for and scope of the proposed competition law . </s>
<s> eighth floor , west wing , central government offices , 11 ice house street , hong_kong ( fax no. : </s>
<s> 2869 4420 ) . </s>
<s> lbac briefed on development approval and housing land supply </s>
<s> the land and building advisory committee ( lbac ) was briefed on the results of the review of the development approval process , </s>
<s> the land supply for housing between 1997 / 98 to 2001 / 02 and the flat production forecast in the coming eight years at its meeting today ( monday ) . </s>
<s> the review of the development approval process aimed to shorten and simplify existing approval procedures and achieve better co @-@ ordination among concerned departments and bureaux . </s>
<s> chairman of the committee , professor yeung yue @-@ man , welcomed the recommendations of the review as a move to speed up the approval process and to streamline procedures to facilitate developments . </s>
<s> " the recommendations would improve efficiency of the development approval process and would achieve more certainty and transparency in the process , </s>
<s> " professor yeung said . </s>
<s> on the land supply for housing to meet the chief executive 's pledge to produce not less than 85,000 flats yearly , </s>
<s> professor yeung said that the target should remain unchanged as long @-@ term demand for housing had been established for the next decade . </s>
<s> the committee noted the recommendations of a consultancy study on shopping habits as well as a study of leisure habits and recreation perferences conducted by the planning department . </s>
<s> the studies aim to facilitate the updating of planning guidelines for retail facilities and recreation and open space . </s>
<s> a territory @-@ wide forecasting model and a forward planning retail demand assessment model are recommended for use in forecasting the demand for retail floorspace . </s>
<s> " we agree with the recommendation of the study that retail development should be market driven and that planning intervention should be kept to the minimum necessary , </s>
<s> " professor yeung said . </s>
<s> the study of leisure habits and recreation preferences recommended to bring up the minimum standards of open space provision for the main urban areas from 1.5 square metres to 2 square metres per person . </s>
<s> professor yeung noted that this was in line with the standards used for the new towns although it is lower than the standard elsewhere such as singapore . </s>
<s> " the standard of 2 square metres per person is reasonable for hong_kong given competing demands in land and the needs to increase the quality of life , </s>
<s> " he said . </s>
