<s> announcing this today ( monday ) , the secretary for financial services , </s>
<s> mr rafael hui said the period of mr fan 's appointment would be from november 15 , 1997 to november 14 , 1999 . </s>
<s> under section 5 of the securities and futures commission ordinance , the chief executive shall appoint not less than eight directors of the commission , half of whom shall be non @-@ executive directors . </s>
<s> at present , the commission is served by 10 directors . </s>
<s> the non @-@ executive directors bring an independent view to the management and organisation of the sfc . they are fully involved in its policy development . </s>
