<s> company law reform standing committee issues annual report </s>
<s> the standing committee on company law reform has published its 13 th annual report for the year 1996 / 97 . </s>
<s> the standing committee is tasked to advise the financial secretary on necessary amendments to the company ordinance , the securities ordinance and the protection of investors ordinance to ensure that hong_kong 's company law continues to meet the needs of the business community . </s>
<s> members of the committee are drawn from a wide spectrum , </s>
<s> including lawyers , accountants , company secretaries , businessmen , academics , representatives of government departments and regulatory bodies . </s>
<s> one of the major topics covered in the annual report is the overall review of the companies ordinance . </s>
<s> the government commissioned an independent consultancy in early 1995 and the consultant was invited to brief members of the standing committee on the progress of the review regularly . </s>
<s> a government spokesman said : " the consultant completed his project in march this year and has submitted a wide range of proposals . </s>
<s> " the consultancy report has also been launched for public consultation until end of the year . " during 1996 / 97 , </s>
<s> and the introduction of new provisions to enable the official receiver to contract out insolvency cases to the private sector more efficiently . </s>
<s> " since its establishment in 1984 , the standing committee has made a total of 69 recommendations which involve legislative amendments . </s>
<s> of these , 51 have been implemented and a further five are included in proposals for legislative amendments now being prepared , " the spokesman added . </s>
