<s> on tuen mun wu king morninghope school , </s>
<s> the spokesman assured that the department was aware of the need for improving the facilities of the school and was progressing in that direction as an interim measure . </s>
<s> " a possible site has been identified at area 3 c , tuen mun , </s>
<s> and preliminary project feasibility study will be conducted as soon as the project is approved , " he said . </s>
<s> the spokesman said the department would continue to liaise closely with the schools to work out solutions for improvement during the interim period prior to the completion of the new schools . </s>
<s> in the meantime , the department is conducting a strategic study on special school premises . </s>
<s> lpg taxi pilot scheme to start soon </s>
<s> the liquefied petroleum gas ( lpg ) taxi pilot scheme took a big step forward today ( saturday ) when a group of taxi suppliers and licence holders signed agreements with the government to take part in the year @-@ long trial . </s>
<s> the scheme , part of the government initiatives to cut down emission caused by diesel vehicles , </s>
<s> is scheduled to begin later this month ( november ) . it aims to collect data to demonstrate that lpg taxis are operationally and commercially viable under local condition . </s>
<s> under the agreement , the licencees will make available their taxi licences to support the 30 lpg taxis to be supplied by the motors companies . </s>
<s> during the signing ceremony , deputy director of environmental protection , mr mike stokoe , </s>
<s> signed the agreement on behalf of the government with the taxi licence holders and vehicle suppliers , </s>
<s> and was witnessed by the deputy secretary for planning , environment and lands , mr benjamin tang . </s>
<s> measures to speed up development approval process </s>
<s> the planning department has introduced a number of measures to speed up the development approval process . </s>
<s> " these measures are positive steps towards achieving the chief executive 's target in his 1997 policy address of building at least 85,000 flats a year , </s>
<s> from now on , replies will be given within six weeks upon receipt of the following submissions : </s>
<s> ( i ) certification and deposit of master layout plans for comprehensive development areas approved by the town planning board ( tpb ) under section 4 a ( 3 ) of the town planning ordinance ( tpo ) ; </s>
<s> ( ii ) the checking of compliance with approval conditions imposed by the tpb under section 16 ( 5 ) of the tpo ; and </s>
<s> ( iii ) application for minor amendment to a planning permission previously granted by the tpb which are processed under delegated authority to the director of planning . </s>
<s> " another measure is to strengthen the role of the district planning conference in reaching a positive decision on planning matters , </s>
<s> " he said . </s>
<s> to achieve this , the chairman of the conference is now empowered to over @-@ rule other departmental objections , </s>
<s> if necessary , to proceed with housing development projects as quickly as possible . </s>
<s> the proponents for development projects may also attend the conference to present proposals and views on any development problems . </s>
<s> as regards the validity period of planning permission , </s>
<s> the spokesman said the tpb had agreed to an extension from two to three years to reduce the need for subsequent applications for extension . </s>
<s> the tpb has also agreed that its secretary should provide successful applicants with a list of government officials responsible for checking the compliance with individual approval conditions . this will help applicants take follow @-@ up actions to comply with the approval conditions . </s>
<s> in addition , </s>
<s> more information on planning will be made available at planning department 's public counter on the 16 th floor , murray building , garden road , central , hong_kong . </s>
<s> to enhance its communication with relevant professional bodies , the department will publish detailed notes on its practices and procedures on certain planning matters . </s>
<s> " we are committed to improving our working procedures to speed up the development approval process and housing supply , </s>
<s> " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> vaccination reminder against predicted measles epidemic </s>
<s> the department of health ( dh ) today ( saturday ) once again reminded parents to take their one to five @-@ year @-@ old children to any general out @-@ patient clinics ( gopcs ) or maternal and children health centre ( mchcs ) for measles vaccination if they have not already done so . </s>
<s> the reminder was issued as the current special measles vaccination campaign , which aims to avert a predicted measles epidemic next year , </s>
<s> is entering the final phase before its conclusion on november 15 ( saturday ) . </s>
<s> " they should make good use of the remaining six days of the vaccination campaign to immunise their children and give them maximum protection against the predicted measles epidemic , </s>
<s> " a dh spokesman said . " all gopcs and mchcs now allow walk @-@ in vaccinations . </s>
<s> in the last major measles outbreak in hong_kong in 1988 , 3,162 cases and eight deaths were reported . </s>
<s> the vaccination campaign , which started on september 8 , has so far covered 213,000 children aged one to five , </s>
<s> representing 56 percent of this age group . </s>
<s> although most children in hong_kong have received their first dose of vaccine when they are one year old , </s>
<s> a second dose is necessary to enhance their immunity , the spokesman explained . </s>
<s> " the vaccine is safe , effective and free , </s>
<s> and can be received four weeks after the first one , " he emphasised . </s>
<s> " the measles , mumps and rubella ( mmr ) vaccine or anti @-@ measles vaccine ( amv ) offers very good protection against the disease . " </s>
<s> in the meantime , health staff of the department have been visiting primary schools to vaccinate children between the age of six and 11. some 376,000 pupils have been covered , representing 80 per cent of this age group . </s>
<s> serological studies show that the immunity of those aged one to 19 is inadequate , </s>
<s> suggesting that this group would most likely be affected should an outbreak occur . </s>
<s> the spokesman noted that during the last vaccination exercise for people between 12 and 19 , a total of 427,000 youngsters were covered , </s>
<s> representing 73 per cent of this age group . </s>
<s> for enquiries , members of the public can call the special measles vaccination campaign hotlines on 2833 0111 and 2591 6330 . </s>
