<s> guidance notes for registered medical practitioners </s>
<s> the labour department is sending copies of the " guidance notes on the diagnosis of notifiable occupational diseases " by direct mail to 8,000 registered medical practitioners to remind them of reporting all occupational diseases to the department in the course of their daily work . </s>
<s> the guidance booklet contains 47 kinds of notifiable occupational diseases which are compensable under the employees ' compensation ordinance , </s>
<s> the pneumoconiosis ( compensation ) ordinance and the occupational deafness ( compensation ) ordinance . </s>
<s> under section 15 of the occupational safety and health ordinance enacted in may this year , medical practitioners are required to notify occupational diseases to the commissioner for labour . </s>
<s> the notification must be in writing and on a form approved by the commissioner and it must be lodged as soon as possible . </s>
<s> medical practitioners can also refer any patient who is suspected to be suffering from work @-@ related illness to the labour department 's kwun tong occupational health clinic . </s>
<s> " the booklet is intended for the use of medical practitioners in identifying and diagnosing occupational diseases listed in the occupational safety and health ordinance , " occupational health consultant of the department , dr lo wai @-@ kee , </s>
<s> said today ( sunday ) . </s>
<s> " the notes in the booklet do not purport to be exhaustive , but are intended as an aid to medical practitioners dealing with these illness . </s>
<s> with the help of these notes , we hope more medical practitioners in hong_kong will report cases of occupational diseases to the labour department which can then do the follow @-@ up work , </s>
<s> " dr lo added . </s>
<s> also enclosed with the booklet are a sample of the approved form for medical practitioner to notify all confirmed and suspected occupational diseases to the occupational health service of the labour department and a promotional ruler which listed out seven common notifiable occupational diseases . </s>
<s> the seven diseases are contact dermatitis , occupational deafness , pneumoconiosis , tenosynovitis of hand and forearm , tuberculosis in health care workers , chemical poisoning and occupational asthma . </s>
