<s> " there is no question that the government did not observe the significance of the service , " the spokesman stressed . </s>
<s> the official ceremony next year will be held at the memorial shrine in city hall . </s>
<s> it is intended that the event will be attended by the chief executive , other senior officials and community leaders . representatives of war veteran groups and related community organisations will also be invited to attend . </s>
