<s> proposed bus / bus interchange at tai lam tunnel toll plaza </s>
<s> the transport department has proposed to set up a bus / bus interchange at tai lam tunnel toll plaza to tie in with the opening of route three ( country park section ) in mid @-@ 1998 . </s>
<s> speaking on the plan today ( monday ) , a spokesman for the department said : </s>
<s> " a number of existing bus routes from yuen long will be diverted to operate via route three ( country park section ) and a new route will commence at the same time . </s>
<s> " these buses will route via tai lam tunnel and the proposed bus / bus interchange at the toll plaza will be a convenient stop for passengers to interchange for buses to their destination . </s>
<s> " passengers need not pay again for interchange or just pay a concessionary fare when they board another one at the interchange . </s>
<s> " it will serve as a complement to the extensive public transportation network linking new territories west and other areas in hong_kong . " </s>
<s> to provide quality services for passengers , the interchange at tai lam tunnel toll plaza will have shelters . </s>
<s> all buses using the interchange will be air @-@ conditioned . </s>
<s> the proposed bus routes which will be diverted to operate via the new expressway upon its opening instead of tuen mun road and castle peak road are as follows : </s>
<s> moreover , </s>
<s> kowloon motor bus ( kmb ) has proposed to run a new route no. 269 between tin shui estate and hung hom ferry pier via route three ( country park section ) for those who need to travel to kowloon east and hong_kong island . </s>
<s> for residents along the section of castle peak road between yuen long and tuen mun , kmb has drawn up two new routes , </s>
<s> nos. 63 m ( yuen long ( west ) - tsing yi station ) and 63 x ( tin tsz estate - jordan road ferry pier ) , </s>
<s> to meet the traffic demand following the bus diversions . </s>
<s> the spokesman said : </s>
<s> " the journey time for the routes diverted to operate via the new expressway will be reduced to about 10 minutes , resulting in a better and more efficient bus services for the passengers . " </s>
<s> the transport department has proceeded to consult various provisional district boards on the establishment of the bus / bus interchange and bus diversion arrangements . </s>
<s> basic law protects investment in hong_kong </s>
<s> hong_kong believes the best way to attract and protect investment is to institute an investment regime that is free , open , transparent and stable . </s>
<s> and these principles are firmly enshrined in the basic law . </s>
<s> the secretary for trade and industry , miss denise yue , said this at the hong_kong , </s>
<s> shanghai , osaka economic co @-@ operation conference jointly organised by the federation of hong_kong industries , shanghai federation of industry and commerce and osaka industrial association at the hong_kong convention and exhibition centre this ( monday ) morning . </s>
<s> miss yue said the basic law , which delineated and institutionalised the unprecedented concept of " one country , two systems " , </s>
<s> protected the rights , freedoms and lifestyle of the hong_kong people . </s>
<s> it guaranteed the independence of hong_kong 's judiciary and , apart from foreign affairs and defence , it gave the hksar full responsibilities to manage its own affairs . </s>
<s> she said the basic law required the hksar to : </s>
<s> * practise the capitalist system for at least 50 years after 1997 , thereby giving a firm basis </s>
<s> * pursue a free trade policy and remain a free port ; </s>
<s> * operate its own independent finances and formulate its own monetary and fiscal policies ; </s>
<s> * uphold a freely convertible hong_kong currency , with free flow of capital and no foreign exchange controls . </s>
<s> the basic law stipulated the rule of law in hong_kong and prescribed the operation of an independent system of law and an independent judiciary with the power of final adjudication which was now vested in the court of final appeal . </s>
<s> " the rule of law makes sure that contracts entered into are enforceable . </s>
<s> " it ensures that the generators of wealth - investors and entrepreneurs - have the confidence in obtaining fair redress in courts , in the full knowledge that their rights will not be impinged upon by any party or subject to governmental whims , " miss yue said . </s>
<s> the practice of a level playing field was also vitally important to investors . </s>
<s> in hong_kong , anyone could start any legitimate business in hong_kong - without hidden constraints , import duty or non @-@ tariff barriers ; </s>
<s> without prejudice to the nationality of the owners of the business ; and without favouritism or partiality on the part of the government . </s>
<s> miss yue noted that investors flocked to places where the public service was corruption @-@ free . </s>
<s> " since the establishment of the independent commission against corruption ( icac ) in 1974 , </s>
<s> hong_kong has gained a reputation as one of the cleanest places in the region to do business . </s>
<s> concerning the protection of the investors ' property , miss yue said again , the basic law mandated the hksar , </s>
<s> in accordance with law , to protect the right of individuals and legal persons on the acquisition , use , </s>
<s> disposal and inheritance of property , and compensate for the lawful deprivation of their property . </s>
<s> this protection not only covered tangible property but , equally important , intellectual property rights . </s>
<s> a low and predictable tax regime was another important consideration of investors . </s>
<s> hong_kong 's tax regime was simple and its rates were consistently low . </s>
<s> the basic law required the hksar to have its own independent taxation and specifically stated that investors in hong_kong would not be subject to taxation by mainland china . </s>
<s> she said the basic law also empowered the hksar government to conclude and implement agreements with foreign states , regions and relevant international organisations in the appropriate fields , including the fields of trade and economic . </s>
<s> " this enabled us to conclude specific investment protection agreements with its trading partners which provided an additional safeguard for their investment in hong_kong . </s>
<s> " since 1991 , hong_kong had been actively negotiating for a network of bilateral investment promotion and protection agreements ( ippas ) . </s>
<s> these agreements provided its foreign investors with specific benefits such as national and most @-@ favoured - nation treatment , </s>
<s> protection against non @-@ commercial risks , safeguard against expropriation , and right to international arbitration . </s>
<s> so far , hong_kong had concluded a total of 13 ippas with its trading partners . </s>
<s> miss yue said after its reunification with china , hong_kong would continue to practise a free trade and open market economic policy . </s>
<s> it welcomed businesses from all parts of the world . </s>
<s> as an open economy , the hksar government had no special approval procedure for foreign investments . </s>
<s> and it did not interfere with management of investments in hong_kong . </s>
<s> it also put no roadblocks before investment overseas by its own entrepreneurs or by others who wished to invest in other places through hong_kong . </s>
<s> it thus came as no surprise that hong_kong was the world 's fourth largest source of foreign direct investment and the largest external investor in the mainland of china , </s>
<s> miss yue said . </s>
<s> hong_kong ranks second in asia 's retail sales </s>
<s> the world competitiveness yearbook of 1997 ranked hong_kong 15 in the world 's retail sales on a per capita basis , </s>
<s> reaching us $ 4,254 , </s>
<s> second only to japan in asia , the secretary for trade and industry , miss denise yue said today ( monday ) . </s>
<s> delivering the welcome speech at the 51 st general assembly of the international group of department stores , miss yue said shopping was one of the most popular activities in hong_kong as people became more affluent . </s>
<s> according to a world bank study , hong_kong 's per capita income was us $ 24,600 in 1996 , amongst the top 10 in the world . </s>
<s> the tourist industry also contributed to the flourishing retail business . </s>
<s> she noted that the retail and wholesale industry was the second largest service sector in hong_kong in terms of sales turnover , number of establishments and employment . </s>
<s> " in 1996 , </s>
<s> the retail sector alone employed some 200,000 people in some 52,000 establishments . total sales reached us $ 28.7 billion last year . " </s>
<s> miss yue said that the robust retail sector was engendered by a number of factors : </s>
<s> - hong_kong had a free and open business environment . </s>
<s> - it provided a level playing field where foreign and local investors are treated exactly alike . </s>
<s> - there was no restriction on the right to establish retail operations . </s>
<s> - because of hong_kong 's free port policy , no tariffs were levied on imports and no non @-@ tariff measures were imposed to restrict the import of </s>
<s> - there was no sales or consumption tax . </s>
<s> " on top of these , hong_kong 's tax regime is one of the lowest and simplest in the world profits tax at 16.5 per cent only . </s>
<s> " the excellent and cost effective physical and telecommunications infrastructure guarantees quick delivery of goods and keeping up with world market trend . </s>
<s> " linkage support is also adequate in terms of customised information package , merchandising , advertising , </s>
<s> miss yue said the retail industry in hong_kong also benefited from hong_kong 's role as the gateway to mainland china . </s>
<s> " mainland china is gradually opening its retail market to foreign investment at designated cities in the form of joint ventures with import rights . </s>
<s> " for these ventures , the local partner being the licence holder will provide floor space , </s>
<s> while the foreign partner will contribute capital and management expertise and usually be responsible for day @-@ to @-@ day supervision of the retail establishments . </s>
<s> " mainland china particularly welcomes the development of chain stores which will enable it to develop economies of scale of sourcing and distribution , </s>
<s> to unify quality standards and promote the development of branded products . </s>
<s> " department stores having business experience in hong_kong were well @-@ placed to tap these opportunities , " miss yue said . </s>
<s> turning to the recent financial turmoil , she said that notwithstanding such turmoil , </s>
<s> asia remained the highest economic growth region in the world . </s>
<s> " in the medium term , the spending power of almost half of the world 's population will continue to rise , </s>
<s> generating an insatiable shopping demand for department stores to meet , " she said . </s>
