<s> ' tide tables for hong_kong 1998 ' on sale </s>
<s> the ' tide tables for hong_kong 1998 ' , which provides an information reference on tides in hong_kong , is now on sale . </s>
<s> the tables listed the predicted heights and times of daily high and low waters at eight locations , </s>
<s> including chi ma wan , ko lau wan , lok on pai , quarry bay , tai o , tai po kau , tsim bei tsui and waglan island . </s>
<s> phases of the moon are also available . </s>
<s> the tables will serve as a useful guide for engineers , shipping and wharfing companies , container terminal operators , yachtsmen , as well as fishing and water sports enthusiasts . </s>
<s> the bilingual publication is now on sale at $ 11 a copy at the government publications sales centre , marine department headquarters and hong_kong observatory headquarters . </s>
