<s> as i have full confidence in the financial soundness of iba i now go further , </s>
<s> the exchange fund stands squarely behind this institution and will provide all the necessary financial support it may require to meet its obligations for as long as is necessary . </s>
<s> as we know , rumour @-@ mongers serve their own selfish purposes . they are not acting in the interest of all of us . </s>
<s> we have very sound fundamentals in hong_kong , and i am quite sure we have the determination and strength to overcome this difficulty . </s>
<s> exco decision on gc delineation </s>
<s> the chief executive in council has made a decision on the delineation of geographical constituencies for the legislative council election next may , </s>
<s> the decision is set out in the declaration of constituencies ( legislative council ) order 1997 which will be gazetted on friday ( november 14 ) and tabled in the provisional legislative council ( pro @-@ legco ) on november 19 . </s>
<s> " the chief executive in council has accepted the recommendations of the independent electoral affairs commission in their entirety in making the decision , </s>
<s> " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> the report of the commission submitted to the chief executive will be tabled in the pro @-@ legco on the same day as the order . </s>
<s> " for the legislative council election to be held in may 1998 , hong_kong will be delineated into five geographical constituencies - one for hong_kong island ; </s>
<s> two for kowloon , to be named kowloon east and kowloon west respectively ; </s>
<s> and two for the new territories , to be named new territories east and new territories west respectively . </s>
<s> " there will be four seats for the hong_kong island constituency , three each for the kowloon east constituency and the kowloon west constituency , </s>
<s> and five each for the new territories east constituency and the new territories west constituency , " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> the hong_kong island constituency will comprise four districts , namely , central and western , </s>
<s> wan chai , eastern and southern . the kowloon east constituency will comprise two districts , </s>
<s> namely , wong tai sin and kwun tong while the kowloon west constituency will consist of three districts , namely , yau tsim mong , sham shui po and kowloon city . </s>
<s> the new territories east constituency will comprise four districts , namely , north , tai po , </s>
<s> sha tin and sai kung and the new territories west will comprise five districts , </s>
<s> namely , tsuen wan , tuen mun , yuen long , kwai tsing and islands . </s>
<s> " the making of the order is another important step in the preparation for the legislative council election next year . the voter registration campaign will proceed in full speed to tie in the publication of the electoral roll early next year , </s>
<s> " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> pledge to maintain the finest police force </s>
<s> the government is determined to maintain the police force as one of the finest , upholding law and order with integrity , honesty and professionalism , </s>
<s> in response to views expressed by various people concerning a number of recent incidents involving police officers , </s>
<s> the spokesman said : " the incidents are being fully and impartially investigated and there will be no tolerance for those who have acted unlawfully or improperly . " </s>
<s> he maintained that the majority of the members of the police force were dedicated to their work and had served the community well , </s>
<s> as reflected in the continued improvement of the law and order situation during the past years . </s>
<s> on suggestions that there should be an independent mechanism to investigate complaints against police officers , the spokesman said that the present police complaints system was one with checks and balances . </s>
<s> " he said . </s>
<s> the government have already introduced a number of improvement measures including the installation of closed circuit television and video or tape @-@ recording facilities at capo and the introduction of the interview witness scheme and the observers scheme for ipcc members . </s>
<s> arising from the ipcc 's own review of the investigation procedures of capo and the comparative study of police complaints system in other police jurisdictions , </s>
<s> the government is implementing a total of 48 improvement measures such as setting up a special ipcc panel to monitor serious cases and conducting surveys and research to gauge public opinion on the police complaints system . </s>
<s> on prevention of corruption in the police force , the spokesman said the recent joint operation with the icac underlined the determination of the police force to eradicate corruption within the force . </s>
<s> " the police force is also implementing the force anti @-@ corruption strategy which emphasises preventing and tackling corruption through training , </s>
<s> inculcation of ethical values , procedural reviews to reduce corruption opportunities and vigorous enforcement action , " he said . </s>
<s> in the first nine months of 1997 , the number of corruption complaints against police officers dropped by 16 per cent when compared with the same period last year . </s>
<s> " integrity and honesty remain the core value of our police force , " he said . </s>
<s> the spokesman also reaffirmed the government 's intention to implement those recommendations on the law reform commission report on arrest which had been made by an interdepartmental working group in june this year . </s>
<s> as part of the recommendations , the spokesman said the government was committed to introducing video @-@ interviewing of suspects at all police stations to enhance transparency of the statement taking process and the admissibility of confession statements . </s>
<s> " the target is to set up a vir at each police station in the next two years , </s>
<s> " he said . </s>
<s> " the commissioner of police is determined to improve the service quality of the force . for example , </s>
<s> by promoting a force vision and stating a common purpose of values so that every member of the police force shares the common values of integrity and honesty , respect for the rights of members of the public and of the force , </s>
<s> and fairness , impartiality and compassion in all its dealings , " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> hksar / singapore sign sfo agreement </s>
<s> the hong_kong special administrative region ( hksar ) and singapore signed an agreement for the surrender of fugitive offenders today ( tuesday ) . </s>
<s> the agreement was signed by the secretary for security , mr peter lai hing @-@ ling , on behalf of the hksar government and the consul general of the republic of singapore to the hksar , mr chan heng wing , on behalf of the singapore government . </s>
<s> speaking at the signing ceremony , mr lai said : </s>
<s> " the signing of the agreement today signifies our ( hksar and singapore ) commitment to work closely together so that criminals cannot escape justice by fleeing to the hksar from singapore , </s>
<s> or vice versa . " </s>
<s> the agreement on the surrender of fugitive offenders is the 10 th bilateral agreement on the surrender of fugitive offenders concluded by hong_kong . </s>
<s> it sets out the conditions for the surrender of fugitive offenders between the two places , and contains the usual safeguards found in similar international agreements . </s>
<s> mr lai said the surrender of fugitive offenders agreement would enhance the international community 's confidence in hksar 's criminal justice system , </s>
<s> the continuity of the rule of law and the future of the hksar as a whole . </s>
<s> the fugitive offenders ordinance which provides the necessary legislative backing for the implementation of the agreement is already in place . </s>
<s> the agreement will enter into force 30 days after both sides notified each other in writing that their respective requirements for the entry into force of the agreements have been complied with . </s>
<s> 33 building plans approved in september </s>
<s> the buildings department approved a total of 33 building plans in september this year -- 12 on hong_kong island , five in kowloon and 16 in the new territories . </s>
<s> this compared with 62 building plans approved in august and 42 in july . </s>
<s> the approved plans covered 15 for apartment and apartment / commercial developments , three for commercial developments , two for factory and industrial developments , </s>
<s> and 13 for community services developments . </s>
<s> consent was given in the month for works to start on 40 building projects , which will provide 61,635 square metres of usable domestic floor area and 56,347 square metres of usable non @-@ domestic floor area on completion . </s>
<s> the department also issued 32 occupation permits -- 15 on hong_kong island , seven in kowloon and 10 in the new territories . </s>
<s> of the buildings certified for occupation in september , the usable floor areas for domestic and non @-@ domestic uses were 74,178 square metres and 43,484 square metres respectively . the declared cost of new buildings completed in the month totalled about $ 2.049 billion . </s>
<s> in addition , 40 demolition consents involving 69 buildings and structures were issued . </s>
<s> the department 's control and enforcement division received 1,418 complaints against unauthorised building works in september , and issued 361 removal orders on unauthorised works . </s>
