<s> the basic terms for the sale of these 94 flats will be identical to those in the last exercise . they will go to the highest bidders , </s>
<s> subject to minimum prices specified for the individual flats . </s>
<s> only individual end @-@ users who have not bought surplus government quarters before will be eligible to tender , and no one will be able to buy more than one unit . </s>
