<s> the transport department has commissioned airport ferry services limited to operate a new ferry service between chek lap kok and tuen mun ferry pier ( outside pierhead garden ) . </s>
<s> the company is a joint venture comprising discovery bay transportation services limited , marinteknik international limited and wang tak engineering & shipping company limited . </s>
<s> speaking on the tender result today ( thursday ) , a spokesman for the department said : </s>
<s> " the new ferry service will be introduced in 1998 to tie in with the opening of the new airport at chek lap kok . </s>
<s> " the vessels used will each have a seating capacity of 300 passengers to meet anticipated travelling demand . " </s>
<s> the chek lap kok / tuen mun ferry services is scheduled to operate from 6 am to 10 pm daily at a frequency of 20 / 30 @-@ minute interval . </s>
<s> the fare for each single trip is $ 15 for adult and $ 10 for children . </s>
<s> the transport department has invited tender for this new ferry services in april this year and received a total of four submissions . </s>
