<s> housing department to mediate in on ning garden case </s>
<s> a government spokesman today ( friday ) reiterated that the housing department will do all it can to mediate in the dispute between the developer and the owners of the on ning garden in order to help resolve the problems involved as a result of the soil settlement in this private sector participation scheme development . </s>
<s> besides notifying the developer of the defects which require urgent repairs , the department has also demanded that the developer should rectify some of the other defects in question at their own expense within a specified time frame . </s>
<s> the department has been meeting with the developer and has been pressing them to take prompt action to rectify such defects . </s>
<s> on october 20 this year , a team of housing department professionals was deployed to carry out inspections in on ning garden to investigate the structure safety of the estate ; to comment on the likely causes to the 266 cracks reported by the owners ; </s>
<s> and to identify any imminent hazards relating to common utility services . </s>
<s> the in @-@ house professional team completed their assessment report on october 30 and concluded that 96 out of the 266 defects reported by the owners were caused by site settlement . </s>
<s> " the lists of defects produced by the in @-@ house professionals are by no means exhaustive and conclusive , " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> " if further defects were found to be caused by site settlement in the development , the department will ask the developer to carry out necessary repair works without delay . </s>
<s> " the department takes a serious view on the issue and has asked the developer to complete the repair works within the prescribed time , </s>
<s> and to report progress to the department every week , " he added . </s>
<s> ce and sti to attend apec meetings in vancouver </s>
<s> will represent the hong_kong special administrative region ( hksar ) to attend the annual gathering of economic leaders from the 18 asia @-@ pacific economic co @-@ operation ( apec ) member economies , to be held on november 24 @-@ 25 in vancouver , canada . </s>
<s> the secretary for trade and industry , miss denise yue , will attend the apec ministerial meeting on november 21 @-@ 22 . </s>
<s> the director @-@ general of trade , mr alan lai nin , will attend the informal senior officials meeting on november 19 @-@ 20 . </s>
<s> using the name ' hong_kong , china ' , attends this important event in the region . </s>
<s> " it signifies the fact that hksar remains a separate and full member of apec . we continue to speak for hong_kong 's own economic and trade interests . " </s>
<s> " the ministerial meeting will review the activities of apec in 1997 and set direction for the future . </s>
<s> " one of the focal points will be to identify a package of sectors for early voluntary liberalisation for submission to economic leaders . </s>
<s> " the challenge is to arrive at a balanced package which commands wide support among apec members and has economic impact , </s>
<s> " she said . </s>
<s> " it is expected that economic leaders will discuss infrastructure development , electronic commerce and asian @-@ pacific region 's financial stability , " she said . </s>
<s> miss yue hoped that the economic leaders would exchange views on the world trade organisation ( wto ) financial services negotiations now in progress in geneva , </s>
<s> and the desirability of pursuing further broad @-@ based trade liberalisation in the wto as the world moves into the new millennium . </s>
<s> hong_kong 's ambulance service has become the first in the region to receive an accreditation award from the paramedic academy of the justice institute of british columbia ( jibc ) in canada for its development of paramedic service in the territory , </s>
<s> in a speech marking the fire services department 's acceptance of the award , mr cheung said the advisory group on extended training for ambulance personnel recommended in 1991 that paramedical training should be provided to members of the ambulance service . </s>
<s> such training includes defibrillation , intubation , intravenous infusion and uses of selected drugs . </s>
<s> this recommendation , endorsed in the same year by the administration , had since become the target of the fire services department , </s>
<s> the department then decided to upgrade the level of ambulance service to emergency medical assistant ii ( ema ii ) level by phases . </s>
<s> in 1992 , two of the department 's ambulance officers were sent to jibc to receive paramedic training . </s>
<s> since then , regular training courses have been conducted in hong_kong jointly by ema ii instructors of the jibc and hospital authority doctors . </s>
<s> mr cheung said that up to now 49 officers and 160 of other ranks had qualified as ema ii. </s>
<s> among the 49 officers , </s>
<s> two of them were qualified course co @-@ ordinators while eight were qualified instructors . </s>
<s> the number of ema ii ambulances put on run reached the initial planned number of 33 , mr cheung added . </s>
<s> as part of the development programme and as agreed with the hospital authority , a medical consultant was appointed in april this year , he said . </s>
<s> the role of the consultant is to provide education and training to staff of the ambulance command of the fire services department . </s>
<s> but also represented a more challenging future , mr cheung said . </s>
<s> " while we are proud of being the first ambulance service to receive the award in the region , </s>
<s> i am certain that ambulance service members of the fire services will continue their good work with efficiency and enthusiasm . " </s>
<s> the award was presented to mr cheung by dr tony williams of jibc . </s>
<s> air quality report for october released </s>
<s> the environmental protection department today ( friday ) released air quality report for october 1997 . </s>
<s> the report said that the nitrogen dioxide concentration recorded on october 21 at the mong kok roadside air quality monitoring station was 158 ug / m 3 , slightly higher than the air quality objectives ( aqo ) by five per cent . </s>
<s> the high air pollution levels were due to the accumulation of emission from motor vehicles under adverse weather conditions with low wind speed . </s>
<s> over the past 12 months , the particulate concentration have been maintaining at high levels . </s>
<s> the preceding 12 @-@ month averages of respirable suspended particulates recorded in the three stations in mong kok , central / western and kwai chung ranged from 100 per cent to 142 per cent of the annual aqo of 55 ug / m 3 . </s>
<s> for nitrogen dioxide , the twelve @-@ month averages were also high and ranged from 63 per cent to 108 per cent of the annual aqo of 80 ug / m 3 . </s>
<s> the report includes the monitoring results obtained from three districts , which represent three important land use types in the territory : </s>
<s> * locations close to road traffic in built @-@ up urban </s>
<s> * combined commercial and residential districts , and </s>
<s> * districts close to industrial areas . </s>
<s> air pollutants reported included sulphur dioxide , nitrogen dioxide , total suspended particulates , and the respirable suspended particulates . </s>
<s> all these pollutants can affect respiratory health in sufficient concentration . </s>
<s> air pollution originated from various sources , including combustion , industrial and construction processes . </s>
<s> in terms of impact on local air quality , motor vehicle exhaust is the most important source of nitrogen dioxide and airborne particulate matter , especially the smaller respirable particles . </s>
<s> statistics on domestic exports for third quarter 1997 </s>
<s> in the third quarter of 1997 , </s>
<s> domestic exports classified to the four major industries of textiles ; wearing apparel ; machinery , equipment , apparatus , parts and components ; </s>
<s> and consumer electrical and electronic products ; together accounted for 72 % of hong_kong 's total domestic exports of manufactured goods , according to statistics released today ( friday ) by the census and statistics department . </s>
<s> in the third quarter of 1997 , domestic exports classified to the machinery , equipment , </s>
<s> apparatus , parts and components industry increased by 18 % over a year earlier to $ 10.3 billion . </s>
<s> domestic exports classified to the textiles industry increased by 8 % to $ 14.8 billion ; and those to the wearing apparel industry increased by 1 % to $ 11.2 billion . </s>
<s> however , domestic exports classified to the consumer electrical and electronic products industry decreased by 9 % to $ 6.0 billion . </s>
<s> as for domestic exports classified to the other industries , a marked increase of about 14 times was recorded for the petroleum and coal products industry . </s>
<s> the increase was concentrated mainly in the category of petroleum oils for the preparation of lubricating oils . </s>
<s> for the industry of transport equipment , although the change in absolute value was not large , a marked increase of 66 % was recorded . </s>
<s> however , notable decreases were recorded in the value of domestic exports classified to the basic metals and fabricated metal products industry ( - $ 226 million or - 10 % ) ; </s>
<s> and those to the leather and leather products industry ( - $ 148 million or - 41 % ) . </s>
<s> the above statistics of domestic exports classified by industrial origin are derived by re @-@ grouping the merchandise export items originally grouped under the external trade classification system according to the industries in which these merchandise items are normally produced . </s>
<s> transactions in gold and specie are excluded . </s>
<s> the industrial classification used is the hong_kong standard industrial classification ( hsic ) . </s>
<s> the hsic is to be distinguished from the united_nations standard international trade classification ( sitc ) used in the regular trade statistics reports . </s>
<s> in comparison , the hsic is more related to production processes whereas the sitc is more geared to end uses of products . </s>
<s> caution should be taken when referring to these domestic export statistics classified by industrial origin . there may be several intermediate processing stages in the production of certain merchandise export items . </s>
<s> in compiling the above statistics , the total value of such an item , however , </s>
<s> has been wholly related to the industry in which the item is finally produced . </s>
<s> the above domestic export statistics of a particular industry may include products which are secondary products by establishments of other industries . further details of merchandise domestic export statistics classified by industrial origin are in table 1. </s>
<s> some 300 students take part in electrical science competition </s>
<s> the assistant director of education ( chief inspector of schools ) , mr tam chun @-@ kit , will officiate at the prize presentation ceremony of the clp electrical science competition tomorrow ( saturday ) . </s>
<s> some 300 students from 53 secondary schools competed in three competitions , namely " research project competition " , " poster design competition " and " quiz on general knowledge relating to electricity " , </s>
<s> under the theme " electricity - past and future " . </s>
<s> students participating in the " research project competition " explored the development of electricity from past to future and the effect of electricity on the society . </s>
<s> some of them presented their ideas in the forms of display boards , multi @-@ media computer presentation packages or book reports while others constructed models to show electrical devices or systems in the past or future . </s>
<s> regarding the " poster design competition " , about 90 entries conveying the idea of the importance of electricity had been received . </s>
<s> a total of 21 secondary schools took part in the quiz focusing on the general knowledge of the use of electricity , </s>
<s> including theories , history and safety rules . the final of the quiz will be held before the prize presentation ceremony at the same venue . </s>
<s> the competition is jointly organised by the education department , the hong_kong institution of engineers - electrical division and the china light & power company , limited . </s>
<s> winning research projects and posters will be displayed at the technical subjects education resources centre on the ground floor , 145 junction road , lok fu between december 8 and 13. members of the public are welcome to visit the exhibition . </s>
