<s> better pier facilities on lamma and lantau </s>
<s> the government plans to construct piers and improve berthing facilities on lamma and lantau islands to cope with increasing demand for local ferry services by villagers and tourists . </s>
<s> in north lamma , an l @-@ shaped pier will be built at luk chau tsuen while an existing pier at lo tik wan will be extended . </s>
<s> the new pier , within an area of about 1,910 square metres of foreshore and sea @-@ bed at luk chau tsuen , will provide a berthing place for " kaitos " or local village ferry services . </s>
<s> the existing pier at lo tik wan will be extended to a t @-@ shaped pier of about 200 square metres , to be built on a site of 1,100 square metres of foreshore and sea @-@ bed . </s>
<s> on lantau island , a t @-@ shaped pier of about 450 square metres extending from the existing pier in tong fuk will be built on a site of about 1,840 square metres of foreshore and sea @-@ bed . </s>
<s> moreover , a new t @-@ shaped pier of about 350 square metres will be built to replace the existing trappist haven monastery pier at tai shui hang in east lantau . </s>
<s> an area of 1,670 square metres of foreshore and sea @-@ bed will be affected . </s>
<s> to protect the coastal land from erosion , minor works affecting an area of about 230 square metres of foreshore and sea @-@ bed will be carried out in front of hau wong temple , tung chung in north lantau to provide a mattress type of seawall . </s>
<s> works on all the projects will begin in mid @-@ 1998 for completion in a year . </s>
<s> relocation of proposed reprovisioned bus terminus in central </s>
<s> the government proposes to amend the engineering works for the central reclamation , phase i project to provide a more convenient bus terminus to the public . </s>
<s> the amendment involves the relocation of a proposed reprovisioned bus terminus to a site west of harbour building at 38 pier road . it will be served by an elevated footbridge and related staircase / elevator facilities . </s>
<s> in this connection , a road near harbour building will be realigned and a bus bay converted to a footpath . </s>
<s> the new bus terminus will replace the temporary rumsey street bus terminus when completed in mid @-@ 1998 . works are due to begin early next year . </s>
