<s> said the secretary for security , mr peter lai , at the launching ceremony of the anti @-@ drugs charity walk 1997 this ( sunday ) morning . </s>
<s> noting that more young people and students were participating in the charity walk this year , mr lai said this active participation was a good example of public support for the fight against drug abuse . </s>
<s> " we require the joint efforts from different sectors in the community to help young people realise the harmful effects of drug abuse , </s>
<s> stay away from drugs and lead a healthy and positive lifestyle . </s>
<s> " young people are the primary target of our anti @-@ drug education and publicity programmes . through extensive preventive education and publicity efforts over the years , </s>
<s> there has been a drop in the number of young people abusing drugs , " he added . </s>
<s> mr lai said statistics of the central registry of drug abuse showed that there were 3,988 reported drug abusers aged under 21 in 1995 , </s>
<s> down seven per cent from 1994 . </s>
<s> the number further dropped to 3,656 in 1996 , representing an 8.3 per cent decrease compared with 1995 . </s>
<s> in the period from january to june this year , reported drug abusers numbered only 1,964 , down 17.2 per cent from the reported figure of 2,371 for the same period last year . </s>
<s> mr lai said that despite the decrease in the number of reported young drug abusers , the government was far from complacent , </s>
<s> especially when the proportion of young psychotropic substance abusers had increased from 37.9 per cent in the first half of 1996 to 42.2 per cent in the same period of 1997 . </s>
<s> the government was also aware of the deteriorating problem of abuse of " ice " , </s>
<s> with the rate of reported young " ice " abusers increased from 5.2 per cent in the first half of 1996 to 11.2 per cent in the same period in 1997 . </s>
<s> mr lai pointed out that the government would map out anti @-@ drug strategies and strengthen preventive education work in accordance with the latest trend of drug abuse . </s>
<s> " this year , </s>
<s> experience reveals that if parents show more concern for their children and help them cope with stress in life , </s>
<s> young people will be able to lead a more healthy life , and realise that drugs could not bring them and their families any good , " said mr lai . </s>
<s> mr lai went on to say that the government , apart from providing anti @-@ drug talks for secondary and primary 6 students , </s>
<s> would design a similar talk for primary 5 students so that they would build up self @-@ confidence and realise the importance of a healthy lifestyle . </s>
<s> in addition , </s>
<s> the government would revise the contents of anti @-@ drugs talk for secondary students ; continue liaision with district school liaison committees for organising different anti @-@ drugs activities ; </s>
<s> and strengthen counselling services for youngsters who occasionally experiment with drugs . </s>
<s> " we are trying to help these youngsters to extricate themselves from drugs addiction , </s>
<s> and train them with life skills for re @-@ integration into society , " he said . </s>
<s> about 2,000 people , mostly school students and junior police call members , participated in the walk which was aimed at disseminating anti @-@ drug messages to the public and raising funds for the community chest in aid of drug treatment and rehabilitation organisations . </s>
<s> buildings department achieves performance pledge </s>
<s> the buildings department scored an average of 97.7 per cent in achieving its performance targets in the third quarter of this year , </s>
<s> according to its 12 th report on performance pledge released today ( sunday ) . </s>
<s> full achievement rate was recorded for five types of services to the community . </s>
<s> disapproval of first submission of plans and major revisions found not compiling with the building regulations , issuing occupation permits , processing applications for inclusion in authorised persons ' and registered structural engineers ' registers , and processing new restaurant licence applications , </s>
<s> " while the processing time for applications for inclusion in authorised persons ' and registered structural engineers ' registers has been reduced from six to five months , </s>
<s> the achievement rate remained 100 per cent , " he added . </s>
<s> performance results for inspecting potentially dangerous buildings , signs and slopes ; processing resubmission of applications for restaurant licences ; </s>
<s> and approval for first submission of buildings plans and major revisions were 99.7 per cent , 98.2 per cent and 98.1 per cent respectively . </s>
<s> achievement rates for other types of services were 97.3 per cent and 97.1 per cent respectively for approval and disapproval for resubmission of plans ; 96.9 per cent for 24 @-@ hour emergency service relating to dangers in buildings ; and 94.8 per cent for issuing of consent for demolition and new buildings works . </s>
<s> accounting for the slight drop of 0.5 percentage point in the overall achievement rate from the previous quarter , the spokesman said there was a 40 per cent increase in reports on unauthorised building works and defective drains , resulting in 88.6 per cent achievement rate in inspecting and screening the reports . </s>
<s> " in achieving our performance targets , </s>
<s> we make the built environment safe and healthy for the community , " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> " our mission has always been to set and enforce safety , health and environmental standards for private buildings , " he added . </s>
<s> government concerned with on ning garden </s>
<s> the government is very concerned with the developments at on ning garden and has been following them very closely in a bid to help resolve the problem . </s>
<s> a government spokesman said today ( monday ) that the housing department had been pressing the developer to fulfil its agreement to rectify all defects associated with site settlement and had given the developer until november 28 ( friday ) , </s>
<s> 1997 to complete the urgent repair works . </s>
<s> " if the developer fails to comply with the undertaking by that date , </s>
<s> the government will undertake all repair works related to site settlement and take legal action against the developer to recover costs , " he added . </s>
<s> in 1992 and 1993 , the developer had carried out repairs resulting from site settlement at on ning garden . </s>
<s> it also gave an undertaking to rectify any defects caused by site settlement for a period of 10 years from the date of issue of the occupation permit . </s>
<s> since then , the owners corporation has identified further defects , some of which the developer disputed . </s>
<s> the housing department has been mediating in the dispute between the developer and the owners . a team of professionals from the department was deployed in october 1997 to carry out inspections on site . </s>
<s> while confirming the structural safety of the blocks , the team identified a number of defects caused by site settlement which the developer is required to rectify . </s>
<s> civil servants participating in elections </s>
<s> the civil service bureau ( csb ) has issued a circular to provide guidelines to civil servants wishing to stand for the 1998 legislative council election committee and the national people 's congress election and to participate in these electioneering activities . </s>
<s> " the circular has incorporated changes in response to comments made by the staff side during a recent consultation exercise , " said a csb spokesman . </s>
<s> " it makes clear that most civil servants may serve on the election committee for the 1998 legislative council election and the election conference to select hksar deputies to the national people 's congress . </s>
<s> they may also seek election to the national people 's congress in their individual capacities , subject to there being no actual or potential conflicts of interest and all relevant civil service regulations being observed , </s>
<s> " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> he added that four groups of civil servants should not take part in such election activities . they are : directorate officers , </s>
<s> " the restrictions placed on the four groups of civil servants are nothing new , " he explained . </s>
<s> " they follow a long standing practice which is well understood by civil servants . " they serve to ensure that those civil servants who are directly involved in policy formulation and promulgation , in the enforcement of public order , </s>
<s> and in decision making at the policy level will not be involved in political activities , thus avoiding conflict of interest situation . </s>
<s> " we believe that the guidelines set out in the circular strike a fair balance between the rights of civil servants to participate in the forthcoming elections and the need of the community for an impartial civil service , </s>
<s> " he said . </s>
