<s> unemployment and underemployment statistics released </s>
<s> the seasonally adjusted unemployment rate for the period july - september 1997 was 2.2 % , </s>
<s> and the underemployment rate was 1.0 % , according to the latest labour force statistics released today ( monday ) by the census and statistics department . </s>
<s> for the period august - october 1997 , the provisional seasonally adjusted unemployment rate was marginally higher , </s>
<s> at 2.3 % , while the provisional underemployment rate remained unchanged at 1.0 % . </s>
<s> comparing the latest three @-@ month period august - october 1997 with the period july - september 1997 , the increase in the unemployment rate occurred mainly in the construction , manufacturing and transport sectors . </s>
<s> the unemployment situation in the other major sectors was broadly stable . </s>
<s> as to the underemployment rate , an increase was seen in the construction sector while a decline was observed in the transport sector . </s>
<s> the underemployment situation in the other major sectors remained broadly stable . </s>
<s> a government secretariat spokesman observed that growth in total employment in the third quarter continued to outpace that in labour supply . </s>
<s> in the three months ending september 1997 , total employment showed a notable increase of 4.3 % over a year earlier , </s>
<s> while total labour supply grew by 3.8 % . </s>
<s> during the period july - september 1997 , the number of unemployed persons was estimated at 69,700 , and the number of underemployed persons was estimated at 33,100 . </s>
<s> the unemployment and underemployment statistics were obtained from a continuous general household survey . </s>
<s> the survey for july - september 1997 covered a quarterly sample of some 23,100 households or 77,500 persons , </s>
<s> selected scientifically to represent the land @-@ based civilian non @-@ institutional population in hong_kong . </s>
<s> data on labour force characteristics were obtained from the survey by interviewing each member aged 15 and over in the households sampled . </s>
<s> in the survey , the definitions used in measuring unemployment and underemployment follow closely those recommended by the international labour organisation . </s>
<s> being " seasonally adjusted " refers to the fact that unemployment rate has been adjusted for seasonal variations in the proportion of first @-@ time job @-@ seekers in the labour force . </s>
<s> detailed analysis of labour force characteristics is given in the report on the general household survey which is published four times a year . </s>
<s> the next report covering the quarter ending september 1997 will be on sale at the government publications centre at ground floor , low block , 66 queensway , hong_kong , by the end of december 1997 . </s>
