<s> measles campaign successfully concluded </s>
<s> the 1997 special measles vaccination campaign , organised by the department of health ( dh ) , </s>
<s> concluded successfully last saturday ( november 15 ) , with more than 1.09 million people aged from one to 19 immunised against the acute communicable disease . </s>
<s> " since the campaign was launched on july 28 , a total of 1,090,985 people , aged from one to 19 , </s>
<s> have turned up for vaccinations , representing 76 per cent of the target population of this age group , " a dh spokesman said today ( monday ) . </s>
<s> the vaccination exercise , the largest of this kind ever organised to avert a predicted measles epidemic next year , was conducted in three phases , </s>
<s> targeting respectively at youngsters aged between 12 and 19 , children and primary school students aged between six and 11 , and children and kindergarten students aged between one and five . </s>
<s> " in the 12 @-@ 19 age group , 430,000 youngsters were vaccinated , representing about 74 per cent of the target , </s>
<s> " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> " in the latter two age groups , </s>
<s> 416,920 and 234,136 children were vaccinated , representing 89 per cent and 64 per cent of their respective targets . " </s>
<s> the spokesman attributed the good results obtained within such a short period of time to a high public awareness of the seriousness of the disease and the positive and enthusiastic response of the parents . </s>
<s> " this campaign has provided the susceptible groups with maximum protection against measles . with this coverage , we are confident that the predicted outbreak can be averted , " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> in order that everyone in the target group is immunised against the disease , </s>
<s> he said , it is important that those who , for various reasons , </s>
<s> have not come forward for the second dose of vaccination , should receive similar protection . </s>
<s> " they should either approach any of our general out @-@ patient clinics ( gopcs ) or maternal and child health centres ( mchcs ) for the vaccination service in the next few weeks or receive the inoculations from their private medical practitioners at their own expenses , </s>
<s> " the spokesman added . </s>
<s> enquiries about measles vaccinations can be directed to any gopc and mchc during office hours . </s>
<s> briefing on intellectual property rights laws </s>
<s> the patents ordinance and registered designs ordinance , which came into force on june 27 this year , </s>
<s> mark an important step in the efforts of hong_kong in protection of intellectual property rights ( ipr ) , said the senior solicitor of the intellectual property department , ms fanny pang today ( monday ) . </s>
<s> speaking at a seminar attended by over 130 participants , </s>
<s> ms pang said the two ordinances provide for the establishment of ipr regimes in the hksar for the protection of industrial designs and inventions in line with international standards . </s>
<s> targeting at lawyers and practitioners of designs and patents , the seminar was organised by the intellectual property department to brief them on the two new laws and associated registration procedures . </s>
<s> the last time a seminar was held was on august 6 when it was conducted in english . </s>
<s> the seminar held today was in cantonese . </s>
<s> " the patents ordinance provides for the grant of independent , standard patents valid for 20 years in hong_kong based on the registration of a patent granted by the chinese patent office , the united kingdom patent office or the european patent office designating the united kingdom , </s>
<s> " said ms pang . </s>
<s> " this arrangement gives the hksar the benefit of patents which are fully searched and examined by internationally respected patent offices , </s>
<s> without the need for the hksar to invest in its own examination system . " </s>
<s> the ordinance also provides for the grant of short @-@ term patents for a period of eight years . </s>
<s> " this form of patent suits inventions with a short commercial life , " ms pang said . </s>
<s> as for registered design , she said : " under the registered designs ordinance , </s>
<s> design which appeals to the eye and is applied to an article by means of an industrial process will be eligible for registration subject to formality examination . " </s>
<s> the period of protection of a registered design will initially be five years . it may be extended for four periods of five years each upon payment of the prescribed renewal fee . </s>
<s> the maximum duration of protection will be a total of 25 years , she said . </s>
<s> speakers from the intellectual property department talked on the procedures for the new patents system and registered design registration system before the seminar concluded with a question @-@ and @-@ answer session . </s>
