<s> special stamps on the year of the tiger to be issued in january </s>
<s> the postmaster general , mr robert footman , </s>
<s> announced today ( monday ) that a set of special stamps on the theme of the " year of the tiger " will be issued on january 4 ( sunday ) , 1998 . </s>
<s> " this is the 12 th and the last in the current series of lunar new year special stamps released by hongkong post commencing from the ' year of the rabbit ' in 1987 . </s>
<s> " there will be four denominations , </s>
<s> namely $ 1.3 , $ 2.5 , $ 3.1 and $ 5. </s>
<s> these stamps will be printed in sheets of 50 stamps with a gutter separating two panes of 25 stamps . </s>
<s> a souvenir sheet incorporating the four stamps will also be issued . </s>
<s> " a stamp booklet , containing six $ 1.3 stamps and six $ 3.1 , will be available at $ 26.4 each . </s>
<s> the stamps were designed by mr kan tai @-@ keung and printed by ashton @-@ potter ( canada ) ltd , " mr footman said . </s>
<s> as from friday ( november 21 ) , </s>
<s> the stamps will be on display for advance information of the public at the general post office , tsim sha tsui post office , tsuen wan post office and sha tin central post office . </s>
<s> official first day covers will be put on sale at all post offices at $ 1 each on the same day . </s>
<s> advance orders for mint stamps , serviced first day covers and presentation packs will be accepted at all post offices from friday ( november 21 ) to december 4 . </s>
<s> no handling fee will be charged . </s>
<s> " there is no limit on the order quantity but it must be in multiples of five and the minimum is five sets of stamps or five serviced first day covers , </s>
<s> " mr footman said . </s>
<s> " the order will be available for customers ' collection as from january 26 , 1998 at the post office where the order is placed , " he added . </s>
<s> meanwhile , a beautifully designed presentation pack containing the four stamps will be available for sale at $ 20 each at all post offices as from january 4 , 1998 . </s>
<s> serviced first day covers affixed with a full set of the stamps cancelled with the special postmark will be put on sale at $ 15.4 each at the 22 philatelic offices on the same day . </s>
<s> a restriction of five sheets of stamps of each denomination ( 250 sets of stamps ) , 20 souvenir sheets , five booklets , </s>
<s> five presentation packs and five serviced first day covers per customer queuing would be imposed on the first day of issue on january 4 and on subsequent days while stock lasts , mr footman said . </s>
<s> " hand @-@ back service will be provided at all post offices to official and privately @-@ made covers bearing indication of the first day of issue on january 4 , 1998. a special postmark will also be introduced . </s>
<s> the gpo @-@ 1 hand stamp will be available for hand @-@ back service at all 22 philatelic offices . </s>
<s> " all post offices will be opened on january 4 and the opening hours will be from 8 am to 4 pm . however , counter services provided will be restricted to sale of the new stamps and acceptance of registered mails only , " he added . </s>
