<s> the president and his accompanying party will also visit the new airport at chek lap kok and attend a luncheon to be hosted by the hong_kong trade development council at the hong_kong convention and exhibition centre . </s>
<s> acp cost estimates further reduced </s>
<s> the government has further reduced the overall cost estimates for the airport core programme ( acp ) by $ 1,042 million to $ 155,322 million as a result of savings achieved through tight cost monitoring and control measures . </s>
<s> compared with the original budget of $ 163,730 million estimated in 1992 , </s>
<s> the revision represents a total reduction of $ 8,408 million , or 5.1 per cent of the original budget . </s>
<s> this is the third time the acp budget has been reduced . </s>
<s> the budget was first cut to $ 158,169 million in january 1994 and in october 1996 , it was further reduced to $ 156,364 million . </s>
<s> the director of the new airport projects co @-@ ordination office ( napco ) , mr billy lam chung @-@ lun , attributed the achievement to the excellent efforts in cost control and in effective claim settlement by the works agents and government departments involved in the acp projects . </s>
<s> the latest savings of $ 1,042 million have been identified from government facilities at the new airport , </s>
<s> tung chung new town , lantau link , route 3 , west kowloon reclamation , as well as utilities and other projects . </s>
<s> members of the finance committee of the provisional legislative council and the airport consultative committee were informed of the new savings in napco 's latest quarterly report on progress of the acp . </s>
<s> the quarterly report also revealed that up to the end of september 1997 , </s>
<s> a total of 5,224 claims have been resolved at a cost of $ 2,580 million , against a claimed amount of $ 9,741 million . </s>
<s> mr lam said all works agents involved would continue to tackle claims conscientiously and ensure that fully substantiated claims are settled in a value for money , </s>
<s> cost effective manner . " we are confident that there will be sufficient contingency funds within the overall budget to meet all outstanding claims , " mr lam predicted . </s>
<s> as at the end of september this year , </s>
<s> the government projects in the acp were 99 per cent complete while overall the acp , including the new airport and the airport railway , was about 90 per cent complete . </s>
<s> they are : the lantau link , the north lantau expressway , </s>
<s> tung chung development phase 1 , the kwai chung and tsing yi sections of route 3 , the west kowloon expressway , the west kowloon reclamation , the western harbour crossing and phase 1 of the central reclamation . scheduled for completion next year are the two remaining projects , </s>
<s> the new airport and the airport railway . </s>
<s> " it remains our target to completing the whole acp on time and within budget , " said mr lam . </s>
<s> a total of 74 convictions were recorded in the courts in october for breaching anti @-@ pollution legislation enforced by the environmental protection department . </s>
<s> of these cases , </s>
<s> 21 were convictions made under the water pollution control ordinance ( wpco ) , 16 under the noise control ordinance ( nco ) , 11 under the air pollution control ordinance ( apco ) , 24 under the waste disposal ordinance ( wdo ) , </s>
<s> one under the dumping at sea ordinance ( daso ) and one under the ozone layer protection ordinance ( olpo ) . </s>
<s> the fines ranged from $ 2,000 to $ 60,000 . </s>
<s> win house industries limited was fined for $ 60,000 for using powered mechanical equipment without a valid construction noise permit . </s>
<s> staff of the social welfare department last ( monday ) night distributed a total of 513 blankets to street sleepers in a territory @-@ wide operation during the cold weather . </s>
<s> of the total , 149 were distributed on hong_kong island , 38 in east kowloon , 259 in west kowloon , 39 in new territories east and 28 in new territories west . </s>
<s> at the same time , the departmental hotline extended its service overnight to render assistance and advice to those in need . </s>
<s> altogether 18 calls were received between 10 pm yesterday and 9 am today . </s>
