<s> statement on new south wales supreme court 's judgment </s>
<s> follwoing is a statement issued by the department of justice : </s>
<s> " in july this year the hksar government requested the australian government to surrender ronald tse chu @-@ fai ( tse ) to hong_kong in respect of fraud and other charges relating to his alleged conduct when he was financial controller of the allied group of companies . </s>
<s> bail having been refused after his arrest , tse applied to the supreme court of new south wales , for habeas corpus . </s>
<s> " this afternoon the new south wales supreme court granted tse 's application , although on the application of the australian attorney @-@ general , </s>
<s> the execution of the judgment was stayed for 14 days , to enable time for an appeal to be lodged . </s>
<s> in the meantime tse was granted bail conditioned that he surrender his passport , </s>
<s> reside at a specified address , not approach any points of departure from australia and report to the police weekly . </s>
<s> " the point of law upon which habeas corpus was granted , related to the interpretation by the court of an australian law i.e. the australian extradition act . </s>
<s> in interpreting that law the court held that hong_kong was not an extradition country within the definition of that term in the statute . </s>
<s> " the 52 @-@ page judgment of the court is being considered by those representing the hksar government in australia , and by counsel in the department of justice . it is expected that an appeal will be lodged . </s>
<s> " the judgment does not raise doubts on hksar 's capacity to enter into agreements on the surrender of fugitive offenders ; it has simply found the australian legislation not adequate to implement the agreement between the hksar and australia . " </s>
<s> promoting a clean business environment in hong_kong </s>
<s> the secretary for justice , ms elsie leung oi @-@ sie , today ( friday ) said that the hong_kong sar 's legal system helps to promote a clean business environment in hong_kong . </s>
<s> speaking at the american chamber of commerce business ethics conference today , ms leung said the rule of law , </s>
<s> the independence of the judiciary , and the protection of human rights are three fundamental elements of the legal system that help to foster ethical conduct . </s>
<s> without it , there is no protection against corruption , nepotism or expropriation . </s>
<s> only under the rule of law are businessmen guaranteed the level playing field and the competitive environment which they need . </s>
<s> " the independence of the judiciary is another cornerstone of our legal system that promotes ethical behaviour . this independence ensures that , </s>
<s> when judges determine disputes , they are free from all types of pressure , including pressure that powerful businessmen , </s>
<s> and businessmen with powerful friends , could bring to bear , " she said . </s>
<s> commenting on the third important element of the legal system - the protection of human rights , </s>
<s> ms leung pointed out that the basic law guarantees a long list of fundamental rights , including equality before the law ; </s>
<s> freedom of speech , of association and of demonstration ; and the right to vote and stand for election . </s>
<s> in addition to these specific guarantees , </s>
<s> the basic law states that the provisions of the international convenant on civil and political rights , and the international covenant on economic , social and cultural rights , </s>
<s> as applied to hong_kong shall remain in force , and that restrictions on rights and freedoms shall not contravene them . </s>
<s> " the fact that these rights are set out in the basic law is significant for two reasons , " ms leung noted . </s>
<s> " first , the rights become fully justiciable , </s>
<s> and not simply moral aspirations or international norms . secondly , by being in the basic law , the rights are elevated to constitutional rights , </s>
<s> which cannot be restricted at the whim of the executive or legislature . </s>
<s> " our constitution , </s>
<s> and legal system , thereby send the clearest signal to the community that ethical conduct is to be encouraged , " she said . </s>
<s> turning to specific areas of the law that foster ethical business conduct , ms leung noted that the community 's view as to what is the minimum acceptable behaviour develops over time and increasingly , higher minimum standards were being set . </s>
<s> " this is particularly true in the business world where , in recent years , </s>
<s> many regulatory agencies have been established to oversee the activities of various sectors , </s>
<s> and where conduct such as insider dealing and money @-@ laundering is now subject to legislative control , " she said . </s>
<s> to illustrate her point , ms leung gave a detailed account of legislation for three specific areas of the law , </s>
<s> namely , anti @-@ corruption legislation , the control of unfair contract terms , and anti @-@ discrimination laws . </s>
<s> the prevention of bribery ordinance was enacted in 1971 , </s>
<s> legislation in respect of unfair contract terms is more recent . and anti @-@ discrimination legislation only came into force last year , along with the establishment of the equal opportunities commission . </s>
<s> " i have no doubt that , in the years to come , </s>
<s> ethical conduct in the private sector will be further reinforced by legislation on other areas of concern , " ms leung added . </s>
<s> the census and statistics department today ( friday ) released the consumer price index ( cpi ) figures for october 1997 . </s>
<s> the year @-@ on @-@ year rate of increase in the cpi ( a ) was 5.5 % in october 1997 , slightly higher than that of 5.3 % in september . </s>
<s> the year @-@ on @-@ year rate of increase in the cpi ( b ) , at 5.7 % in october 1997 , was also slightly higher than that of 5.6 % in september . </s>
<s> the corresponding rate of increase in the hang seng cpi was 5.9 % in october , same as the increase recorded in september . </s>
<s> the composite cpi , which is compiled based on the combined expenditure pattern of households covered by the three sub @-@ indices , showed a year @-@ on @-@ year increase of 5.7 % in october 1997 , </s>
<s> slightly higher than that of 5.6 % in september . </s>
<s> analysed by component , faster year @-@ on @-@ year rates of price increase than the overall average in october were recorded for housing ( 8.7 % in cpi ( a ) and 9.5 % in composite cpi ) and clothing and footwear ( 8.1 % in cpi ( a ) and 6.9 % in composite cpi ) . </s>
<s> meanwhile , those components with slower year @-@ on @-@ year rates of price increase than the overall average were durable goods ( 1.7 % in cpi ( a ) and 1.5 % in composite cpi ) ; miscellaneous services ( 2.9 % in cpi ( a ) and 2.7 % in composite cpi ) ; </s>
<s> food - excluding meals bought away from home ( 3.6 % in cpi ( a ) and 3.7 % in composite cpi ) ; fuel and light ( 4.1 % in both cpi ( a ) and composite cpi ) ; transport ( 4.1 % in cpi ( a ) and 4.2 % in composite cpi ) ; </s>
<s> meals bought away from home ( 4.8 % in cpi ( a ) and 4.3 % in composite cpi ) and alcoholic drinks and tobacco ( 5.0 % in cpi ( a ) and 4.9 % in composite cpi ) . </s>
<s> comparing october 1997 with september 1997 , the cpi ( a ) and cpi ( b ) increased by 0.5 % and 0.8 % respectively . the corresponding increases for the hang seng cpi and composite cpi were 1.0 % and 0.8 % . </s>
<s> taking the first 10 months of 1997 together , the increases in both the cpi ( a ) and cpi ( b ) averaged at 5.9 % over a year earlier . </s>
<s> the corresponding increases for the hang seng cpi and composite cpi were 6.1 % and 5.9 % . </s>
<s> for the three months ended october 1997 , the cpi ( a ) and cpi ( b ) were , on average , </s>
<s> higher by 5.8 % and 5.9 % respectively over a year earlier . </s>
<s> the corresponding increases for the hang seng cpi and composite cpi were 6.0 % and 5.9 % . </s>
<s> for the 12 months ended october 1997 , the cpi ( a ) and cpi ( b ) were , on average , </s>
<s> higher by 6.0 % and 5.9 % respectively than the preceding 12 @-@ month period . </s>
<s> the corresponding increases for the hang seng cpi and composite cpi were 6.1 % and 6.0 % . </s>
<s> the seasonally adjusted monthly rates of increase in the cpi ( a ) and cpi ( b ) averaged at 0.1 % and 0.4 % respectively during the three months ended october 1997 . </s>
<s> the corresponding increases for both the hang seng cpi and composite cpi were 0.3 % . </s>
<s> more details are given in the " consumer price index report " for october 1997 , which is available at $ 28.0 per copy from the government publications centre , </s>
<s> ground floor , low block , queensway government offices , 66 queensway , hong_kong and the publications unit of the census and statistics department , </s>
<s> 19 th floor , wanchai tower , 12 harbour road , wan chai , hong_kong . </s>
<s> for local and overseas mailings , contact should be made with the information services department , 28 th floor , siu on centre , 188 lockhart road , wan chai , hong_kong . </s>
<s> for enquiries about the indices , please telephone the consumer price index section of the census and statistics department at 2805 6403 . </s>
<s> revised procedures for government land auctions </s>
<s> prospective bidders at government land auctions will be required to register with the lands department on the day of auction before taking part in bidding , </s>
<s> " there is a consensus among the review panel on land auction arrangements and the industry that the existing land auction arrangements should be improved both to ensure that the auctions will be conducted in an orderly manner and to protect the industry from bids by persons who have no intention or capacity to bid for sites , </s>
<s> " mr pope said . </s>
<s> the new measure is a result of deliberation by the review panel and consultation with the real estate developers ' association . </s>
<s> the principle adopted is that the new measure should be simple to administer and effective in excluding non @-@ genuine bidders without causing inconvenience to the genuine . </s>
<s> registration will come into effect at the next auction on december 11 . </s>
<s> " mr pope said . </s>
<s> " the cheque will be returned to the registered person immediately upon completion of the registration procedures . </s>
<s> the list of registered persons and the recorded information will be kept in strict confidence , " he added . </s>
<s> " the registered person will then be given a numbered paddle . only bids from a paddle @-@ holder will be accepted . the paddle will be valid for all lots to be sold at the same auction , " he said . </s>
<s> " bidding paddles will be valid only on the day of issue and should be returned to our staff when the bidder leaves the auction hall , " mr pope said . </s>
<s> and from 1.45 pm until the end of the auction at a suitable location near the auction auditorium . </s>
<s> family status discrimination ordinance becomes effective </s>
<s> the family status discrimination ordinance ( fsdo ) , </s>
<s> which renders discrimination against a person on the ground of family status unlawful in employment and other specified areas of activity , </s>
<s> comes into effect with the gazettal of a commencement notice today ( friday ) . </s>
<s> a spokesman for the home affairs bureau said that following the passage of the fsdo by the previous legislative council in june this year , the government had planned to bring the ordinance into effect within the same year . </s>
<s> " the objective of the ordinance is to ensure that persons who have responsibility for the care of immediate family members , for example , </s>
<s> provision of goods , facilities and services , disposal and management of premises and activities of government . </s>
<s> " the areas of activity covered by the fsdo are similar to those of the sex discrimination ordinance ( sdo ) . </s>
<s> " on the other hand , in order to give small employers time to familiarise with the legislation , </s>
<s> business establishments with not more than five employees will have a three @-@ year grace period , " the spokesman noted . </s>
<s> in addition to the sdo and the disability discrimination ordinance ( ddo ) , the fsdo is the third piece of equal opportunities legislation in hong_kong which would be administered by the equal opportunities commission ( eoc ) . </s>
<s> " aggrieved persons may seek the assistance of the eoc and the commission will , </s>
<s> as required under the fsdo , handle complaints , conduct investigations and encourage conciliation between parties in dispute to effect a settlement as far as possible . </s>
<s> the eoc may also provide legal or other forms of assistance to those aggrieved , " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> meanwhile , three separate commencement notices which brought the family status discrimination ( proceedings by equal opportunities commission ) regulation , </s>
<s> district court equal opportunities ( amendment ) rules and labour tribunal ( general ) ( amendment ) rules into immediate operation were also gazetted today . </s>
<s> the regulation and the two court @-@ related amendment rules were approved by the provisional legislative council on october 29 and november 12 respectively . </s>
<s> " like the sex discrimination ( proceedings by equal opportunities commission ) regulation made under the sdo last year , </s>
<s> the present regulation in respect of the fsdo will enable the eoc to bring court proceedings in its own name when it appears to the commission that the claim is well founded , </s>
<s> and where the case raises a question of principle and it is in the interests of justice to do so . </s>
<s> " the two court @-@ related amendment rules seek to expand the existing court procedures applicable to cases brought under the sdo and ddo to those under the fsdo as well . </s>
<s> to ensure cases filed are heard without delay , </s>
<s> cases brought under the fsdo will also be placed in the equal opportunities list , instead of joining the queue with other civil cases , " the spokesman explained . </s>
<s> the equal opportunities list is presently being handled by judge wong hing @-@ chun who will hear cases arising from the three anti @-@ discrimination ordinances . </s>
<s> scheme aims to establish maintenance culture </s>
<s> the long @-@ term goal of the building safety inspection scheme is to cultivate and firmly establish a maintenance culture in all building owners , the director of buildings , dr choi yu @-@ leuk , </s>
<s> the scheme is aimed at promoting systematic inspection and preventive maintenance of private buildings to help reduce dangers and give early warning of unavoidable dangers . </s>
<s> addressing the urban asset management conference in the philippine capital , dr choi said the scheme was essential in achieving the objective of making the best use of resources and assets in society . </s>
<s> " the maintenance culture will take root firmly only through the effective inspection , </s>
<s> maintenance or repair of buildings , " he said . </s>
<s> " for this purpose , </s>
<s> it is necessary to organise effectively owners of each building in addition to overcoming financial and technological difficulties . </s>
<s> " this is tantamount to building a mini @-@ quasi @-@ government as a new management layer to effect building maintenance between the two traditional management levels , </s>
<s> namely , the government and individual owners . </s>
<s> " dr choi said . </s>
<s> from the technical management point of view , dr choi said , </s>
<s> the building safety inspection scheme provided an important means to a feedback system to ensure continual improvement in private @-@ sector asset management in a way similar to that in the public sector . </s>
<s> " only with the involvement of all building owners and tenants can we expect to fully identify building defects and the significant resulting problems , </s>
<s> and to find effective solutions and future preventive measures . </s>
<s> " in this feedback process , </s>
<s> the government can identify research and development needs , co @-@ ordinate the work and guide the application of the results , </s>
<s> in addition to performing the traditional control function , " he said . </s>
<s> dr choi said that central to the building safety inspection scheme was the building safety assurance concept which operated on the premise that deterioration of materials in buildings could be arrested if buildings were to be maintained or repaired by appropriate methods according to specified physical standards . </s>
<s> " such standards will need to be determined in relation to the level of building safety assurance to be achieved under the scheme which in turn should be commensurate with societal optimum balance between redevelopment and repair . </s>
<s> " this will require risks assessment to be made taking into consideration the aspirations and affordability levels of society , </s>
<s> " he added . </s>
<s> support for services sector given additional funding </s>
<s> the government 's pledge to promoting services industry is given a boost . the provisional legislative council finance committee today ( friday ) approved an increase in commitment of $ 50 million for the services support fund ( ssf ) . </s>
<s> set up by the government in july 1996 with an initial commitment of $ 50 million , the ssf aims to provide financial support for projects which would benefit the growth and promote the competitiveness of the services industries of hong_kong . </s>
<s> the fund is administered by the industry department upon the advice of the ssf vetting committee . </s>
<s> organisations with project proposals meeting the ssf objectives may apply for funding support . </s>
<s> such organisations may include services @-@ support bodies ; trade and industry associations ; higher education institutions ; </s>
<s> and professional bodies and research institutes . </s>
<s> private companies can also apply if their projects will bring benefits to the service that go beyond the interests of individual enterprises . </s>
<s> a total of 27 projects of $ 49.5 million had been approved so far since the setting up of the ssf . </s>
<s> the approved projects cover a wide spectrum of sectors , </s>
<s> including information technology , wholesale and retail , import and export trade , tourism , transportation , catering and professional services . </s>
<s> a spokesman for the industry department said : " judging from the enthusiastic response as reflected by the number of applications , </s>
<s> there is strong demand for funding support from the ssf . " </s>
<s> " the addition of $ 50 million to the fund will enable us to provide financial support to more new and worthwhile projects , " the spokesman added . </s>
<s> applications for hcfcs free quota invited </s>
<s> the environmental protection department ( epd ) today ( friday ) invites applications for free quotas to import 34 types of hydrochlorofluorocarbons ( hcfcs ) for local consumption in 1998 . </s>
<s> applications for free quotas are open to all companies which have registered under the ozone layer protection ordinance . allocations will be made on a need basis . </s>
<s> importers with proven records of using normal and free quotas for retained imports of hcfcs in 1997 will be automatically allocated with normal quotas . </s>
<s> principal environmental protection officer , mr raymond leung , said : </s>
<s> " according to the montreal protocol to protect the ozone layer , </s>
<s> the hcfcs quotas for hong_kong in 1998 should be capped at 2526 tonnes , in terms of the most commonly used refrigerant hcfc @-@ 22 . </s>
<s> " forty per cent of the total available quotas for 1998 are allocated as free quotas in two phases . </s>
<s> " half of these will be allocated in this exercise while the remaining ones will be distributed in phase 2 free quota allocation exercise . " </s>
<s> mr leung said this quota system had been introduced to control the local consumption of hcfcs so as to fulfil hong_kong 's international obligations under the protocol . </s>
<s> " hong_kong 's consumption of hcfcs would be reduced in phases to zero by the year 2030 according to the schedule of the protocol , </s>
<s> " he added . </s>
<s> applications for the phase 1 free quotas should be submitted in person to epd 's air management group , </s>
<s> 33 rd floor , revenue tower , 5 gloucester road , wan chai , hong_kong by 5 pm on december 30 , 1997 . </s>
<s> late applications will not be accepted . </s>
<s> application forms are available at the above address . </s>
<s> further details can be obtained from the air management group on 2594 6242 or 2594 6243 . </s>
<s> planning standards and guidelines on industry revised </s>
<s> the government has revised chapter five of the hong_kong planning standards and guidelines ( hkpsg ) on industry to take account of the latest structural changes in the trade , </s>
<s> " the revised guidelines are based mainly on the findings and recommendations of a consultancy study on the provision of industrial premises and development of planning guidelines and design parameters for new industrial areas and business parks , which was completed in july 1997 , " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> the study recommended that new industrial areas be developed on the basis of up @-@ to @-@ date planning standards and guidelines and that the choice of premises and uses permitted in industrial area be broadened . </s>
<s> " these involves a new industrial land use typology for the planning and reservation of industrial land , </s>
<s> as well as planning and development parameters such as minimum lot sizes , site coverage , </s>
<s> plot ratios , road widths , standards for the provision of parking and loading / unloading facilities , support facilities and provision of amenities , </s>
<s> " the spokesman explained . </s>
<s> " as a result , </s>
<s> a new industrial land use typology comprising general industrial uses and special industrial uses , has been adopted in the revised chapter , " he said . </s>
<s> the general industrial uses include the existing industrial use classification which are accommodated in ordinary multi @-@ storey factory buildings , purpose @-@ built godowns and dual @-@ purpose industrial and office buildings . the special industrial uses are characterised by and accommodated in specially @-@ designed premises , </s>
<s> such as an industrial estate , a science park and a business estate . </s>
<s> " the methodology for forecasting industrial land requirements has also been revised and new development parametres including locational , transport , </s>
<s> parking , loading and unloading requirements are provided for various types of industrial use , " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> " guidelines on layout design , landscaping , the provision of open space and supporting facilities are introduced in order to improve the overall quality of the industrial areas , </s>
<s> " he said . </s>
<s> " the revised standards and guidelines have received general support during the consultation exercise among relevant advisory bodies and industrial @-@ related organisations , " he added . </s>
<s> hkpsg comprises a series of 11 chapters which are sold separately . each chapter is devoted to a particular aspect of land use or facility . </s>
<s> the revised chapter five of hkpsg is now on sale at $ 32 per copy at the government publications centre , ground floor , low block , queensway government offices , </s>
<s> 66 queensway , hong_kong . </s>
<s> water quality to improve with sewerage works in stanley </s>
<s> the quality of sea water and sanitary condition in stanley and tai tam will be significantly improved when the stanley area sewerage and sewage disposal project is completed in 1999 . </s>
<s> a contract for the construction of branch sewers to collect sewage from about 50 government and private properties in these unsewered areas was signed by the drainage services department today ( friday ) . </s>
<s> " the collected sewage will be centrally treated at the existing sewage treatment plant in stanley , " a spokesman for the department said . </s>
<s> " there will also be geotechnical and building works to improve the working environment in the cavern of the plant , </s>
<s> " he added . </s>
<s> the contract was awarded to kwan kee construction co. ltd. at a cost of $ 22.1 million . </s>
<s> meanwhile , another contract on the laying of sewers in shek o , </s>
<s> chung hom kok , repulse bay , middle bay , deep water bay and shouson hill areas will be signed next month . </s>
<s> all the collected sewage will undergo secondary treatment at the stanley sewage treatment plant before discharging into the sea . </s>
<s> the project is expected to complete also in 1999 . </s>
