<s> source of contaminated vegetables traced </s>
<s> the department of health this ( monday ) afternoon successfully traced the source of supply of sugar pea shoot to a local supermarket after meeting its management . </s>
<s> a department spokesman said : " after checking the relevant documents , </s>
<s> it was found that the consignment of vegetable which had found to be contaminated with the pesticide , methamidophos , was originated from a farm in guangdong . " the department has liaised with the guangdong import and export commodities inspection bureau for the necessary follow @-@ up action . </s>
<s> " </s>
<s> in the course of investigating the food poisoning case involving a japanese women who had consumed chinese chrysanthemum and fallen ill last friday night , the department of health had identified the supermarket and took samples of chinese chrysanthemum and sugar pea shoot from the same consignment for laboratory tests . </s>
<s> samples of the latter vegetable were found to be contaminated with methamidophos . </s>
<s> meanwhile , the department of the health today received reports of another food poisoning case . </s>
<s> the case involved two elderly women , aged 82 and 72 respectively , who had consumed chinese chrysanthemum on november 22 . </s>
<s> remnant of the food was tested and found to contain residue of methamidophos . </s>
<s> the two patients were treated at queen mary hospital . the 72 @-@ year @-@ old woman was discharged while the older lady is hospitalised . </s>
<s> government to set up land disposal committee </s>
<s> the secretary for planning , environment and lands , mr bowen leung , </s>
<s> said today ( monday ) that a land disposal committee would be established to monitor the progress of the land disposal programme ( ldp ) for the coming five years . </s>
<s> speaking at the seminar on " land bank policy " organised by the hong_kong project management exchange centre limited , </s>
<s> mr leung said that the ldp would roll forward each year and the committee would also work out the second 5 @-@ year ldp with details expected to be announced in march 1998 . </s>
<s> mr leung said the committee will hold its first meeting next month ( december ) . </s>
<s> " in order to increase land supply and to build up land reserve , the government has committed to developing 10 strategic growth areas , </s>
<s> including the remaining part of central and wan chai reclamation , green island and southeast kowloon etc. </s>
<s> " it is estimated that these strategic growth areas will provide sufficient land to build 270,000 housing units capable of accommodating 720,000 people between 2006 and 2011 and these plans will be more firmed up after the relevant studies are completed , </s>
<s> " he said . </s>
<s> mr leung pointed out that due to the scarcity of land resources , </s>
<s> the government needed to carry out reclamation projects , as appropriate , and to set up land reserve so as to cope with future development as well as to meet public demand for housing . </s>
<s> " the government will provide enough land for housing through the five @-@ year ldp . together with the residential redevelopment projects carried out by both the public and private sectors , </s>
<s> the government is confident to achieve the target of providing not less than 85,000 housing units a year with effect from 1999. " </s>
<s> mr leung noted that despite that the property market had softened during the past few weeks , </s>
<s> the government 's commitment to provide sufficient land to meet housing demand would not be affected . </s>
<s> he stressed that the government would continue to dispose of land according to the ldp . </s>
<s> in response to public concern on the adverse impact of the reclamation projects , </s>
<s> mr leung stressed that the government would not carry out reclamation projects unless deemed necessary . </s>
<s> " the government will carry out comprehensive assessment of the reclamation projects and where required , </s>
<s> mitigation measures would be implemented in order to protect the harbour from any unacceptable damage , " he added . </s>
<s> ec endorses broad operational approach for education fund </s>
<s> the education commission ( ec ) discussed today ( monday ) the broad approach for the mode of operation of the quality education fund ( qef ) . </s>
<s> speaking after the ec meeting , the chairman of the commission , professor rosie young , said : </s>
<s> " we welcome the endorsement by the chief executive at his first policy address of our recommendation in the report no. 7 to set up an qef to promote quality education . " </s>
<s> " we look forward to the provisional legislative council 's approval in december for the grant of $ 5 billion to establish the qef and a support unit within the education and manpower bureau ( emb ) to administer the fund , " professor young added . </s>
<s> " ec will assume an overall advisory role to the government on the operation of the fund . </s>
<s> a qef steering committee will be set up under ec to enable it to perform this role . </s>
<s> " under the steering committee , a vetting committee will be set up to further refine and decide on various aspects of the operation mechanism , including the assessment criteria , </s>
<s> the design of the application forms , the agreement with the trustee , frequency of calls for applications and meetings , and the monitoring mechanism , </s>
<s> " she said . </s>
<s> also , similar to the arrangement for the subsidised schools provident fund , the director of accounting services ( das ) will be appointed to handle the investment of the fund . </s>
<s> a qef investment advisory committee will be established to set policies for and to monitor the investment of the fund . </s>
<s> members of this committee should comprise the chairman of the qef steering / vetting committee , the secretary for education and manpower , the secretary for the treasury , </s>
<s> the director of education and the das or their representatives . </s>
<s> " we anticipate the qef to be able to start operating in early 1998 . </s>
<s> the establishment of the fund should go a long way to providing an effective means to encourage bottom @-@ up initiatives , and the opportunity for the community to participate in the building of quality culture , " said professor young . </s>
<s> the meeting also discussed the use of information technology ( it ) in schools . </s>
<s> professor young said : </s>
<s> " we look forward to government 's comprehensive strategy early next year to promote the use of it in schools to enhance teaching and learning . " </s>
<s> the government has accepted recommendations by a consultancy study which , when implemented , </s>
<s> may speed up approvals given by the lands department ( ld ) by up to three months , saving about half the processing time . </s>
<s> the study was on the ld 's consent scheme , which deals with applications for the sale and purchase of units in uncompleted developments and the approval of deeds of mutual covenants ( dmcs ) . </s>
<s> the consultancy study was commissioned under the helping business programme as part of the government 's initiatives to increase the supply of residential units for sale in the property market . </s>
<s> the consultants have come up with detailed recommendations to address all the problems identified : </s>
<s> * government requirements and procedures for the issue of consents and dmc approvals should be clearly set out for both applicants and ld staff in comprehensive guidance notes , </s>
<s> including requirements relating to the management of government premises to be incorporated into the dmcs for government premises . </s>
<s> * ld should attempt to draft model dmc clauses for government requirements to facilitate easy adoption by developers in their documents , thus reducing the time required for vetting by ld staff . </s>
<s> * training programmes should be designed to help ld staff adopt a proactive approach in resolving problems . </s>
<s> * a dedicated office should be set up in the ld to support staff in resolving differences among the parties and improving communication . </s>
<s> * more dmc approval cases should be contracted out to the private sector so that ld staff may accord top priority to large residential cases . </s>
<s> " we will positively consider these recommendations for adoption and have set up a departmental steering group to take them forward for implementation , </s>
<s> " the principal solicitor of the ld , mr tom berry , said . </s>
<s> " because cases vary significantly in size and complexity , it is not possible to precisely quantify the potential savings in time which may result from these recommendations , </s>
<s> " mr berry said . </s>
<s> " but on the basis of a typical case , </s>
<s> the consultants estimate that about two months may be saved for an application for consent to sell and up to three months for approval of a dmc , " he said . </s>
<s> response to drowning at kowloon park </s>
<s> in response to media enquiries with regard to a drowning case at kowloon park last saturday , </s>
<s> a spokesman for the fire services department today ( monday ) said there was no argument between any parties concerned in the rescue operation . </s>
<s> there was also no delay in treatment and conveyance of the patient to hospital , he added . </s>
<s> he gave the following details : </s>
<s> " ambulance a 192 of tsim sha tsui fire station and paramedic ambulance a 243 of tsim tung ambulance depot were tasked at 4.32 pm to attend a drowning case at kowloon park swimming pool . </s>
<s> a 192 arrived at scene at 4.34 pm . </s>
<s> lifeguards at scene reported to the ambulance crew that a drowning patient was found to have breathing and heartbeats . </s>
<s> however , the ambulance crew checked the patient and found that there were no breathing and heartbeats . </s>
<s> he was then conveyed by a 192 to queen elizabeth hospital . the crew of a 243 also boarded ambulance a 192 to assist treatment . " </s>
