<s> november issue of monthly digest of statistics on sale </s>
<s> two feature articles entitled " statistics on electronic products and the electronics industry " and " business receipts indices for service industries " are published in the november 1997 issue of the hong_kong monthly digest of statistics , which is now on sale . </s>
<s> the electronics industry is one of the major export earners in hong_kong . </s>
<s> statistics on electronic products and the electronics industry have been regularly compiled by the census and statistics department to facilitate users in understanding developments in these areas . </s>
<s> as there is no international definition on electronic products and the electronics industry , </s>
<s> a study on the subject was conducted by the census and statistics department sometime ago to devise a set of principles for classifying electronic products and electronics industry for use in compiling the related statistics in hong_kong . </s>
<s> the classification of electronic products and electronics industry are subsequently updated annually to take into account the latest development of the electronics industry . </s>
<s> the article , " statistics on electronic products and the electronics industry " , introduces the currently adopted classifications of electronic products and the electronics industry . </s>
<s> the performance of electronic products and the electronics industry as reflected in trade statistics and industrial statistics in recent years is also discussed . </s>
<s> the census and statistics department also started to compile quarterly business receipts indices in 1993 to provide statistical data on current performance of 12 selected service industries . </s>
<s> in support of government 's initiative in service promotion , </s>
<s> the department has developed and published more detailed business receipts indices starting from the reference quarter of the first quarter of 1996 . </s>
<s> in addition to the existing indices for 12 service industries , new indices for another nine industries and two service domains are compiled . </s>
<s> the nine newly compiled industry @-@ based indices relate to wholesale / retail , air transport , land transport , maritime transport , telecommunications , financial markets and fund management , real estate , </s>
<s> the two new service domains are tourism , convention and exhibition services and computer and information services . </s>
<s> the article entitled " business receipts indices for service industries " gives details on the coverage and compilation method of the new business receipts indices and describes the latest changes in business performance of service industries . </s>
<s> the november 1997 issue of the hong_kong monthly digest of statistics is now on sale at $ 34 a copy . </s>
<s> in addition to the above two feature articles , </s>
<s> it contains the most up @-@ to - date information on hong_kong 's development regarding economic growth , labour market , inflation and many other social and economic issues . </s>
<s> purchase of this publication can be made at the government publications centre , ground floor , low block , queensway government offices , 66 queensway , hong_kong . </s>
<s> the publication is also available for sale at the publications unit of the census and statistics department , 19 th floor , wanchai tower , 12 harbour road , wan chai , hong_kong . </s>
<s> regular subscription can also be arranged with the publications sales office of the information services department on 2598 8194 . </s>
