<s> perimeter fence remains open to public </s>
<s> in response to media enquiries on the perimeter fence being erected for the central government offices ( cgo ) at lower albert road , </s>
<s> an sar government spokesman stressed today ( thursday ) that it was not aimed at detering protesters nor was it constructed solely because of the relocation of the chief executive 's office to cgo . </s>
<s> he explained that the construction was a normal maintenance exercise since the old fence was built a long time ago and had to be replaced . </s>
<s> in so doing , he said , the government has taken the opportunity to strengthen and extend it so as to improve the overall security of cgo . </s>
<s> the spokesman assured the public that the fence would in no way " segregate " the hksar government from the general public . </s>
<s> " the government remains an open , efficient and accountable government and is committed to listening to community views and debating publicly issues of importance to the community , </s>
<s> " he added . </s>
<s> the new fence will not be closed unless there is a real and very serious security problem . </s>
<s> in fact , it will remain open most of the time and will not affect normal access to the cgo by the general public . </s>
<s> petitions can be staged as at present . </s>
<s> the open and underground car parks in the cgo will also be opened to the public after office hours and during public holidays . </s>
<s> residential mortgage survey results for october 1997 </s>
<s> mortgage lending continued to slow in october according to the results of the latest monthly survey conducted by the hong_kong monetary authority ( hkma ) . </s>
<s> gross new loans made during the month decreased significantly by 29.8 % to $ 17.9 billion . </s>
<s> the average size of new loans also dropped to $ 1.95 million in october compared to $ 2.13 million in september . </s>
<s> as a result , the amount of outstanding mortgage loans grew at a much slower rate of 0.7 % to $ 420.8 billion in october , </s>
<s> compared to the 2.9 % increase in september . </s>
<s> this is the smallest monthly increase since august 1996 . </s>
<s> new loans approved during the month increased by 10.8 % to $ 22 billion , reflecting the slight revival of market activity in late september and early october . </s>
<s> loans approved during the month but not yet drawn also increased by 25.1 % from $ 11.8 billion in september to $ 14.7 billion in october . </s>
<s> the annualised rate of growth of outstanding loans in the three months to october decreased to 25.7 % from 41.8 % in september . </s>
<s> the average change over the last 12 months also decreased to 32 % from 34 % in september . </s>
<s> on the pricing front , mortgage rates further hardened in october . </s>
<s> of the new loans approved during october , only 9.5 % were priced at best lending rate , well below the 23.7 % in september . </s>
<s> loans granted at more than 0.25 % above best lending rate increased significantly to 59 % in october from 40.1 % in september . </s>
<s> " given the current market conditions , we can expect reduced market activity and hence the slower pace of lending to continue for the time being , </s>
<s> " said deputy chief executive of the hong_kong monetary authority , mr david carse . </s>
<s> gross loans for the purchase of properties in mainland china increased to $ 395 million in october from $ 283 million in september . </s>
<s> the amount of outstanding loans increased by 3.87 % to $ 7.59 billion . </s>
<s> study on additional cross @-@ border links </s>
<s> the planning department has commissioned a feasibility study on additional cross @-@ border links , a spokesman for the department said today ( thursday ) . </s>
<s> " the study will investigate the environmental and ecological impacts of two new road crossings proposed by the shenzhen and the zhuhai authorities , </s>
<s> namely the five @-@ kilometre shenzhen @-@ hong_kong western corridor across deep bay and the 27 @-@ kilometre lingdingyang bridge across the lower estuary of the pearl river , " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> " their implications on land use planning , land acquisition , economic and financial viability , </s>
<s> engineering feasibility and preliminary design will also be looked into . </s>
<s> " the study , due to start tomorrow , is the second of a three @-@ stage further investigation proposed in a preliminary study known as the crosslinks study , </s>
<s> it also outlined a possible network of roads within hong_kong to connect the new road crossings . </s>
<s> " however , </s>
<s> the preliminary study highlighted a number of important issues which required detailed investigations before a decision could be made to implement any of the proposed road projects , </s>
<s> " the spokesman explained . </s>
<s> the first stage of the feasibility study began in last april to focus on cross @-@ boundary traffic and existing crossing capacities . </s>
<s> the second stage , </s>
<s> running in parallel with the first , is due for completion by mid @-@ 1999 at a cost of about $ 21 million . </s>
<s> an agreement was signed between the director of planning , dr peter pun , and a representative from the consultancy firm - mouchel asia limited . </s>
<s> " upon its completion , the government will be in a better position to take a view on the implementation of the proposed road projects , </s>
<s> " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> " the last stage of the study , </s>
<s> on highway engineering feasibility and project impact assessments , will follow if a decision to proceed is made , " he said . </s>
<s> government pushes fire prevention message </s>
<s> in the wake of several tragic fires last year which claimed a number of lives and caused serious property damage , the deputy director of home affairs , mr augustine cheng , </s>
<s> reiterated today ( thursday ) the government 's commitment to raising public awareness of fire prevention in buildings , especially in commercial premises , to prevent a recurrence of such tragedies . </s>
<s> " the home affairs department will allocate more resources to promote the fire prevention message , " said mr cheng after a fire drill held at one and two harbourfront , </s>
<s> hung hom . </s>
<s> he said that professional building management was essential in ensuring the proper functioning of fire safety facilities in buildings . </s>
<s> tenants of the buildings must also familiarise themselves with fire safety measures and equipment in the building to avoid panic in the event of fire . </s>
<s> " the security bureau , the home affairs department and the fire services department have organised a number of talks , seminars and courses this year on prevention of fire in buildings , </s>
<s> " mr cheng said . </s>
<s> a large @-@ scale seminar on building management focusing on the topic would be held next year , he added . </s>
<s> " we hope that with the government 's active promotion and the public co @-@ operation , </s>
<s> fire prevention will become an integral part of building management and accepted by all tenants so that the risk of fire will be cut to the minimum , </s>
<s> " mr cheng said . </s>
<s> the fire drill , jointly organised by the kowloon city district office , the fire services department and hutchison whampoa properties limited , </s>
<s> was aimed at enhancing the public awareness of fire prevention at commercial buildings . </s>
<s> some 200 representatives of major tenants in the two buildings took part in the exercise . </s>
<s> officiating guests included the deputy director of home affairs , mr augustine cheng ; the acting senior divisional officer of the fire services department , mr wong kin @-@ cheong ; and the managing director of hutchison whampoa properties limited , mr raymond chow . </s>
<s> external trade figures for october 1997 </s>
<s> in october 1997 , </s>
<s> the value of hong_kong 's re @-@ exports and imports recorded notable increases over a year earlier , while that of domestic exports rose further . these are shown in the external trade figures for october 1997 released today ( thursday ) by the census and statistics department . </s>
<s> the value of total exports ( comprising re @-@ exports and domestic exports ) in october 1997 increased significantly by 10 % over a year earlier to $ 143.0 billion . </s>
<s> within this total , the value of re @-@ exports increased by 11 % to $ 122.9 billion , </s>
<s> while the value of domestic exports increased by 3.1 % to $ 20.0 billion . </s>
<s> the value of imports increased by 11 % over a year earlier to $ 152.9 billion in october 1997 . </s>
<s> as the value of total exports in october 1997 was smaller than that of total imports , a visible trade deficit of $ 10.0 billion , </s>
<s> equivalent to 6.5 % of the value of imports , was recorded . </s>
<s> this was slightly larger than the corresponding deficit of $ 8.2 billion , equivalent to 5.9 % of the value of imports , in october 1996 . </s>
<s> for the first 10 months of 1997 as a whole , the value of total exports increased by 3.8 % over the same period last year . </s>
<s> within this total , the value of re @-@ exports rose by 4.6 % , while the value of domestic exports decreased by 0.7 % . </s>
<s> the value of imports registered an increase of 5.6 % . </s>
<s> over the same period , a visible trade deficit of $ 137.5 billion , </s>
<s> equivalent to 10 % of the value of imports , was recorded . </s>
<s> this was larger than the deficit of $ 110.3 billion , equivalent to 8.7 % of the value of imports , recorded in the same period in 1996 . </s>
<s> commenting on the latest trade statistics , a government secretariat spokesman said that growth in the value of hong_kong 's re @-@ exports picked up significantly in october 1997 , following modest increases in the past three months . </s>
<s> concurrently , the value of domestic exports recorded a year @-@ on @-@ year increase for the third consecutive month in october . </s>
<s> taken together , the value of total exports grew by 10 % in october over a year earlier , and by 3.8 % in the first 10 months of 1997 as a whole . </s>
<s> as export prices remained on an easing trend so far this year , growth in total exports in real terms in the first 10 months of 1997 was likely to be faster than that in 1996 . </s>
<s> meanwhile , retained imports grew further in october , amidst sustained domestic demand . </s>
<s> the spokesman also observed that the visible trade deficit had narrowed during the period july @-@ october 1997 , compared with the first half of the year . </s>
<s> the ratio of the deficit to the total value of imports came down substantially from 17.6 % in march to 6.5 % in october . </s>
<s> for july @-@ october 1997 as a whole , the corresponding ratio was 7.1 % , lower than that of 12.6 % recorded in the first half of the year . </s>
<s> a more detailed analysis of hong_kong 's external trade for october 1997 , by commodity and country , will be released in mid @-@ december 1997 . </s>
