<s> he was educated in hong_kong . </s>
<s> he joined the government as a paralegal in 1960 . </s>
<s> he was called to the english bar in 1970 and worked as a crown counsel from 1970 to 1974. he went into private practice as a barrister in 1974 until he was appointed director of public prosecutions in 1994 . </s>
<s> he was appointed queen 's counsel in 1995 . </s>
