<s> sg to return from us tomorrow </s>
<s> the solicitor general , mr daniel fung , will return to hong_kong tomorrow ( saturday ) after a two @-@ week visit to london and the united_states . </s>
<s> during his visit to new york , boston and washington dc in the united_states between november 20 and 28 , </s>
<s> mr fung delivered a number of speeches and met with members of the legal profession , academics and think @-@ tankers . </s>
<s> in new york , mr fung delivered a keynote speech " hong_kong 's changing legal environment " at a conference " doing business in china and hong_kong post 1997 " organised by new york university law school . </s>
<s> while in boston , he visited the harvard law school and exchanged views with the faculty members on a wide range of issues . </s>
<s> during his last leg of visit in washington dc , mr fung gave talks at a breakfast meeting co @-@ hosted by the american bar association and the us @-@ china business council , and a luncheon hosted by the heritage foundation . </s>
<s> earlier , mr fung visited london and took the opportunity to address justinians in london and delivered a speech at the college of law . </s>
<s> works bureau exhibition shows continuous growth of hk </s>
<s> the government is fully committed to ensuring that necessary investments are made to provide hong_kong with a high quality infrastructure to sustain our development and economic growth . </s>
<s> this was said by the secretary for works , </s>
<s> mr kwong hon @-@ sang , at a reception today ( friday ) in celebration of the " build for the future " exhibition being held at the hong_kong convention and exhibition centre ( hkcec ) , wan chai . </s>
<s> mr kwong said that apart from the airport core programme which cost $ 155 billion , </s>
<s> the government had spent over $ 72 billion on public works projects in the five years between 1992 and 1997 . </s>
<s> " in this current year we are managing around 1,000 on @-@ going and new projects , with an estimated expenditure of over $ 20 billion . looking ahead , </s>
<s> we expect that this level of expenditure will be sustained throughout the next few years , " he said . </s>
<s> speaking at the same occasion , dr the hon sze @-@ yuen chung , the executive council convenor and a trained engineer , </s>
<s> said he was confident that continuing infrastructure development would help maintain hong_kong 's position as a leading international commercial , financial and business centre . </s>
<s> he said that those who had viewed the exhibition would agree that the very active infrastructure development programme in a geographically small and restrictive city like hong_kong had been very impressive . </s>
<s> through presentation of the latest achievements in the construction of major projects , </s>
<s> it also provided ample evidence that hong_kong was capable of offering professional engineering services and expertise in respect of engineering planning , contract management and works procurement on an international level , said dr chung . </s>
<s> the " build for the future " exhibition is organised jointly by the works bureau and eight departments to promote hong_kong 's expertise and professional services in infrastructure development and construction . </s>
<s> these departments are : architectural services department ; </s>
<s> civil engineering department ; drainage services department ; electrical and mechanical services department ; highways department ; new airport projects co @-@ ordination office ; territory development department and water supplies department . </s>
<s> the exhibition , now being held in room 301 a , hong_kong convention and exhibition centre , </s>
<s> will last until 6 pm tomorrow ( saturday ) . </s>
<s> monetary statistics for october 1997 published </s>
<s> total deposits and loans and advances both fell slightly during october 1997 . </s>
<s> deposits </s>
<s> total deposits decreased by 0.7 % in october , against a 2 % rise in september . </s>
<s> during the month , demand and time deposits dropped by 1.9 % and 2.9 % respectively , while savings deposits fell for four months in a row , </s>
<s> down by a significant 7.8 % . </s>
<s> the fall in time deposits was partly due to the high base of comparison in september , </s>
<s> when such deposits were boosted by placements of new share subscription monies before the refund dates . </s>
<s> the expansion in foreign currency deposits was attributable primarily to a rise of 8.7 % in us $ deposits , </s>
<s> which more than offset a 0.3 % fall in non @-@ us $ foreign currency deposits . loans and advances </s>
<s> total loans and advances declined slightly by 0.2 % in october , compared with a rise of 0.8 % in september . </s>
<s> during the month , offshore loans recorded a mild growth of 0.6 % , having declined for three consecutive months . </s>
<s> on the other hand , domestic credit contracted by 0.9 % , </s>
<s> after expanding for six months in a row . of the local loans , both loans for trade financing and other loans fell by 0.9 % . </s>
<s> during october , hk $ loans registered a drop of 2.3 % , having increased continuously since april this year . </s>
<s> foreign currency loans , however , rebounded by 1.4 % , </s>
<s> after declining for three consecutive months . </s>
<s> as the decrease in hk $ deposits was larger than that of hk $ loans , the hk $ loan @-@ to @-@ deposit ratio rose further , from 112.1 % at end @-@ september , </s>
<s> to 113.9 % at end @-@ october . </s>
<s> money supply </s>
<s> in line with the fall in hk $ deposits , all monetary aggregates registered a decline in october , </s>
<s> with hk $ m 1 decreasing by 2.1 % and hk $ m 2 and hk $ m 3 falling by 3.8 % respectively . </s>
<s> in the twelve months to october , the expansion of hk $ m 1 decelerated to 5.9 % while hk $ m 2 and hk $ m 3 moderated to 14 % . </s>
<s> the annual growth of broad money supply in october was in line with the pace of nominal gdp growth . </s>
<s> works to reduce flooding in north district </s>
<s> the government will construct water channels along the lower and upper indus river as well as the river beas to reduce flooding in the north district of the new territories . </s>
<s> this is part of the long @-@ term river training works in the indus basin . </s>
<s> embankments will be built in a section of lower indus between the west of kowloon canton railway 's lo wu station and the north of fu tei au road . existing water channels will be excavated and widened . </s>
<s> similar works will be carried out at the river beas , between the east of ho sheung heung village and the west of river sutlej . </s>
<s> the project , due to begin next year and complete in 2001 , will cover about seven hectares of foreshore and sea bed in the area . </s>
<s> likewise , works will be carried out in a section of the upper indus to the north of sheung shui , covering about six hectares of foreshores and sea bed . </s>
<s> the project will begin in 1999 and be completed in 2002 . </s>
<s> draft ho man tin outline zoning plan approved </s>
<s> the chief executive in council has approved the draft ho man tin outline zoning plan ( ozp ) to provide a statutory land use framework for the development and redevelopment in the area . </s>
<s> the ozp covers an area of about 208 hectares which , when fully developed , is expected to have a total population of about 111,000 , </s>
<s> 54 per cent in public housing and 46 per cent in private . </s>
<s> about 78.4 hectares , or 37.7 per cent of the total area , </s>
<s> have been zoned for residential development . </s>
<s> these include 36.1 hectares for high @-@ density residential developments , 30.4 hectares for medium @-@ density and 11.9 hectares for low @-@ rise , low @-@ density developments . </s>
<s> about 70 hectares , or 33.6 per cent of the total area , </s>
<s> have been zoned " government / institution / community " ( gic ) for the development of facilities to serve local residents and to meet territorial needs . </s>
<s> about 12.6 hectares , or six per cent of the total area , </s>
<s> have been zoned " open space " to provide land for active and passive recreational uses . </s>
<s> perth street sports ground and sheung shing street park are within this zone . </s>
<s> about 0.4 hectare , or 0.2 per cent of the land area , has been zoned " other specified uses " . </s>
<s> these specific uses include the petrol filling stations at argyle street , waterloo road and princess margaret road . </s>
<s> about 7.6 hectares , or 3.7 per cent of the total area , </s>
<s> have been zoned " green belt " for the preservation of the natural landscape . </s>
<s> it covers mainly the slopes to the east of the ho man tin high level service reservoirs and to the south @-@ east of the other two service reservoirs near valley road estate in the southern part of the area . </s>
<s> the remaining 39.3 hectares , or 18.9 per cent of the total area , have been reserved mainly for road and pedestrian street uses . </s>
<s> the approved plan ( no. s / k 7 / 8 ) is available for public inspection during office hours at : </s>
<s> * planning department , 16 th floor , murray building , garden road , </s>
<s> * kowloon district planning office , 11 th floor , leighton centre , </s>
<s> 77 leighton road , </s>
<s> * kowloon city district office , rooms 1706 @-@ 1713 , one harbourfront , 18 @-@ 22 tak fung street , </s>
<s> copies of the plan are on sale at the survey and mapping office , lands department , 14 th floor , murray building , garden road , central , hong_kong and the kowloon map sales office , </s>
<s> draft tsuen wan ozp amended </s>
<s> the town planning board today ( friday ) announced several amendments to the draft tsuen wan outline zoning plan ( ozp ) to alleviate the industrial / residential interface problem at the periphery of the industrial area in tsuen wan . </s>
<s> the amendments involve the rezoning of three sites with a total area of about 2.67 hectares , </s>
<s> near the junction of ma tau pa road and yeung uk road from " industrial " to " comprehensive development area ( 1 ) " to facilitate comprehensive redevelopment in the area . </s>
<s> for environmental reasons , non @-@ residential development acting as a " land use buffer " will be permitted in these sites . </s>
<s> a corresponding amendment is made to add the " comprehensive development area ( 1 ) " zone to the notes of the ozp . </s>
<s> another amendment is to add a remark to the notes of the ozp to state the maximum building height for " village type development " . the amended plan ( no. </s>
<s> s / tw / 8 ) is available for public inspection until december 19 during office hours at the following locations : </s>
<s> * planning department , 16 th floor , murray building , garden road , central , hong_kong ; </s>
<s> tsuen wan government offices , 38 sai lau kok road , tsuen wan , new territories ; </s>
<s> and </s>
<s> tsuen wan station multi @-@ storey carpark building , 174 @-@ 208 castle peak road , tsuen wan , new territories . </s>
<s> any person affected by the amendments may submit written objections to the secretary of the town planning board , c / o planning department , </s>
<s> 13 th floor , murray building , garden road , central , hong_kong , before december 19 . </s>
<s> copies of the plan are available for sale at the survey and mapping office , lands department , 14 th floor , murray building , garden road , central , hong_kong and the kowloon map sales office , </s>
<s> draft tsz wan shan , diamond hill and san po kong ozp approved </s>
<s> the chief executive in council has approved the draft tsz wan shan , diamond hill and san po kong outline zoning plan ( ozp ) to provide a statutory land use framework for the development and redevelopment in the areas . </s>
<s> the plan covers an area of about 325 hectares . </s>
<s> upon full development , the district is expected to house 177,600 people , </s>
<s> 77 per cent in public housing and 23 per cent in private . </s>
<s> for that purpose , 32 per cent of the total area ( about 105.1 hectares ) , </s>
<s> has been zoned " residential ( group a ) " . this zone covers existing and planned public and private residential developments . </s>
<s> major planned residential developments include a private sector participation scheme ( psps ) development at hammer hill road , and another at part of the ex @-@ blackdown barracks site , plus a sandwich class housing at fung tak road . </s>
<s> about 7.2 hectares of land to the south of the diamond hill mtr station , </s>
<s> or two per cent of the total area , have been zoned " comprehensive development area " ( cda ) for a comprehensive commercial / residential development with community facilities . </s>
<s> maximum gross floor areas of 87,520 square metres and 150,000 square metres are respectively laid down for domestic and non @-@ domestic uses within the cda zone . </s>
<s> to the north of the diamond hill mtr station , </s>
<s> 2.7 hectares of land or one per cent of the total area have been zoned " other specified uses " for a commercial / residential development above a public transport terminus . </s>
<s> part of the development has been completed . </s>
<s> the maximum domestic and non @-@ domestic gross floor areas of the development are 107,500 and 52,200 square metres respectively . </s>
<s> about 48.3 hectares , or 15 per cent of the total land area , </s>
<s> have been zoned " government / institution / community " ( gic ) for the development of gic facilities to serve local residents . </s>
<s> major existing gic uses include the wong tai sin police station , wong tai sin infirmary , our lady of maryknoll hospital , san po kong magistracy and government offices . </s>
<s> meanwhile , </s>
<s> the planned gic uses include a clinic , an indoor recreation centre , a service reservoir and a pumping station , and a number of primary and secondary schools . </s>
<s> about 24.5 hectares , </s>
<s> or eight per cent of the total area , have been zoned " open space " to provide active and passive recreational uses . </s>
<s> major existing open spaces include the choi hung road playground , east kai tak playground , tsz wan shan estate central playground , lok wah street rest garden and fung tak road park . </s>
<s> the proposed open spaces include an open space at part of the ex @-@ blackdown barracks site and several sites for urban park and other recreational uses . </s>
<s> about 74.6 hectares , or 23 per cent of the total area , </s>
<s> have been zoned " green belt " to define the limit of urban development . </s>
<s> the hillslopes of temple hill , unicorn ridge and lion rock are within this zone . </s>
<s> the rest , about 48.7 hectares , or 15 per cent of the total area , </s>
<s> has been reserved for road and other related uses . </s>
<s> the approved ozp ( no. s / k 11 / 9 ) is available for public inspection during office hours at : </s>
<s> * planning department , 16 th floor , murray building , garden road , central , hong_kong ; </s>
<s> * kowloon district planning office , 11 th floor , leighton centre , 77 leighton road , </s>
<s> causeway bay , </s>
<s> fourth floor , san po kong government offices building , king fuk street , san po kong , kowloon . </s>
<s> copies of the plan are available for sale at the survey and mapping office , lands department , 14 th floor , murray building , garden road , central , hong_kong and the kowloon map sales office , </s>
<s> tender invites for managing cross boundary coach terminus </s>
<s> the transport department is inviting interested parties to tender for the fitting @-@ out , managing , operating and maintaining of a cross boundary coach terminus in kowloon . </s>
<s> this coach terminus is situated at the ground floor of the hong_kong scout association headquarters on austin road . </s>
<s> the management contract will commence in the first quarter of 1998 on a date specified by the government . </s>
<s> a spokesman for the department said ( today ) : </s>
<s> " the successful tenderer is required to fit @-@ out the terminus by providing additional facilities and associated equipment within four months from the commencement of the contract . </s>
<s> " thereafter , the contractor will manage , operate and maintain the terminus for cross boundary coach services for a period of four years , </s>
<s> with provisions for extension by the government . " </s>
<s> revenue will be generated from charges levied on cross boundary coach operators for using the terminus and other approved income , </s>
<s> such as advertising . </s>
<s> " the contractor will share such revenue with the government as their remuneration , </s>
<s> " the spokesman added . </s>
<s> details of the tender invitation were published in today 's government gazette . </s>
<s> applicants are required to provide evidence of their experiences and competencies in fitting @-@ out , </s>
<s> managing , operating and maintaining such transport facilities or evidence of their abilities to engage expertise and resources in these respects from acceptable sources . </s>
<s> " sufficient and relevant information should be submitted for assessment of whether an applicant is qualified to participate in the tendering or not , </s>
<s> " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> interested parties may obtain the tender documents by producing a company letter indicating their interests from the business management division of the department at room 3728 a , 37 th floor , </s>
<s> immigration tower , 7 gloucester road , wan chai . </s>
<s> application must be submitted in five copies , enclosed in a sealed and marked envelope with the tender reference . </s>
<s> they should be addressed to the chairman , central tender board . </s>
<s> east wing , central government offices , lower albert road , central , hong_kong , on or before noon of january 16 , 1998 . </s>
<s> late submissions will not be accepted . </s>
<s> members of the public can contact mr f y tai on 2829 5484 for further information . </s>
<s> new maximum security complex at stanley prison </s>
<s> a four @-@ storey maximum security complex will be built at stanley prison in april next year to help relieve the congestion in hong_kong 's penal institutions . </s>
<s> the self @-@ contained complex will accommodate 256 category a inmates in eight cell units equipped with workshops , </s>
<s> in addition , there will be a central administration unit , a small library and a chapel inside the building complex which is surrounded by high security fencing . </s>
<s> the works will also involve the demolition of the existing two @-@ storey maximum security unit and a hospital block to make way for the new building complex . </s>
<s> the demolition will follow the completion of a new hospital block early next year . the new block is being built under phase one of the redevelopment projects of stanley prison . </s>
<s> the works , due for completion in september 1999 , is part of the phase two of the redevelopment projects . </s>
<s> new bylaw to facilitate management of new airport </s>
<s> the airport authority ( aa ) has made the airport authority bylaw under the airport authority ordinance to facilitate effective management of the new airport at chek lap kok and to ensure safety and efficiency of airport operations . </s>
<s> the secretary for economic services intends to move a motion for the approval of the bylaw by the provisional legislative council ( plc ) at its meeting on december 17 . </s>
<s> a spokesman for the economic services bureau today ( friday ) said that subject to the plc 's endorsement , </s>
<s> the bylaw was expected to be brought into operation in early 1998 to tie in with the programme of airport trials . </s>
<s> he said that most of the provisions in the airport authority bylaw were modelled on the existing hong_kong airport ( regulations ) ordinance and its subsidiary legislation which applied to kai tak , </s>
<s> the aa will provide a briefing on the bylaw to the panel on economic services of the plc at its meeting next monday ( december 1 ) . </s>
<s> executive council makes air navigation amendment order </s>
<s> the air navigation ( hong_kong ) ( amendment ) order 1997 was made by the executive council on november 25 , 1997 . </s>
<s> a spokesman for the economic services bureau today ( friday ) said that before july 1 , </s>
<s> 1997 , the nationality mark for aircraft registered in hong_kong was a group of two capital letters " vr " and the registration mark was a group of three capital letters beginning with " h " , that is " haa " to " hzz " . </s>
<s> pursuant to article 129 ( 1 ) of the basic law , </s>
<s> it was agreed at the sino @-@ british joint liaison group in june this year that from july 1 , </s>
<s> 1997 aircraft registered in hong_kong must use " b " , the unified nationality mark of china , </s>
<s> as their nationality mark but they could continue to use a group of three letters beginning with the letter " h " as their registration mark . </s>
<s> there was a six @-@ month transitional period from july 1 to december 31 , 1997 for hong_kong airlines to amend the nationality marks on their aircraft . </s>
<s> the spokesman said that currently , </s>
<s> the air navigation ( hong_kong ) order 1995 reflected only the requirements prior to july 1 , 1997 and provided that the nationality mark of aircraft registered in hong_kong should be " a group of two capital letters " . </s>
<s> the amendment order aimed to bring it in line with the provisions laid down by the central people 's government concerning the nationality marks of aircraft , he added . </s>
<s> the amendment order published in the government gazette today is proposed to come into effect on january 1 , 1998 to tie in with the expiration of the concerned transitional arrangements . </s>
