<s> trunk sewer system proposed for hung shui kiu </s>
<s> the environmental protection department published in the gazette today ( friday ) a plan to build a trunk sewer system at the unsewered area of hung shui kiu of yuen long . </s>
<s> the new sewerage system will effectively reduce pollutants currently discharged to nearby watercourses and bring improvements to the sanitary conditions of the area , a spokesman for the environmental protection department said . </s>
<s> the proposed project will collect sewage generated from existing village houses and future residential and commercial developments for an estimated population of about 40,000 . </s>
