<s> the financial secretary , mr donald tsang , will depart tomorrow ( sunday ) for kuala lumpur to participate in a meeting of finance ministers scheduled for december 1 and 2. </s>
<s> the participants are from the asean economies plus australia , china , hong_kong special administrative region ( hksar ) , japan , korea and the united_states . </s>
<s> the meeting is hosted by the deputy prime minister and finance minister of malaysia , mr anwar ibrahim . </s>
