<s> the framework was agreed in manila on november 19 , 1997 by senior finance and central bank officials representing 14 economies including hksar and was endorsed by the apec economic leaders on november 25 in vancouver . </s>
<s> other topics for discussion include the role of market participants in the recent crisis , financial liberalisation and global capital flows . </s>
