<s> lpg taxi trial scheme launched </s>
<s> to fundamentally and effectively improve our air quality so as to safeguard public health in hong_kong rested in the quest for a cleaner motor fuel which could take the place of diesel , </s>
<s> the secretary for planning , environment and lands , mr bowen leung , said this ( saturday ) morning . </s>
<s> " hong_kong has relied heavily on the use of diesel vehicles , thus rendering a high concentration of respirable suspended particulates ( rsp ) beyond the acceptable level , </s>
<s> " mr leung said during the launching of the liquefied petroleum gas ( lpg ) taxi trial scheme . </s>
<s> like many other countries , mr leung said hong_kong 's public health is being adversely affected by the large fleet of motor vehicles which emit a considerable amount of rsp . </s>
<s> " overseas studies indicate that the higher the rsp concentration , </s>
<s> the higher would be the rate of respiratory infection . </s>
<s> " the technical development of lpg vehicles used in many overseas countries such as japan , </s>
<s> the netherlands and australia for many years has reached a mature state . </s>
<s> " we are , therefore , </s>
<s> very confident about the safety standard of lpg vehicles . </s>
<s> " furthermore , the emission of such vehicles are far cleaner than those of diesel vehicles . </s>
<s> it will render a great help in improving our air quality , " he said . </s>
<s> thirty lpg taxis taking part in the year @-@ long trial scheme assembled at the lpg filling station in tsing yi to mark the launching of the scheme . </s>
<s> mr leung , together with the secretary for transport , mr nicholas ng ; the commissioner for transport , mrs fanny law , and the director of environmental protection , </s>
<s> mr robert law officiated at a ceremony in sending off the taxis . </s>
<s> the acting director of electrical and mechanical services , mr k w tong ; and the acting director of fire services , mr k y tsang , </s>
<s> were also present at the function during which a demonstration of the safety aspects of lpg taxis and the filling of these vehicles with the cleaner fuel were conducted . </s>
<s> to determine whether lpg vehicles would suit the local conditions , several departments have since 1996 been working with the gas suppliers and the motor trade in studying their safety requirements . </s>
<s> mr leung said the initial assessment has concluded that it is both safe and technically feasible to use lpg vehicles in hong_kong . </s>
<s> " the launching of the lpg vehicle trial today lays the ground for mass introduction of such vehicles in future . the purpose is to allow the intensive use of lpg vehicles under the local driving environment in ascertaining their practical reliability . </s>
<s> " the data so collected will help us to map out a practical plan to replace the existing diesel taxi fleet , </s>
<s> including the implementation schedule ; any necessary incentive measures and the maintenance and regulatory framework . </s>
<s> " we can also start thinking ahead in working out our ensuing strategy by encouraging other types of diesel vehicles such as light buses to switch to this cleaner fuel , </s>
<s> " he added . </s>
<s> to tie in with the experiment , </s>
<s> four temporary gas filling stations have been set up in chai wan , kowloon bay , shatin height and tsing yi to support the lpg taxis . </s>
<s> the stations are required to comply with the most stringent safety standards in both site selections and operation . </s>
<s> together with the extensive and inter @-@ related protection installations within the stations , the safety of these filling facilities are comparable to those of the existing petrol stations . </s>
<s> mr leung said the government has also established a monitoring committee in reviewing regularly the performance and operating costs of these taxis so that the formulation of policies and the trial run can take place in parallel . </s>
<s> " at the same time , we will set up a comprehensive vehicle repair framework ; arrange for the training of maintenance mechanics and the planning of sufficient lpg filling stations . </s>
<s> " when we have confirmed that lpg vehicles can be used in hong_kong for long term on a large scale , the ancillary facilities could be completed in tandem to support the implementation of a clean air motor fuel strategy , </s>
<s> " said mr leung . </s>
<s> the 30 lpg taxis will provide service as of today and the first batch of customers comprised the six government officials who attended the launching ceremony as each of them took an lpg taxi home after the event was completed . </s>
<s> the hong_kong monetary authority ( hkma ) published its latest issue of the quarterly bulletin today ( saturday ) . </s>
<s> the issue contains a study on the security of internet banking , an explanatory article on latest disclosure requirements for banks ( " financial disclosure package 1997 " ) and two articles on hkma 's new initiatives on the development of the debt market : </s>
<s> securities lending programme and bilateral linkages of central securities depositories . </s>
<s> to prepare for the development of internet banking in hong_kong , </s>
<s> the hkma set up a study group on electronic banking in july 1997 to assess the trend and develop appropriate policy and regulatory responses to this new mode of banking service . </s>
<s> the article outlines the security risks , security measures available to address these risks , and the hkma 's supervisory approach with respect to internet banking in hong_kong . </s>
<s> the 1997 disclosure package for banks comprises a number of new items to enhance transparency of the banking system . </s>
<s> counterparty analysis of securities held , maturity profile of major balance sheet items , breakdown of loan categories , risk management policies , materiality of market risk arising from the trading book , capital adequacy ratio adjusted for market risk , and the year 2000 problem . </s>
<s> the bilateral linkages between hkma 's central moneymarkets unit ( cmu ) and the reserve bank information and transfer system and austraclear in australia will commence operation on monday ( december 1 ) . </s>
<s> the feature article titled " bilateral linkages of central securities depositories " ( csds ) sets out the case for developing such linkages connecting domestic csds in the asian region to form a network , </s>
<s> and illustrates how this will work in practice . </s>
<s> the feature article " securities lending programme " sets out the objectives and the operational framework of the programme which will commence operation on monday ( december 1 ) . </s>
<s> the programme aims specifically to enhance the liquidity of cmu private sector debt securities in the secondary market by providing a mechanism to utilise securities held by long @-@ term investors for short @-@ term use by the more active market participants . </s>
<s> the quarterly bulletin also contains regular articles on the banking and monetary environment during the quarter ending september 1997 . </s>
<s> the quarterly bulletin , which is on sale at the government publications centre , may also be ordered from the press and publications section of the hkma . </s>
