<s> revised prohibition for tung chung road </s>
<s> the transport department today ( saturday ) announced a revised trial scheme to further relax the prohibition on tung chung road between shek mun kap road and south lantau road . </s>
<s> the new scheme will take effect from monday ( december 1 ) at 7 pm . </s>
<s> the existing 7 am - 9 pm prohibited zone on tung chung road will be shortened to 7 am - 7 pm daily every mondays to fridays but round @-@ the @-@ clock prohibition will still be maintained on saturdays , </s>
<s> during the specified periods , </s>
<s> all motor vehicles , except franchised buses , lantau taxis , emergency vehicles and those with valid permits , </s>
<s> will be banned from entering the prohibited zone . </s>
<s> speaking on the trial scheme , a spokesman for the department said : </s>
<s> " recent survey shows that traffic volume on tung chung road in late evenings is below its designed capacity and there is room for short @-@ term relaxation . </s>
<s> " having re @-@ assessed the traffic condition , taking into account public opinions , the department has decided to put on trial this modified traffic control scheme . </s>
<s> the traffic situation will be closely monitored . prohibition will be reinstated to 7 am - 9 pm if the traffic volume in both directions reaches 100 vehicles per hour , or in time of serious congestion or an increase in the number of incidents is observed on tung chung road . " </s>
<s> the spokesman noted that traffic pattern would be different when tung chung new town begins to incorporate more entertainment facilities and upon the commissioning of the new airport in chek lap kok . </s>
<s> " a review of the new scheme will then be conducted to tie in with the anticipated changes in traffic conditions , </s>
<s> " the spokesman added . </s>
<s> vehicles must apply for a tung chung road prohibited zone permit ( pzp ) before they are allowed to enter the restricted part of tung chung road . </s>
<s> the spokesman reminded the public that vehicles with closed road permit ( crp ) and pzp for access to the urban areas will be required to pay full vehicle licence fee as they can drive on all public roads in the territory . </s>
<s> however , those permit holders who only use tung chung road to travel between tung chung and south lantau are required to pay the lower licence fee specified for vehicles operated on just the lantau island . </s>
<s> all roads on lantau island including the whole of tung chung road are closed roads , </s>
<s> except those in tung chung new town and the new airport and private roads in the discovery bay . </s>
<s> vehicles without valid closed road permits are not allowed to travel on lantau island closed roads . </s>
