<s> the number of fire hazard abatement notices issued by the fire services department ( fsd ) in the first three quarters of this year totalled 5,709 , an increase of 62 per cent over the same period last year , the acting director of fire services , </s>
<s> mr john tsang kwong @-@ yu , said this ( sunday ) afternoon . </s>
<s> speaking at the launching ceremony of the 1997 / 98 fire prevention campaign , </s>
<s> mr tsang said that during the same period , fsd received 7,651 complaints over fire hazards , an increase of 65 per cent over the corresponding period in 1996 . </s>
<s> these statistics showed an increase in people 's awareness of fire prevention , mr tsang added . </s>
<s> the campaign this year centres on the theme of fire safety of commercial and industrial buildings . </s>
<s> he added that the number of fire calls in the first nine months of 1997 stood at more than 26,000 , causing 40 deaths and 442 injuries . </s>
<s> of the injured , 13 were fire personnel . </s>
<s> the tragic fire at garley building had driven home the message that " prevention is better than cure " , </s>
<s> he said that to maintain the momentum of fire prevention awareness , publicity pamphlets would be distributed and open days of fire stations staged . </s>
<s> a fire prevention campaign on a larger scale and involving more government departments would be held next year , mr tsang disclosed . </s>
<s> today 's ceremony , held at the hong_kong cultural centre piazza in tsim sha tsui , </s>
<s> featured also a mini @-@ concert by canto @-@ pop singers , a lion dance and chinese music performance by fsd staff and a drama starring girl guides who helped spread the message of fire prevention . </s>
<s> twelve display booths mounted by the fsd , </s>
<s> housing department and agriculture and fisheries department accorded visitors a chance to view a wide range of exhibits including fire @-@ fighting equipment and get their hands on computer games with fire prevention messages . </s>
<s> members of copyright tribunal appointed </s>
<s> the chief executive has appointed the members of the copyright tribunal for a period of two years from december 1 , 1997 . </s>
<s> a spokesman for the trade and industry bureau said : " the tribunal is a quasi @-@ judicial body established under the new copyright ordinance . </s>
<s> it is empowered to adjudicate disputes on copyright royalties payable to the various bodies that administer copyright collectively . </s>
<s> " the tribunal now has more extensive jurisdiction than the previous tribunal under the old copyright law . </s>
<s> it may also rule on various copyright disputes arising , for example , between employees and employers . </s>
<s> " the tribunal 's functions are governed by the copyright ordinance , and its procedures are set out by its subsidiary legislation . </s>
<s> " both the chairman , mr andrew liao and the deputy chairman , mr robin bridge , of the tribunal are experienced and highly regarded lawyers specialising in the intellectual property field . </s>
<s> other members are drawn from a wide spectrum from the community , </s>
<s> including major copyright sector . </s>
<s> references to the tribunal can be made to the clerk to the copyright tribunal , c / o intellectual property department , 25 th floor , </s>
<s> wu chung house , queen 's road east , wan chai . </s>
<s> the membership of the copyright tribunal is as follows : - </s>
<s> chairman mr andrew liao cheung sing , jp , </s>
<s> sc , is a barrister specialising in intellectual property laws . </s>
<s> he sits on various government boards and committees and has a long record of public services . he is a member of the law reform commission , and the chairman of both the toy and children 's product safety appeal board panel and the consumer goods safety appeal board . </s>
<s> he is also the convenor of the intellectual property group of the bar association . </s>
<s> deputy chairman mr robin bridge is a retired solicitor specialised in intellectual property . </s>
<s> he was the president of the asian patent attorney association ( hong_kong group ) and a partner of messrs robin bridge and john liu . </s>
<s> seven members </s>
<s> the hon ma fung @-@ kwok is a provisional legislative councillor . he is also the vice chairman of the motion picture industry association . </s>
<s> professor chan wing @-@ wah is the head of the music department of the chinese university of hong_kong . he is also a member of the provisional regional council and the arts development council . </s>
<s> dr chan man @-@ hung is the managing director and chief editor of the commercial press ( hong_kong ) . </s>
<s> mr philip ma is the chairman of the retail management association . he is also the president of sincere department store , co. ltd. </s>
<s> mr fan sai @-@ yee is a professional accountant and a partner of fan , </s>
<s> mr ricky fung tim @-@ chee is the chief executive officer of the international federation of phonographic industry ( hong_kong group ) . </s>
<s> a spokesman for the registration and electoral office ( reo ) urged previously registered electors who are eligible for the right of abode in hong_kong but have not yet obtained a permanent identity card to apply to the immigration department immediately so that they can remain on the electoral roll . </s>
<s> it normally takes six weeks for the immigration department to process such an application , he said . </s>
<s> the reo has issued letters by registered post to about 34,000 previously registered electors reminding them that they must acquire permanent resident status if they wish to preserve their right to vote in the legislative council elections next may . </s>
<s> for those who are eligible for the right of abode , they should apply as soon as possible to the immigration department for verification of their eligibility for a permanent identity card . </s>
<s> an information leaflet and an application form have been sent together with the letter to help them better understand their position and make an application as early as possible . </s>
<s> when an application is approved , the immigration department will issue to the applicant a letter stating that he has an established claim to the right of abode in hong_kong and that he can register for a permanent identity card . </s>
<s> the reo accepts that this approval letter is sufficient evidence regarding the permanent resident status for voter registration purpose . </s>
<s> if these persons cannot produce satisfactory documentary proof by january 16 , </s>
<s> their names will be removed from the 1998 provisional register of electors of geographical constituencies , and included in an omissions list , which will be published around mid @-@ february 1998 for public inspection . </s>
<s> under the legislative council ordinance enacted in october , a person must be a permanent resident of the hong_kong special administrative region in order to be eligible for registration as an elector . </s>
<s> electors on the existing electoral roll who are not permanent residents will no longer be eligible to be registered . </s>
<s> not only would they not be able to vote in a geographical constituency in the legislative council elections next may , they would not be eligible to be registered as an elector in any functional constituency . </s>
