<s> " mr lam is well @-@ placed for his new appointment to complement the work of the senior directorate in the department of justice , </s>
<s> " the secretary for the civil service , mr w k lam , said . </s>
<s> " he has a wealth of administrative experience so essential to the effective functioning of the post . " </s>
<s> aged 42. mr stephen lam joined the civil service in 1978 and rose to his present rank of aosgb 1 in january 1996 . </s>
<s> he has held appointments in a variety of departments and branches , </s>
