<s> the department of health today ( tuesday ) confirmed that the sample of anti @-@ fever syrup , which the department obtained yesterday from a client who suspected it to be contaminated with the mouth wash , </s>
<s> " following a priority laboratory test , the sample of the medicine which , </s>
<s> according to the client , was dispensed on november 8 from the dispensary of the cheung sha wan jockey club clinic , was confirmed to be uncontaminated anti @-@ fever syrup , </s>
<s> " a department spokesman said . </s>
<s> meanwhile , the department has contacted one of the two clients involved in the incident who were found out of town . </s>
