<s> " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> this has brought to 145 the number of clients whom the department has contacted for follow @-@ up action . </s>
<s> of the 146 affected clients , there is at present only one client outstanding . </s>
<s> although he is out of town , the department will try all means to reach him . </s>
