<s> monitoring after cyanide incident continues </s>
<s> the government will continue to monitor the air , </s>
<s> water and soil quality in the vicinity of tai po road where drums of sodium cyanide fell from a vehicle yesterday to ensure that all conditions remain normal , a government spokesman said today ( friday ) . </s>
<s> " various departments , including the fire services department ( fsd ) , </s>
<s> the government laboratory , the water services department , the environmental protection department ( epd ) , the drainage services department and the police , </s>
<s> the fsd , the government laboratory and the epd visited the site again this afternoon to conduct tests . </s>
<s> " the fsd later cordoned off the vicinity for further inspections . however , </s>
<s> vehicular traffic is not affected , " he said . </s>
<s> " in the light of this incident , </s>
<s> we are reviewing the need for legislative changes to tighten the control of transportation of toxic materials , " he added . </s>
<s> he confirmed that a meeting between the secretary for security and the acting director of fire services was held this morning to discuss matters arising from the incident . </s>
<s> the dangerous goods regulations require all categories of dangerous goods to be properly packaged and labelled to be safe for conveyance . </s>
<s> however , only categories 1 , 2 and 5 dangerous goods are required to be conveyed in a licensed dangerous goods vehicle . </s>
<s> " there are also provisions in the road traffic ( traffic control ) regulations governing the safe loading of goods on vehicles , </s>
<s> " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> " in the meantime , we will be stepping up efforts to educate people handling dangerous goods to observe carefully the necessary safety requirements , " he added . </s>
<s> in relation to yesterday 's incident , the fsd and the police are carrying out investigations to see if there are any breaches of law . </s>
<s> if breaches are found , prosecution action will be taken . </s>
