<s> revision of environmental permit / licence fees </s>
<s> the government intends to increase fees related mainly to the issue of various types of permits and licences specified in a number of environmental legislation concerning air , noise , water pollution control and waste disposal . </s>
<s> with effect from january 16 , </s>
<s> 1998 , fees under seven ordinances , namely , waste disposal , </s>
<s> water pollution control , noise control , air pollution control , road traffic , ozone layer protection and dumping at sea will be revised . </s>
<s> a government spokesman said today ( friday ) that the proposed fee increases would generate about $ 4 million additional revenue a year . </s>
<s> he said most of the fees were last revised in january 1997 . </s>
<s> " the increases are either based on inflation rate or the second phase of a full cost recovery programme implemented since january 1997 . </s>
<s> " it is government 's general policy that fees should recover the full costs . </s>
<s> where the cost recovery rate is low , we have decided to phase in the increases over a number of years to reduce the impact of the revision , </s>
<s> " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> " the proposed increases represent a small portion of the operating costs borne by the relevant trades and should not therefore affect their operations , </s>
<s> " he added . </s>
<s> details of the proposed revision are gazetted today ( friday ) . </s>
<s> licence fees for employment agencies revised </s>
<s> the fee for the issue or renewal of licence for an employment agency under the employment agency regulations will be adjusted with effect from january 17 , 1998 . </s>
<s> the adjustment , which has been approved by the secretary for the treasury under the interpretation and general clauses ordinance , </s>
<s> is set out in the employment agency ( amendment ) regulation 1997 gazetted today ( friday ) . </s>
<s> " the licence fee for an employment agency and the fee for the duplicate licence for each of the branch office of an employment agency have been revised from $ 1,870 and $ 360 to $ 2,000 and $ 385 respectively , </s>
<s> under the employment ordinance , </s>
<s> any person who wishes to operate an employment agency must apply to the commissioner for labour for a licence and that an employment agency which operates at more than one location is required to apply for a duplicate licence for each branch location . </s>
<s> the fees were last revised in january 1997 and the present revision is aimed at keeping the fees in line with inflation . </s>
<s> enquiries about the licence fees may be directed to the employment agencies administration of the labour department on 2852 3535 . </s>
<s> revised charges for marpol wastes </s>
<s> the government proposes to revise charges for the disposal of marpol wastes under the merchant shipping ( prevention and control of pollution ) ( charges for discharge of polluting waste ) ( amendment ) regulation 1997 gazetted today ( friday ) . </s>
<s> a government spokesman said the revision sought to raise the variable operating cost ( voc ) recovery rate from 25 per cent to 31 per cent , in line with the " polluter pays " principle . </s>
<s> under the international convention for the prevention of pollution from ships ( marpol convention ) , ships are restricted from discharging wastes containing oil or noxious substances ( marpol wastes ) into the sea . </s>
<s> port administrations are required to ensure that adequate reception facilities are available for the disposal of such wastes . </s>
<s> the convention has been extended to hong_kong and the chemical waste treatment centre ( cwtc ) on tsing yi island has functioned as the reception facility since april 1993 . </s>
<s> initially , the government provided a free service for two years . </s>
<s> under the polluter pays principle , </s>
<s> the merchant shipping ( prevention and control of pollution ) ( charges for discharge of polluting waste ) regulation was introduced in august 1995 , </s>
<s> setting out the marpol charging scheme . </s>
<s> the initial charges were set at a level to recover approximately 20 per cent of the operating costs of the cwtc . </s>
<s> the charges were last revised in december 1996 to acheive 25 per cent voc recovery . </s>
<s> " the latest revision will recover about $ 5.9 million per annum from the international shipping community . however , </s>
<s> the taxpayer will continue to bear 69 per cent of the operating costs . </s>
<s> " besides , </s>
<s> the cost of discharging marpol waste in hong_kong by a typical user will be raised from only 1.1 per cent to 1.36 per cent of his total port costs , </s>
<s> " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> the revised charges are expected to come into effect from january 16 , 1998 . </s>
<s> funds approved for 15 language projects </s>
<s> the director of education and trustee of the language fund , mrs helen c p lai yu , has approved funds totalling $ 8.71 million for the first batch of 15 projects from the fifth call for applications to the fund . </s>
<s> " all these projects meet the criteria set by the standing committee on language education and research for allocation of the language fund . they should be immensely helpful in raising standards in chinese , </s>
<s> including putonghua , and english of our students , " mrs yu said . </s>
<s> of the 15 language projects recommended by the standing committee , also known as scolar , two are research projects addressing the committee 's priority research tenders . </s>
<s> one involves studying the application of computer software to enhance chinese language learning , while the other is for investigating the development of phonological awareness ( as related to reading and spelling competence ) in primary students learning english . </s>
<s> of the nine other chinese projects approved , seven are targeted at improving primary language education , which is scolar 's vetting priority . </s>
<s> they include organisation of school @-@ based activities to promote the use of putonghua , production of tv programmes for young children learning chinese , and running various reading and writing schemes . </s>
<s> similar to chinese projects , most of the english projects approved ( three out of four ) aim at enhancing language ability at the pre @-@ primary and primary levels : </s>
<s> these include a production of a television series in english language for hong_kong children , the development of an english teaching package for use in local primary and english foundation schools . </s>
<s> commenting on the quality and variety of the project designs and the experience and expertise of project leaders , the chairman of scolar , dr daniel tse , </s>
<s> said committee members were deeply impressed and were satisfied that private initiatives should continue to play an important role in raising language proficiency in hong_kong . </s>
<s> " scolar will closely monitor the progress of project implementation and work in conjunction with project leaders on the dissemination of the outcomes arising from these meaningful undertakings , </s>
<s> " dr tse added . </s>
<s> " funding for these projects reflect the continued support the language fund lends to the concerted efforts from schools , educational bodies , tertiary institutions , </s>
<s> the total number of projects supported by the language fund to date is 125 , involving grants amounting to $ 149 million . </s>
<s> processing of the applications received during the 5 th call is now at an advanced stage . announcement of the vetting results will be made shortly . </s>
<s> widening of tolo highway proposed </s>
<s> to cope with the increasing traffic demand in the northeast new territories , the government proposes to widen the section of tolo highway between island house interchange in tai po and ma liu shui interchange in sha tin . </s>
<s> the section , a dual three @-@ lane carriageway , will be widened to a dual four @-@ lane carriageway upon completion . </s>
<s> a notice concerning the proposed works was published in the government gazette today ( friday ) . </s>
<s> a plan showing the extent of the proposed works together with a scheme can be seen at : </s>
<s> 38 pier road , central ; * public enquiry service centre , sha tin district office , </s>
