<s> any person who wishes to object to the proposal should write to the secretary for transport , central government offices , </s>
<s> east wing , second floor , lower albert road , hong_kong , not later than february 3 , 1998 . </s>
<s> proposed public transport terminus in ngau chi wan </s>
<s> the highways department proposes to construct a public transport terminus at the junction of po kong village road and fung shing street in ngau chi wan . </s>
<s> the project comprises the construction of footways , platforms , bus stop shelters , carriageways and bus bays , </s>
<s> as well as drainage and landscaping works . </s>
<s> when completed , the terminus will accommodate the existing on @-@ street minibuses and serve as a terminus for franchised buses . </s>
<s> the work is programmed to start early next year for completion in nine months . </s>
<s> a notice on the proposed works was published in the government gazette today ( friday ) . </s>
<s> members of the public may inspect the plan and scheme at : </s>
<s> central and western district office , ground floor , harbour building , 38 pier road , central ; </s>
<s> * district lands office , kowloon east , 10 th floor , yau ma tei carpark building , </s>
<s> 250 shanghai street , </s>
