<s> any person who objects to the proposal should write to the secretary for transport , central government offices , </s>
<s> east wing , second floor , lower albert road , hong_kong not later than february 3 , 1998 . </s>
<s> land resumption in yuen long for drainage improvement </s>
<s> drainage works will begin in may next year in fung kong tsuen , yuen long , to reduce the risks of flooding in the area . </s>
<s> to facilitate the drainage improvement works , 38 private agricultural lots covering an area of 10,174.4 square metres will be resumed . </s>
<s> a spokesman for the lands department said today ( friday ) that a concrete rectangular drainage channel would be built to serve as an outlet for the whole subcatchment , </s>
<s> covering the area to the south of fung kong tsuen access . </s>
<s> the channel would be 650 metres long , four metres wide and three metres deep . </s>
<s> a 3. 5 @-@ metre @-@ wide ancillary vehicular access road will also be built to facilitate channel maintenance in future . </s>
<s> " the yuen long provisional district board and village representatives have been consulted on the drainage and resumption proposals , </s>
<s> " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> " they are supportive of the whole project , </s>
<s> which will help reduce flooding risks for the 1,200 villagers in the area , " he added . </s>
<s> as part of the rural planning and improvement strategy programme , the drainage works is due for completion in late 1999 . </s>
<s> water quality to improve with sewage works in wan chai </s>
<s> sewerage improvement works in wan chai east and north point will be carried out in april next year . </s>
<s> " the works form part of stage i of the wan chai east and north point sewerage project , </s>
<s> an integral part of the government 's on @-@ going effort to improve the sewerage and sewage treatment facilities in the territory , " a spokesman for the drainage services department said today ( friday ) . </s>
<s> outlining the works involved , the spokesman said sewers ranging from 300 millimetres to 900 millimetres in diameter would be laid in trenches with depth up to five metres in the upstream catchments of wan chai east and north point . </s>
<s> they will also include the construction of three kilometres of reticulation sewers as well as associated manholes / access chambers and the relining of about 0.6 kilometres of existing sewers . </s>
<s> " when completed in april 2000 , </s>
<s> these works will provide sufficient capacity in the sewers to meet a projected population of 360,000 in the areas by the year 2011 , " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> he added that the wan chai east and north point sewerage project would be completed late 2002 . </s>
<s> " by that time , the water quality in victoria harbour will be greatly improved , " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> statistics advisory board meeting </s>
<s> the statistics advisory board reviewed the main lines of government statistical work and its latest developments at a recent meeting . </s>
<s> the statistics advisory board is a non @-@ statutory advisory body which advises the commissioner for census and statistics on matters pertaining to official statistics work . </s>
<s> apart from general statistical developments , the board considered several specific issues at the meeting . </s>
<s> these included the compilation of balance of payments ( bop ) statistics for hong_kong , composite employment estimates , distribution of household income and statistics relating to trading firms with manufacturing @-@ related functions . </s>
<s> the board supported the compilation of a complete bop account for hong_kong . this extension in statistical work represents hong_kong 's further commitment to the international community in providing detailed and sufficient economic and financial statistics to investors around the world . </s>
<s> in compiling bop statistics , data have to be collected from financial institutions , </s>
<s> such as banks and securities houses , and other business enterprises . </s>
<s> its rather detailed data requirement will inevitably mean considerable reporting burden to these organisations . </s>
<s> board members were satisfied , however , that the data to be requested from respondents by the census and statistics department was not excessive when compared with the practices of advanced economies such as usa , </s>
<s> canada , australia , singapore and the united kingdom . </s>
<s> they also recognised that the department had been making every effort in containing data requirements , simplifying questionnaires and streamlining procedures so as to minimise respondents ' burden . </s>
<s> board members also advised the department to explore the feasibility of providing electronic templates as an alternative to paper forms for data collection to facilitate respondents in submitting the required information . </s>
<s> regarding composite employment estimates , employment data are at present collected under two different survey systems , namely , </s>
<s> the quarterly survey of employment and vacancies ( sev ) , </s>
<s> which is establishment @-@ based ; and the general household survey ( ghs ) , which is household @-@ based . </s>
<s> the sev and ghs employment data serve different analytical purposes and complement each other in analysis of the labour market situation . </s>
<s> however , the two sets of figures are not fully consistent due to many technical reasons . </s>
<s> board members were aware of the growing demand for a single set of employment estimates which would facilitate users in describing the territory @-@ wide employment structure by industry . </s>
<s> they supported the department 's move in compiling the composite employment estimates by reconciling the sev and ghs estimates under a coherent statistical framework . </s>
<s> members reckoned that the composite employment estimates should be used when the territory @-@ wide employment broken down by industry sector was required . </s>
<s> board members also recommended the department to further consider enhancing the composite employment estimates by providing more breakdowns to cater for various types of social and economic analyses . </s>
<s> meanwhile , members noted that the income level of the hong_kong population had increased significantly in real terms over the period from 1986 to 1996 . </s>
<s> the increase was faster in the high income groups than the low income groups , leading to an increase in the extent of income disparity over the same period . </s>
<s> some members believed that factors like increase in the number of new arrivals from the mainland of china , importation of labour , and changes in household size might have attributed to widening the disparity . </s>
<s> members were aware of the need to be cautious about the limitations of these statistics . </s>
<s> in studying the data on income distribution , </s>
<s> separate account should be taken of factors such as the effect of upward social mobility of individual persons over time , the provision of social benefits by the government , and the structural transformation of occupational pattern . </s>
<s> in discussing the drawing of poverty line , board members concurred that any attempt to do so would involve a lot of subjective value judgement . </s>
<s> they noted that there was no consensus among the hong_kong community on the definition of a poverty line and considered that consensus would be difficult to reach . </s>
<s> however , they urged that more statistics on income and poverty should be compiled to facilitate social research on the subject . </s>
<s> turning to the topic of trading firms with manufacturing @-@ related functions , members noted that many trading firms in hong_kong were serving as a local base for manufacturing firms in the mainland of china and operating in a way somewhat different from conventional trading firms . </s>
<s> these trading firms with manufacturing @-@ related functions have considerable involvement in the technical aspects of the manufacturing processes . </s>
<s> when analysing the situation of the manufacturing industry in hong_kong , one should therefore take account of both figures on manufacturing firms and those on trading firms with manufacturing @-@ related functions . </s>
<s> members suggested that cross @-@ reference should be made in relevant publications to ensure that users would fully recognise the availability and usage of the two sets of figures . </s>
<s> " the statistics advisory board meets regularly and provides very useful advice to the census and statistics department , " said mr frederick ho , commissioner for census and statistics and chairman of the statistics advisory board . </s>
<s> " we will continue to inform the public from time to time of the major issues considered by the board , " he added . </s>
<s> new edition of hong_kong social & economic trends on sale </s>
<s> the 1997 edition of the hong_kong social and economic trends published by the census and statistics department is now on sale . </s>
<s> the period of statistical analysis covered by this edition is from 1986 to 1996 . </s>
<s> with 78 tables and 42 charts , plus concise descriptions , the publication gives readers an overall view of hong_kong 's social and economic development over the past decade . </s>
<s> contents of the publication include : </s>
<s> * population growth and changes in demographic structure </s>
<s> * development in housing , education , health and social welfare </s>
<s> * economic growth as reflected by the national accounts statistics </s>
<s> * developments in major sectors of the economy </s>
<s> * inflation as reflected by changes in the consumer price indices </s>
<s> * external trade </s>
<s> * labour market </s>
<s> the publication also provides definitions of important terms , explanations of key concepts and sources of information . </s>
<s> the publication is on sale at $ 66 per copy . special discounts are available for bulk purchase from school students . </s>
<s> purchases can be made at : </s>
<s> - government publications centre , ground floor , low block , queensway government offices , 66 queensway , hong_kong </s>
<s> - publications unit , census and statistics department , 19 th floor , wanchai tower , 12 harbour road , wan chai , hong_kong </s>
<s> enquiries on the publication may be directed to the general statistics branch ( 2 ) of the census and statistics department at 2582 4734 . </s>
<s> two suspected cases of h 5 n 1 discovered </s>
<s> the department of health today ( saturday ) announced the discovery of two more suspected cases of h 5 n 1 influenza a. </s>
<s> the two suspected cases involved a 54 @-@ year @-@ old man and a 13 @-@ year @-@ old girl . the former has died and the latter is still in hospital . </s>
<s> " our laboratory results were available this morning , </s>
<s> " a department spokesman said . </s>
<s> " the laboratory specimens of the two suspected cases have been sent urgently to the centers for disease control and prevention in atlanta , united_states for confirmation . </s>
<s> " the hospital authority has been informed of the initial findings and has been advised to take appropriate surveillance and prophylactic measures . " in the meantime , </s>
<s> investigation into the two suspected cases is being conducted . " </s>
<s> the special working group on h 5 n 1 set up by the director of health has called an urgent meeting tomorrow ( sunday ) , </s>
<s> after which an announcement will be made . </s>
<s> experts from the centers for disease control and prevention in atlanta will be arriving tonight to participate in the investigation of the recent h 5 n 1 cases . </s>
<s> the spokesman advised that the best way to combat influenza infection was to build up body resistance by having a proper diet with adequate exercise and rest . </s>
<s> " good ventilation should be maintained to avoid the spread of respiratory tract infection , </s>
<s> " he added . </s>
<s> renovated shek wu hui clinic offers more health services the shek wu hui jockey club clinic has been greatly enhanced with improvements and new facilities to provide a wider range of health services including elderly health care and student health screening . </s>
<s> this has been made possible by a renovation and improvement works project which was recently completed at a cost of $ 21 million generously donated by the hong_kong jockey club charities trust . </s>
<s> to mark the completion of the project , a plaque unveiling ceremony will be held next tuesday ( december 9 ) afternoon . </s>
<s> the deputy director of health , dr paul saw ; steward of the hong_kong jockey club , mr david eldon ; and a representative from the architectural service department , will officiate . </s>
<s> the shek wu hui jockey club clinic , a three @-@ storey building situated at jockey club road in sheung shui , is one of the 63 clinics run by the department of health ( dh ) . </s>
<s> it was built in 1960 and has been serving residents in the northern part of the new territories for more than three decades . </s>
<s> " the renovation and improvement works at the shek wu hui clinic clearly reflects the department 's commitment to providing high quality client @-@ oriented service to the community , </s>
<s> " a dh spokesman said . </s>
<s> the renovation project includes structural improvements to the general out @-@ patient clinic on the ground floor , </s>
<s> conversion of the maternity home on the first floor into an elderly health centre and conversion of the departmental quarters on the second floor into a student health screening centre . </s>
<s> other improvement works include the provision of a lift from ground floor to top floor and improvement of the building 's fire services installations . </s>
<s> " the installation of a lift enables easy access to various floors for the patients and clients , </s>
<s> particularly the elderly , " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> " the additions of a new student health screening centre and an elderly health centre are part of the overall improvement in the provision of health services to the northern part of the new territories , and are in line with the recommendations of the working party in primary health care . " </s>
<s> wages must be paid on time </s>
<s> the labour department reminds employers to pay their employees on time , otherwise , they will face severe punishment . </s>
<s> senior labour officer ( prosecutions ) , mrs tonia leung , </s>
<s> gave the reminder today ( saturday ) following a recent court case in which transway construction and engineering limited in to kwa wan was fined $ 20,000 at kwun tong magistracy for failing to pay wages to an employee . </s>
<s> " under section 23 of the employment ordinance , </s>
<s> wages are due at the end of the wage period , and must be cleared as soon as practicable and in any case , </s>
<s> not later than seven days after the end of the period , " mrs leung said . </s>
<s> " moreover , section 25 of the ordinance stipulates that where a contract of employment is terminated , </s>
<s> wages should be paid to the employee on the day of termination and in any case , not later than seven days after termination of employment . " </s>
<s> any employer who fails to comply with these provisions commits an offence which upon conviction may incur a fine of $ 200,000 and one year 's imprisonment . </s>
<s> " to safeguard their rights , </s>
<s> employees whose wages are not paid within the statutory period should approach the labour relations service for advice and assistance as soon as possible , </s>
<s> " mrs leung added . </s>
<s> updates on h 5 n 1 influenza a situation </s>
<s> the preliminary investigations showed that at this stage , </s>
<s> human @-@ to @-@ human transmission of the h 5 n 1 influenza a virus has not been proven and further investigations will be made to study this possibility , </s>
<s> the special working group on h 5 n 1 announced today ( sunday ) . </s>
<s> the initial findings also showed that the four h 5 cases did not share a common source , nor was the virus transmitted from one case to the others . </s>
<s> speaking at a press conference convened after an urgent meeting earlier this afternoon , the deputy director of health , dr paul saw , who is the chairman of the working group , </s>
<s> said : " the first case was confirmed in august . since then , we have stepped up surveillance and as a result , </s>
<s> we have been able to detect the latest three cases . </s>
<s> " this latest development has caused concern both in the local and the international communities . however , </s>
<s> there is no cause for panic as available evidence does not suggest that the disease is widespread . " </s>
<s> dr saw said since the detection of the first case in august , </s>
<s> hong_kong had been working closely with the world health organisation ( who ) and the centres for disease control and prevention and other national authorities in surveillance , case detection and investigation of this new strain of influenza a virus . </s>
<s> " the who has been asked to alert vaccine production centres in the world in the case investigation to follow developments here with a view to preparing the necessary vaccines , </s>
<s> " he said . </s>
<s> " arising from these suspected cases , </s>
<s> the department of health has stepped up the influenza surveillance activities in hong_kong and the who fully supports the measures being taken . " </s>
<s> to further enhance surveillance in hong_kong , dr saw said , the department of health would extend surveillance coverage to all general out @-@ patient clinics . </s>
<s> the hospital authority would also set up surveillance in public hospitals . </s>
<s> in the meantime , dr saw said , the agriculture and fisheries department had also increased surveillance in poultry in collaboration with the university of hong_kong . </s>
<s> colleges and health care workers available information about the h 5 virus through letters and the department of health 's homepage on the internet ( @url@ ) . </s>
<s> the special working group also released the details of the two suspected case discovered yesterday . </s>
<s> the 54 @-@ year @-@ old man involved was admitted to the queen elizabeth hospital on november 29 and died on december 5 of complications arising from pneumonia . </s>
<s> the 13 @-@ year @-@ old girl was admitted on november 26 and is now under treatment in prince of wales hospital . </s>
<s> investigations into the two suspected cases are still continuing . </s>
<s> dr saw advised members of the public that the best way to combat influenza infection was to build up body resistance by having a proper diet with adequate exercise and rest . </s>
<s> " good ventilation should be maintained to avoid the spread of respiratory tract infection . " as for the young , </s>
<s> the elderly and those with chronic diseases , they should seek medical consultations promptly if they develop influenza @-@ like illness , " dr saw added . </s>
<s> more than 120,000 registered as new voters </s>
<s> more than 120,000 people registered as new voters when the voter registration ambassadors ( vras ) called on them yesterday ( saturday ) . </s>
<s> " we are pleased with the work of the vras , </s>
<s> " said a spokesman for the home affairs department . </s>
<s> moreover , another 30,000 registered voters reported change of addresses . the registration and electoral office will update the electoral roll accordingly . </s>
<s> the 30,000 voter registration ambassadors will continue their household visits today ( sunday ) . they aim at knocking on the doors of all the two million households in hong_kong on these two days . </s>
<s> further follow @-@ up visits will be conducted in the evenings of december 8 - 12 to reach those who cannot be contacted over the weekend . </s>
<s> had directorate backs voter registration drive </s>
<s> the director of home affairs , mrs shelley lau , </s>
<s> together with her senior staff today ( sunday ) toured districts to encourage voter registration ambassadors ( vras ) in their efforts to boost the number of electors for next may 's legislative council elections . </s>
<s> accompanied by hundreds of vras , mrs lau and her deputy directors , mr lui hau @-@ tuen and mr augustine cheng , </s>
<s> separately made door @-@ to @-@ door visits in the hong_kong island , new territories east and kowloon west constituencies aiming to maximise the number of voters for the first legislative council elections under the hong_kong special administrative region government . </s>
<s> they will also visit kowloon east and new territories west in the next few days . </s>
<s> mrs lau said she was very impressed by the enthusiasm and commitment which the young vras brought to their work and expressed satisfaction at the results achieved in the first day of the voter registration week . </s>
<s> up to this afternoon , more than 170,000 new voters were registered by the hardworking vras led by the home affairs department staff . </s>
<s> they are also spreading the message of civic education . this is the perfect exercise for introducing our young people to the democratic process , </s>
<s> and to help them develop a true sense of belonging and commitment to hong_kong , their home , " she said . </s>
<s> mrs lau was also satisfied with the safety arrangements made for the ambassadors , </s>
<s> but stressed that they must also take care of their personal safety as they went about making house calls on potential voters . </s>
<s> " they have been instructed to travel in pairs , to avoid entering the flats which they visit or accepting food or refreshments from people , " mrs lau added . </s>
