<s> " he noted . </s>
<s> as regards the domestic staff , the spokesman explained that they not only provide support to functions held at gh , </s>
<s> they also provide domestic services to the ce and mrs tung and support to functions held at the ce 's office , the ce 's official residence and the fanling lodge . </s>
<s> he stressed that there is no question that either the gh is under @-@ utilised and the domestic staff underemployed . </s>
