<s> ma on shan water treatment works open day </s>
<s> members of the public will have the opportunity to see for themselves the thorough treatment of their potable water by visiting the treatment works in ma on shan this saturday ( december 13 ) . </s>
<s> visitors can take a guided tour to have a close look at the various components of the treatment works , including the flocculation and sedimentation tanks for the removal of suspended solids in raw water , and the filter beds where more finely divided suspensions are retained on sand layers . </s>
<s> there will also be display panels and a video show to illustrate the functions of the water supplies department , the current and future sources of hong_kong 's water supply , and other treatment works in the territory . </s>
<s> commissioned in march this year , the ma on shan water treatment works has a daily treatment capacity of 227,000 cubic metres to meet demand from 500,000 customers in ma on shan and sha tin areas . </s>
<s> the treatment works will be open to public from 10 am to 4 pm on saturday as one of the water supplies department 's annual event to help the general public understand how their essential daily need is provided . </s>
<s> the ma on shan water treatment works is located off sai sha road , kwun hang , </s>
<s> sai kung . free shuttle bus service will be provided at on luk street near the bus terminus at sunshine city , ma on shan . </s>
<s> local student finance scheme to be extended to apa students </s>
<s> a government spokesman announced today ( thursday ) that with effect from the 1998 / 99 academic year , </s>
<s> the ambit of the local student finance scheme ( lsfs ) currently administered by the student financial assistance agency ( sfaa ) will be extended to cover local full @-@ time students of the hong_kong academy for performing arts ( hkapa ) . </s>
<s> he explained that as all publicly @-@ funded tertiary institutions except the hkapa are currently covered by the lsfs , </s>
<s> it was fair for the hkapa students to be covered by the scheme as well . </s>
<s> under the new arrangement , students of the hkapa can obtain their grants and loans more speedily as processing time can be cut short substantially . </s>
<s> they will also be entitled to apply for loans under the new non @-@ means tested loan scheme on par with their counterparts in other tertiary institutions . </s>
<s> hkapa has been operating since its inception a financial assistance scheme on its own to ensure that none of its local full @-@ time students would be deprived of access to education due to lack of means . </s>
<s> study on civic awareness and moral values of youth </s>
<s> a working group under the commission on youth has started a study on civic awareness and moral values of youth . </s>
<s> a spokesman for the commission on youth said today ( thursday ) that the commission on youth was being tasked in the policy address to carry out a study on how our young people could take up a more active role in building up the special administrative region and in voluntary work . </s>
<s> the working group had identified " civic awareness " and " moral values " to be the core subjects under the study . </s>
<s> the study will be divided into two parts : </s>
<s> a research for obtaining a profile of the value @-@ orientations , attitudes , expectation and voluntary participation level of young people ; </s>
<s> and a consultation for gathering information and views from different sectors of the community . </s>
<s> the spokesman said : </s>
<s> " apart from scientific research , we are going to meet people from different sectors of the community . it is important that we obtain information and views from both the young people and from the community at large . </s>
<s> either to our e @-@ mail address ( hab 1 @ hab.gcn.gov.hk ) or by mail or fax to : commission on youth c / o home affairs bureau </s>
<s> " details of the topical issues are now available on the internet home page ( info.gov.hk/hab ) under ' topical issues - commission on youth ' or can be obtained from either the marketing office , </s>
<s> government information services , 17 th floor , siu on centre , 176 @-@ 192 lockhart road , wan chai , </s>
<s> or the home affairs bureau at the above address . </s>
<s> " it is expected that the study will enable the commission to recommend on the way forward to enhance the promotion of civic awareness and moral values among the young people , including youth participation in voluntary work . " </s>
<s> two lantau link special bus services to cease operation </s>
<s> in view of a significant drop in patronage , </s>
<s> two lantau link recreational bus routes x 11 and x 32 will cease operation on sunday ( december 14 ) , the transport department announced today ( thursday ) . </s>
<s> at present , routes x 11 and x 32 depart from moreton terrace and kwai fong mtr station respectively for lantau link on sundays and public holidays . </s>
<s> speaking on the arrangements , a spokesman for the department said : </s>
<s> " these two bus routes were introduced shortly after the opening of the lantau link to cater for the upsurge public demand for a tour of the new highways and bridges . </s>
<s> " such demand dropped significantly in the last two months . " </s>
<s> in november , the patronage of these two routes carried an average of 380 and 132 passengers respectively on sundays and public holidays while the average for june was 2,900 . </s>
<s> this represented a drop of about 87 per cent for route x 11 and 95 per cent for route x 32 . </s>
<s> " it is anticipated that the discontinuation of the bus services will not cause any inconvenience to the public , </s>
<s> " the spokesman added . </s>
<s> meanwhile , members of the public can make use of the following bus routes to visit the lantau link : </s>
<s> e 21 ( tai kok tsui - tung chung new town ) </s>
<s> e 22 ( kowloon city ferry pier - tung chung new town ) </s>
<s> e 31 ( tsuen wan ferry pier - tung chung new town ) </s>
<s> proceeds from the 1997 musical rally for the community organised by the 221 st hong_kong scout group of the correctional services department ( csd ) were presented to charities today ( thursday ) . </s>
<s> a total of $ 103,260 was presented to two charitable organisations , </s>
<s> namely , sincere charitable foundation and the treats , with each receiving $ 51,630 . </s>
<s> officiating at the cheques presentation ceremony were the president of the 221 st hong_kong group , mr steve lau hon @-@ wah , and the chairman of the group , mr herman hui chung @-@ shing . </s>
<s> the spectacular musical rally for the community was held on october 17 and 18 this year at the queen elizabeth stadium and attended by a sizeable audience . </s>
<s> young inmates from institutions of csd performed band displays , marching and dances in the musical event . </s>
<s> the musical rally provides the inmates with an opportunity to serve the community in the course of rehabilitation on turning over a new leaf . </s>
<s> three new suspected h 5 n 1 cases being traced </s>
<s> the department of health ( dh ) today ( friday ) confirmed that the department had received notifications from the hospital authority of three new suspected cases of h 5 n 1 influenza a infection . </s>
<s> the first new suspected case involves a five @-@ year @-@ old girl suffering from respiratory infection . </s>
<s> she was admitted to queen mary hospital on december 10 and is now in stable condition . </s>
<s> the second case involves a 24 @-@ year @-@ old woman who was admitted to yan chai hospital on december 7 . </s>
<s> she is receiving treatment for pneumonia in the hospital 's intensive care ward . </s>
<s> the third case involves a 37 @-@ year @-@ old man who was admitted to queen elizabeth hospital on november 24 for treatment of pneumonia . </s>
<s> he was discharged on december 9 upon recovery . </s>
<s> a dh spokesman said : </s>
<s> " the department is looking into these three new cases and is contacting their families and relatives for further investigation . </s>
<s> " clinical samples of the three patients have been received from the hospital authority for testing by the government virus unit and the centres for disease control and prevention in atlanta , united_states . </s>
<s> once available , results will be announced . " </s>
<s> government 's response to eiu study </s>
<s> in response to media enquiries , </s>
<s> a government spokesman today ( friday ) gave the following comments on the economic intelligence unit ( eiu ) study rating hong_kong the third best place to do business in asia : </s>
<s> " without having sight of the full report it would be difficult for the government to make substantial comments on the rating . </s>
<s> however , on the basis of the information released by the eiu , we have the following initial observations : </s>
<s> * we are glad to note the affirmation by the eiu that strong growth , low taxes , property rights and free trade will remain in place in hong_kong . </s>
<s> this is in line with the recent recognition by the heritage foundation in rating hong_kong the freest economy in the world . </s>
<s> * the relatively high cost of running businesses in hong_kong is one thing but overall profitability is another . </s>
<s> we believe hong_kong remains a profitable place for businesses to thrive . </s>
<s> we are confident that our sophisticated range of business and financial services will continue to attract businesses to hong_kong . </s>
<s> * there is no sign of china interfering the hong_kong economy . </s>
<s> this is evidenced by the fact that hong_kong had been left to deal with the recent financial turmoil on its own . " </s>
<s> in response to press enquiries on the global warming conference in kyoto , </s>
<s> a government spokesman said today ( friday ) that the government would study the agreement on new greenhouse gas emission levels very carefully . </s>
<s> " there are many ways to reduce greenhouse gas emission and we need to consult widely before deciding what approach to take , </s>
<s> " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> the united_nations framework convention on climate change ( unfccc ) controls the emissions of greenhouse gases , such as carbon dioxide . </s>
<s> the existing treaty requires developed countries to reduce their year 2000 emissions to 1990 levels . the agreement reached in kyoto established new targets for developed countries for the period up to the year 2010 . </s>
<s> the spokesman said : " although hong_kong is not a party to the unfccc , </s>
<s> we forecast that our emission levels will be around 1990 levels by the year 2000 . </s>
<s> " in 1996 hong_kong 's co 2 emission levels were 5 percent below 1990 levels , </s>
<s> " he said . </s>
<s> in fact , very few developed countries will achieve the unfccc targets . </s>
<s> hong_kong 's forecast population growth means that even keeping greenhouse gas emissions at 1990 levels in 2010 requires significant per capita reductions . </s>
<s> " we have been working for several years on a wide range of energy efficiency projects such as the energy efficiency labelling scheme for electrical appliances , </s>
<s> " the spokesman added </s>
<s> nearly 170 countries are parties to the unfccc . </s>
<s> the protocol agreed in kyoto will not come into effect until it has been ratified by at least six developed countries representing 55 per cent of the world 's greenhouse gas emissions . </s>
<s> the ratification process is expected to take some time as many countries have lengthy internal ratification procedures to undergo . </s>
<s> $ 5 billion granted for quality education fund </s>
<s> following the finance committee 's meeting today ( friday ) , the secretary for education and manpower , </s>
<s> mr joseph w p wong said he was very pleased with the finance committee 's approval of a grant of $ 5 billion to establish a quality education fund ( qef ) to promote quality and innovation in school education at all levels . </s>
<s> " the fund will provide a flexible and responsive funding mechanism to encourage bottom @-@ up initiatives , </s>
<s> " he said . </s>
<s> projects fundable under qef would include school @-@ based innovative projects / experiments ; awards for outstanding performance of schools and teachers ; promotion of extra @-@ curricular activities and school @-@ based training for school principals and teachers . </s>
<s> " the government would shortly appoint a steering committee under the education commission to advise on policies and procedures governing the operation of qef , </s>
<s> and to consider applications for funding and review the effectiveness of funded projects , " mr wong said . </s>
<s> finance committee has also approved the funding for setting up a support unit in the education and manpower bureau to manage qef and to provide secretariat support to the steering committee . </s>
<s> " the steering committee under the education commission will work out the operational details for the quality education fund . i expect the first call for applications can be made early next year , </s>
<s> " mr wong said . </s>
<s> the director of education will be the trustee of qef . the director of accounting services will be appointed to handle the investment of the funds . </s>
<s> an investment advisory committee comprising the chairman of the steering committee , the secretary for education and manpower , director of education and the director of accounting services , </s>
<s> will be established to set policies for and to monitor the investment of the funds . </s>
<s> travel pass and apec business travel card to be launched </s>
<s> two pilot schemes will be launched to speed up immigration clearance for frequent travellers to hong_kong and business people travelling from one participating apec economy to another , </s>
<s> a spokesman for the security bureau said today ( friday ) . </s>
<s> the travel pass pilot scheme , to be introduced early next year , will make it more convenient for foreign businessmen travelling to hong_kong . </s>
<s> " visitors can apply for a travel pass if they hold valid passports ; are eligible to come to hong_kong without a visa for business or social visit purposes ; </s>
<s> have a genuine need to visit hong_kong frequently and have come for visits trouble free on five or more occasions in the 12 @-@ month period immediately preceding application , </s>
<s> " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> a travel pass , which will be charged at a fee of $ 500 and valid for three years , </s>
<s> is good for multiple visits of up to two months on each entry . </s>
<s> with a quota of 10,000 , is open to application on a first @-@ come @-@ first - served basis , he added . </s>
<s> the scheme , also on a trial basis , will be open to business people who are nationals of participating economies , </s>
<s> which include australia , the republic of korea , the philippines , chile and hong_kong . </s>
<s> eligible business people will apply to the designated authority of their own economy . </s>
<s> " hong_kong residents will therefore submit to the director of immigration their applications , </s>
<s> which will be referred to the designated authorities of other participating economies for their assessment and pre @-@ clearance , " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> an apec business travel card is good for multiple visits of two months to participating economies without visas , he said , </s>
<s> adding that the card will be valid for one year for the trial . </s>
<s> the travel card , to be charged at a fee of $ 620 , will be issued to a maximum of 2,000 hong_kong residents under the trial period . </s>
<s> " immigration clearance for holders of the travel pass or the apec business travel card will be faster because they will be able to use resident counters at immigration control points . </s>
<s> " clearance time required by immigration counters for residents is normally shorter than that required by counters for visitors . besides , with pre @-@ clearance , </s>
<s> there is no need for detailed questioning when the approved applicant crosses the control point , " the spokesman explained . </s>
<s> " hong_kong people holding apec business travel cards will also be able to enjoy streamlined immigration clearance at the control points of participating economies , " he said . </s>
<s> " the two schemes are similar in concept to the auto @-@ toll system for tunnels , where vehicle registered for auto @-@ toll can use special lanes to pass toll booths . time is saved because of quicker processing at the booths and shorter queues , </s>
<s> " he added . </s>
<s> for the travel pass pilot scheme , application forms can be obtained from the immigration department , trade @-@ related organisations , and hong_kong economic and trade offices overseas . </s>
<s> " for the apec business travel card trial scheme , we will invite trade related organisations to nominate eligible applicants , </s>
<s> " the spokesman said . </s>
<s> the immigration ( amendment ) ( no. 2 ) regulation 1997 , </s>
<s> which has been approved by the executive council , will empower the director of immigration to issue these documents and to charge fees for them . </s>
<s> the regulation is gazetted today and will be tabled in the provisional legislative council on december 17 . </s>
<s> disability discrimination regulation comes into effect </s>
<s> the disability discrimination ( proceedings by equal opportunities commission ) regulation , which was approved by the provisional legislative council on 10 december 1997 , </s>
<s> comes into effect with the gazettal of the regulation today ( friday ) . </s>
<s> a government spokesman said : </s>
<s> " the regulation enables the equal opportunities commission to bring proceedings in its own name when the commission has reason to believe that a person has committed an unlawful act under the disability discrimination ordinance ( ddo ) ; </s>
<s> the concerned case raises a question of principle and the commission considers it to be in the interests of justice to bring the proceedings . </s>
<s> " before bringing the proceedings , the commission must have already offered assistance by way of conciliation . </s>
<s>
